. There she meets Mao, whose abrupt and bizarre question prompts Nanoka to see herself and her curious life in a completely new light. Now the two travelers from different worlds unite as they take on the dark powers that grip both their lives.\\n<br><br>(Source: VIZ Media, Hulu, edited)\",\"bannerImage\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/banner\\/196012-BbzGv8DuqVah.jpg\",\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx196012-R3YNjunufpYh.jpg\",\"color\":\"#f1935d\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"eVfpoS0rjw0\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/eVfpoS0rjw0\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.anime-mao.com\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/219-EwrfceXsqIWg.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/MAOanimation\"},{\"site\":\"Hulu\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/7-rM06PQyWONGC.png\",\"color\":\"#1CE783\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.hulu.com\\/series\\/mao-7c9b966e-4234-4994-b1ef-37242b834d72\"},{\"site\":\"Disney Plus\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/118-mphNAqNDTvhO.png\",\"color\":\"#21037C\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.disneyplus.com\\/pt-br\\/browse\\/entity-6b6116ca-6f0b-4748-bb8d-b0fbb8eb5119\"},{\"site\":\"Bilibili TV\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/119-NCwGvCjFADGQ.png\",\"color\":\"#00A1D6\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.bilibili.tv\\/en\\/media\\/2343716\"},{\"site\":\"YouTube\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/13-ZwR1Xwgtyrwa.png\",\"color\":\"#FF0000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/playlist?list=PLxSscENEp7Jh6jFqpP-B97p7eUzipzZzv\"},{\"site\":\"Instagram\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.an