\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/206951\",\"description\":\"My reincarnation destination is... \\u201cthe rib of a harem-loving, happy-ending, overpowered hero\\u201d!? An isekai reincarnation anime that defies animation conventions is born!<br><br>\\n\\nBeyond traditional animation, this series delivers an exhilarating isekai reincarnation tale through unconventional techniques like stop-motion, puppet theater, and live-action\\u2014featuring the aloof \\u201cGoddess\\u201d in charge of isekai reincarnations and the protagonist \\u201cMe,\\u201d who endures one absurd reincarnation after another!<br><br>\\n\\n(Source: YouTube Channel, translated)\",\"bannerImage\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/banner\\/206951-P1BNNpbqN4zG.jpg\",\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx206951-qiHcrw7pwzuq.jpg\",\"color\":\"#5dc9f1\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"suKjfBsH3UM\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/suKjfBsH3UM\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/219-EwrfceXsqIWg.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/rokkotsu_anime\"},{\"site\":\"Instagram\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/48-VFlxaXGaNqXk.png\",\"color\":\"#833AB4\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.instagram.com\\/rokkotsu_anime\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/rokkotsu-anime.com\\/\"},{\"site\":\"YouTube\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/13-ZwR1Xwgtyrwa.png\",\"color\":\"#FF0000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/@rokkotsu-anime\"},{\"site\":\"Crunchyroll\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/5-AWN2pVlluCOO.png\",\"color\":\"#F88B24\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.crunchyroll.com\\/series\\/GT0037166