\"episode\":8,\"airingAt\":1778860800,\"media\":{\"id\":169228,\"idMal\":56646,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Hokuto no Ken: FIST OF THE NORTH STAR\",\"native\":\"\\u5317\\u6597\\u306e\\u62f3 -FIST OF THE NORTH STAR-\",\"english\":\"FIST OF THE NORTH STAR: HOKUTO NO KEN\"},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2026,\"month\":4,\"day\":11},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"season\":\"SPRING\",\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Drama\",\"Sci-Fi\"],\"synonyms\":[\"El pu\\u00f1o de la Estrella del Norte: HOKUTO NO KEN\"],\"duration\":24,\"popularity\":4985,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"MANGA\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u5317\\u6597\\u306e\\u62f3\\u30a2\\u30cb\\u30e1 #FISTOFTHENORTHSTAR \",\"averageScore\":57,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/169228\",\"description\":\"In the year 199X, the world is engulfed in a nuclear inferno! The seas have vanished. The earth lies in ruins. It seems all life has been wiped out...but humanity has not perished!<br><br>\\n\\nAcross the scorched and broken land, survivors cling to hope, desperately searching for food and water. However, their hopes are trampled underfoot by violence. Might makes right in this world, and the weak are crushed without mercy.<br><br>\\n\\nFrom the depths of that despair, a lone man with seven scars on his chest emerges. His name is Kenshiro, heir to the legendary assassination art Hokuto Shinken. As he roams the wasteland in pursuit of his sworn enemy Shin, who stole his fianc\\u00e9e Yuria, Kenshiro answers the cries of the oppressed, becoming a beacon of hope in a world of despair.<br><br>\\n\\nStanding in his path are brutal survivors of the apocalypse, their ambitions twisted by power and greed. In a world where the weak are prey and prayers go unheard, Kenshiro forges a path with his iron fists!<br><br>\\n\\n(Source: Official Website)\",\"bannerImage\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/banner\\/169228-L0wA8BGp54fa.jpg\",\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx169228-y79xDpZ29Vv4.jpg\",\"color\":\"#f1bb28\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"Gux_dYHDMK4\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/Gux_dYHDMK4\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/hokuto-anime.com\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/17-R0tMgOvwvhsS.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/twitter.com\\/hokutonokeninfo\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Amazon Prime Video\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/21-bDoNIomehkOx.png\",\"color\":\"#FF9900\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.amazon.co.jp\\/dp\\/B0G4BLNYJJ\"}],\"rankings\":[{\"rank\":90,\"type\":\"RATED\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":false}],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":73,\"name\":\"TMS Entertainment\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/73\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":31149,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Hokuto no Ken\",\"native\":\"\\u5317\\u6597\\u306e\\u62f3\",\"english\":\"Fist of the North Star\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/31149\"}},{\"relationType\":\"ALTERNATIVE\",\"node\":{\"id\":967,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Hokuto no Ken\",\"native\":\"\\u5317\\u6597\\u306e\\u62f3\",\"english\":\"Fist of the North Star\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/967\"}}]}}},{\"id\":411540,\"episode\":7,\"airingAt\":1779111000,\"media\":{\"id\":197824,\"idMal\":62146,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Isekai Nonbiri Nouka 2\",\"native\":\"\\u7570\\u4e16\\u754c\\u306e\\u3093\\u3073\\u308a\\u8fb2\\u5bb6\\uff12\",\"english\":\"Farming Life in Another World 2\"},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2026,\"month\":4,\"day\":6},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"season\":\"SPRING\",\"fo