\"season\":\"SPRING\",\"allTime\":false}],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":7688,\"name\":\"BENTEN Film\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/7688\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":86452,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Reincarnation no Kaben\",\"native\":\"\\u30ea\\u30a3\\u30f3\\u30ab\\u30fc\\u30cd\\u30fc\\u30b7\\u30e7\\u30f3\\u306e\\u82b1\\u5f01\",\"english\":\"Petals of Reincarnation\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/86452\"}}]}}},{\"id\":412600,\"episode\":7,\"airingAt\":1778776080,\"media\":{\"id\":195333,\"idMal\":61943,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Haibara-kun no Tsuyokute Seishun New Game\",\"native\":\"\\u7070\\u539f\\u304f\\u3093\\u306e\\u5f37\\u304f\\u3066\\u9752\\u6625\\u30cb\\u30e5\\u30fc\\u30b2\\u30fc\\u30e0\",\"english\":\"Haibara's Teenage New Game+\"},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2026,\"month\":4,\"day\":3},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"season\":\"SPRING\",\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Romance\",\"Slice of Life\"],\"synonyms\":[\"Haibara\\u2019s Teenage New Game+\"],\"duration\":24,\"popularity\":15867,\"episodes\":12,\"source\":\"LIGHT_NOVEL\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u7070\\u539f\\u304f\\u3093\",\"averageScore\":64,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/195333\",\"description\":\"We all have embarrassing memories or deep regrets from high school, right? Socially anxious college senior Natsuki Haibara sure does. When he thinks back on that time of his life, all he has are fleeting fantasies of a happy adolescence that could have been. Imagine his bewilderment and surprise, then, when he inexplicably finds himself seven years in the past\\u2014one month before his first year of high school! Can Haibara avoid his previous mistakes, make his way to the top of the school social pyramid, and end up with the girl of his dreams? Or will he be forced to relive three years of solitude as the most hated guy in school? He\\u2019ll need all the help he can get in order to succeed, from a workout regimen to online how-to guides, a childhood friend, and plenty of sheer willpower. Watch as Haibara takes a second shot at his teenage years!\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: J-Novel Club)\\n<br><br>\\n<i>Note: The first 4 episodes had an advance screening on March 15th, 2026. The start date reflects the start of the regular series broadcasting.<\\/i>\\n\\n\",\"bannerImage\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/banner\\/195333-66Rnkl0TzxtO.jpg\",\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx195333-KUIF1eqOdVdd.png\",\"color\":\"#1aa1ff\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"MPJrey_y_DU\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/MPJrey_y_DU\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/17-R0tMgOvwvhsS.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/haibara_anime\"},{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/haibarakun-anime.com\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Crunchyroll\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/5-AWN2pVlluCOO.png\",\"color\":\"#F88B24\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.crunchyroll.com\\/series\\/GT00371668\\/haibaras-teenage-new-game\"}],\"rankings\":[{\"rank\":65,\"type\":\"RATED\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":false},{\"rank\":77,\"type\":\"POPULAR\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":false},{\"rank\":30,\"type\":\"POPULAR\",\"season\":\"SPRING\",\"allTime\":false}],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":126,\"name\":\"Studio Comet\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/126\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":143071,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Haibara-kun no Tsuyokute Seishun New Game\",\"native\":\"\\u7070\\u539f\\u304f\\u3093\\u306e\\u5f37\\u304f\\u3066\\u9752\\u6625\\u30cb\\u30e5\\u30fc\\u30b2\\u30fc\\u30e0\",\"english\":\"Haibara\\u2019s Teenage New Game+\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/143071\"}},{\"relationType\":\"ALTERNATIVE\",\"node\":{\"id\":167434,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Haibara-kun no Tsuyokute Seishun New Game\",\"native\":\"\\u7070\\u539f\\u304f\\u3093\\u306e\\u5f37\\u304f\\u3066\\u9752\\u6625\\u30cb\\u30e5\\u30fc\\u30b2\\u30fc\\u30e0\",\"english\":null},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/167434\"}}]}}},{\"id\":412612,\"episode\":7,\"airingAt\":1779116400,\"media\":{\"id\":197754,\"idMal\":62331,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"LIAR GAME\",\"native\":\"LIAR GAME\",\"english\":\"LIAR GAME\"},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2026,\"month\":4,\"day\":7},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"season\":\"SPRING\",\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Drama\",\"Psychological\"],\"synonyms\":[\" \\u30e9\\u30a4\\u30a2\\u30fc\\u30b2\\u30fc\\u30e0\",\"\\u0418\\u0433\\u0440\\u0430 \\u043b\\u0436\\u0435\\u0446\\u043e\\u0432\"],\"duration\":24,\"popularity\":29660,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"MANGA\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u30e9\\u30a4\\u30a2\\u30fc\\u30b2\\u30fc\\u30e0 #LIARGAME\",\"averageScore\":60,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/197754\",\"description\":\"Wishing she would live up to the ideal, Kanzaki Nao's father named her thusly for \\u201chonesty\\u201d. Nao has more than lived up to her father's wishes--even exceeding them and earning the label of \\\"a foolishly honest girl\\\". This makes Nao the least qualified candidate for the high stakes 'Liar Game', where winning requires deceiving the opponent out of their money and losing means receiving massive debt. However, that doesn't stop a box containing a hundred million yen in cash and a card informing her of her participation in the game from arriving at her doorstep, nor does it stop her from being promptly tricked out of the entire sum of money. Upon hearing that a genius swindler, responsible for the bankruptcy of a major corporation, is being released from jail, Nao goes to the swindler, Shinichi Akiyama, to enlist his help. With that, the two are drawn into the dark, greed-filled, and deceptive world of the Liar Game.\",\"bannerImage\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/banner\\/197754-cMWxeRdhYrFW.jpg\",\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx197754-Q5KqcUhIdypp.png\",\"color\":null},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"FIPOXj00ysQ\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/FIPOXj00ysQ\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.liargame-anime.com\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/219-EwrfceXsqIWg.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/liargame_anime\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Crunchyroll\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/5-AWN2pVlluCOO.png\",\"color\":\"#F88B24\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.crunchyroll.com\\/series\\/GT00371851\\/liar-game\"},{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.liargame-anime.com\\/en\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/219-EwrfceXsqIWg.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/liargame_en\"}],\"rankings\":[{\"rank\":83,\"type\":\"RATED\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":false},{\"rank\":42,\"type\":\"POPULAR\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":false},{\"rank\":20,\"type\":\"POPULAR\",\"season\":\"SPRING\",\"allTime\":false}],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":11,\"name\":\"MADHOUSE\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/11\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":31649,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"LIAR GAME\",\"native\":\"LIAR GAME\",\"english\":null},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/31649\"}}]}}},{\"id\":412660,\"episode\":7,\"airingAt\":1778774400,\"media\":{\"id\":210234,\"idMal\":63304,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Mamonogurai no Boukensha: Ore Dake Mamono wo Kuratte Tsuyoku Naru\",\"native\":\"\\u9b54\\u7269\\u55b0\\u3089\\u3044\\u306e\\u5192\\u967a\\u8005 ~\\u4ffa\\u3060\\u3051\\u9b54\\u7269\\u3092\\u55b0\\u3089\\u3063\\u3066\\u5f37\\u304f\\u306a\\u308b~\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2026,\"month\":4,\"day\":3},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"season\":\"SPRING\",\"format\":\"TV_SHORT\",\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Adventure\",\"Fantasy\"],\"synonyms\":[\"Monster Eater\"],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":5373,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"LIGHT_NOVEL\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u9b54\\u7269\\u55b0\\u3089\\u3044\\u306e\\u5192\\u967a\\u8005\",\"averageScore\":38,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/210234\",\"description\":\"Rudd\\u2019s a nobody-- just an E-Rank adventurer with a seemingly useless talent of status immunity. An outcast in a city obsessed with labyrinth crawling, he\\u2019s stuck scraping by as a \\u201cgrubby forager,\\u201d navigating guild politics and backstabbing adventurers just to survive. But when a betrayal leaves him for dead without any supplies or help, he does the unthinkable and consumes the flesh of fallen monsters...\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: WEBTOON)\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx210234-MZaMjdbBzEHz.jpg\",\"color\":\"#e4505d\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"tXZbVN3xc7U\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/tXZbVN3xc7U\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/animationid.com\\/mamonogurai\\/\"}],\"rankings\":[{\"rank\":11,\"type\":\"RATED\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":false},{\"