e\":77,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/171110\",\"description\":\"Anime adaptation of Part 3 of <i>Honzuki no Gekokujou<\\/i>.\\n<br><br>\\nFollowing a disastrous encounter with a noble, Myne finally resolves to say goodbye to her family and friends in the lower city, changing her name to \\u201cRozemyne\\u201d and beginning her new life as the adopted daughter of Ehrenfest\\u2019s archduke. However, her days as an archnoble in noble society are brutal, as she is put through rigorous etiquette and magic training on top of her duties as High Bishop and forewoman. It all proves too much for a weak little seven-year-old girl... Or it would have, had the High Priest not offered her the keys to the temple\\u2019s book room as a reward. If she could get her hands on those, she\\u2019d be able to read all sorts of precious books! Her name may have changed, but Rozemyne\\u2019s passion for books remains the same as she charges into a whole new world! The detailed setting expands as the printing industry grows in size. Here begins Part 3 of this biblio-fantasy for book lovers everywhere!\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: J-Novel Club) \",\"bannerImage\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/banner\\/171110-lgtmKokpevUM.jpg\",\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx171110-7zOdInS6DQNL.jpg\",\"color\":\"#5daee4\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"rtPF6rjrdSU\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/rtPF6rjrdSU\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/booklove-anime.jp\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/17-R0tMgOvwvhsS.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/twitter.com\\/anime_booklove\"},{\"site\":\"Crunchyroll\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/5-AWN2pVlluCOO.png\",\"color\":\"#F88B24\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.crunchyroll.com\\/series\\/G6793XKZY\\/ascendance-of-a-bookworm\"}],\"rankings\":[{\"rank\":24,\"type\":\"RATED\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":false},{\"rank\":45,\"type\":\"POPULAR\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":false},{\"rank\":12,\"type\":\"RATED\",\"season\":\"SPRING\",\"allTime\":false},{\"rank\":22,\"type\":\"POPULAR\",\"season\":\"SPRING\",\"allTime\":false}],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":858,\"name\":\"WIT STUDIO\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/858\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":110801,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Honzuki no Gekokujou: Shisho ni Naru Tame ni wa Shudan wo Erandeiraremasen Dai 3-bu - Ryoushu no Youjo\",\"native\":\"\\u672c\\u597d\\u304d\\u306e\\u4e0b\\u524b\\u4e0a~\\u53f8\\u66f8\\u306b\\u306a\\u308b\\u305f\\u3081\\u306b\\u306f\\u624b\\u6bb5\\u3092\\u9078\\u3093\\u3067\\u3044\\u3089\\u308c\\u307e\\u305b\\u3093~\\u7b2c\\u4e09\\u90e8\\u300c\\u9818\\u4e3b\\u306e\\u990a\\u5973\\u300d\",\"english\":\"Ascendance of a Bookworm: Part 3\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/110801\"}},{\"relationType\":\"PREQUEL\",\"node\":{\"id\":121176,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Honzuki no Gekokujou: Shisho ni Naru Tame ni wa Shudan wo Erandeiraremasen 3rd Season\",\"native\":\"\\u672c\\u597d\\u304d\\u306e\\u4e0b\\u524b\\u4e0a \\u53f8\\u66f8\\u306b\\u306a\\u308b\\u305f\\u3081\\u306b\\u306f\\u624b\\u6bb5\\u3092\\u9078\\u3093\\u3067\\u3044\\u3089\\u308c\\u307e\\u305b\\u3093 \\u7b2c3\\u671f\",\"english\":\"Ascendance of a Bookworm Season 3\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/121176\"}},{\"relationType\":\"ALTERNATIVE\",\"node\":{\"id\":110805,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Honzuki no Gekokujou: Shisho ni Naru Tame ni wa Shudan wo Erandeiraremasen Dai 3-bu - Ryouchi ni Hon wo Hirogeyou!\",\"native\":\"\\u672c\\u597d\\u304d\\u306e\\u4e0b\\u524b\\u4e0a~\\u53f8\\u66f8\\u306b\\u306a\\u308b\\u305f\\u3081\\u306b\\u306f\\u624b\\u6bb5\\u3092\\u9078\\u3093\\u3067\\u3044\\u3089\\u308c\\u307e\\u305b\\u3093~ \\u7b2c\\u4e09\\u90e8 \\u300c\\u9818\\u5730\\u306b\\u672c\\u3092\\u5e83\\u3052\\u3088\\u3046!\\u300d\",\"english\":\"Ascendance of a Bookworm ~I'll do anything to become a librarian!~ Part 3 Let's spread books through the duchy!\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/110805\"}}]}}},{\"id\":413256,\"episode\":6,\"airingAt\":1779033600,\"media\":{\"id\":202523,\"idMal\":62983,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Marika-chan no Koukando wa Bukkowareteiru\",\"native\":\"\\u8309\\u8389\\u82b1\\u3061\\u3083\\u3093\\u306e\\u597d\\u611f\\u5ea6\\u306f\\u3076\\u3063\\u58ca\\u308c\\u3066\\u3044\\u308b\",\"english\":\"Marika's Love Meter Malfunction\"},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2026,\"month\":4,\"day\":6},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"season\":\"SPRING\",\"format\":\"TV_SHORT\",\"genres\":[\"Comedy\",\"Drama\",\"Ecchi\",\"Romance\",\"Supernatural\"],\"synonyms\":[],\"duration\":6,\"popularity\":10349,\"episodes\":8,\"source\":\"MANGA\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u8309\\u8389\\u82b1\\u3061\\u3083\\u3093\\u306e\\u597d\\u611f\\u5ea6\\u306f\\u3076\\u3063\\u58ca\\u308c\\u3066\\u3044\\u308b\",\"averageScore\":49,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/202523\",\"description\":\"Confessing to my childhood friend Marika was impossible for someone as unpopular as me. So, I did what any desperate boy would do\\u2014I wished upon a shooting star! When I woke up, that dream had come true?! I could see a love meter for people, just like in a love simulation game. Once I realized this was real and not a dream I went straight to see Marika. Her love meter was so low it had broken and practically fallen all the way to hell! If she hated me so much why was she so nice?! Is this how she really felt or...?!\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: Coolmic)\\n<br><br>\\n<i>Note: Episode 1 received an advanced distribution on AnimeFesta on March 13th, 2026. The start date reflects 