 a fantasy world where monsters inhabit. All he has are non-combat skills such as \\\"Appraisal\\\"! From a hopeless situation, he is saved by encounters, and his all-powerful abilities blossom! An another world adventure tale of miraculous reversal cheats burst forth!\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: Alpha Manga)\\n<br><br>\\n<i>Note: Saikyou no Shokugyou wa Yuusha demo Kenja demo Naku Kanteishi (Kari) Rashii desu yo? was streamed a week in advance of the TV broadcast on dAnimestore, and ABEMA starting with episode 2. The first episode was released on April 2, 2026. Regular broadcasting began on April 4, 2026.<\\/i>\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx200769-8WkFkoFxc2fw.jpg\",\"color\":\"#5dbbf1\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"f3QbevP2CG0\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/f3QbevP2CG0\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/219-EwrfceXsqIWg.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/kanteishi_anime\"},{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/kanteishikari-anime.com\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Crunchyroll\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/5-AWN2pVlluCOO.png\",\"color\":\"#F88B24\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/crunchyroll.com\\/series\\/GT00371875\\/the-strongest-job-is-apparently-not-a-hero-or-a-sage-but-an-appraiser-provisional\"}],\"rankings\":[{\"rank\":26,\"type\":\"RATED\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":false},{\"rank\":12,\"type\":\"POPULAR\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":false}],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":6170,\"name\":\"Studio Flad\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/6170\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"ALTERNATIVE\",\"node\":{\"id\":99895,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Saikyou no Shokugyou wa Yuusha demo Kenja demo Naku Kanteishi