            "text": "{\"data\":{\"Page\":{\"pageInfo\":{\"hasNextPage\":false,\"total\":47},\"media\":[{\"id\":180812,\"idMal\":59730,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"A-Rank Party wo Ridatsu Shita Ore wa, Moto Oshiegotachi to Meikyuu Shinbu wo Mezasu.\",\"native\":\"A\\u30e9\\u30f3\\u30af\\u30d1\\u30fc\\u30c6\\u30a3\\u3092\\u96e2\\u8131\\u3057\\u305f\\u4ffa\\u306f\\u3001\\u5143\\u6559\\u3048\\u5b50\\u305f\\u3061\\u3068\\u8ff7\\u5bae\\u6df1\\u90e8\\u3092\\u76ee\\u6307\\u3059\\u3002\",\"english\":\"I Left My A-Rank Party to Help My Former Students Reach the Dungeon Depths!\"},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2025,\"month\":1,\"day\":12},\"endDate\":{\"year\":2025,\"month\":6,\"day\":29},\"status\":\"FINISHED\",\"season\":\"WINTER\",\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Adventure\",\"Comedy\",\"Fantasy\"],\"synonyms\":[\"After Leaving the A-Rank Party, I Aim for the Deep Part of the Labyrinth With My Former Students\",\"Aparida\",\"\\u041f\\u043e\\u043a\\u0438\\u043d\\u0443\\u0432 \\u0433\\u0440\\u0443\\u043f\\u043f\\u0443 \\u0410-\\u0440\\u0430\\u043d\\u0433\\u0430, \\u044f \\u043d\\u0430\\u043f\\u0440\\u0430\\u0432\\u0438\\u043b\\u0441\\u044f \\u0432\\u043c\\u0435\\u0441\\u0442\\u0435 \\u0441\\u043e \\u0441\\u0432\\u043e\\u0438\\u043c\\u0438 \\u0431\\u044b\\u0432\\u0448\\u0438\\u043c\\u0438 \\u0443\\u0447\\u0435\\u043d\\u0438\\u043a\\u0430\\u043c\\u0438 \\u0432 \\u0433\\u043b\\u0443\\u0431\\u0438\\u043d\\u044b \\u043b\\u0430\\u0431\\u0438\\u0440\\u0438\\u043d\\u0442\\u0430\",\"Aku Meninggalkan Regu Peringkat-A untuk Membantu Mantan Muridku\",\"Sau khi r\\u1eddi kh\\u1ecfi T\\u1ed5 \\u0111\\u1ed9i h\\u1ea1ng A, T\\u00f4i th\\u00e1m hi\\u1ec3m M\\u00ea cung c\\u00f9ng \\u0110\\u1ec7 t\\u1eed c\\u0169\"],\"duration\":23,\"popularity\":47544,\"episodes\":24,\"source\":\"LIGHT_NOVEL\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u30a8\\u30d1\\u30ea\\u30c0\",\"averageScore\":65,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/180812\",\"description\":\"Yuke, a red mage, angrily declares that he's leaving Thunder Pike, the A-rank party he's been with for five years, because he's fed up with being insulted and ridiculed by the other members.<br>\\n<br>\\nWhile searching for a new party, he runs into his former students Marina, Silk, and Rain, and decides to join their party, Clover. Encouraged by their admiration of him as their teacher, Yuke leads them in completing several quests that show off his own extraordinary magic and skills while bringing out the girls' abilities to their fullest.<br>\\n<br>\\nThen, through an \\\"adventure broadcast\\\" by an artifact known as Camelot, Clover becomes well-known throughout society. The party's dream is to conquer Achromatic Darkness, the most challenging dungeon of all, but as they take on other dungeons in hopes of eventually achieving that goal, they gradually become entangled in chaos that threatens the whole world...\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: Crunchyroll)\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx180812-162w2RBaqJzE.jpg\",\"color\":\"#5028a1\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"_5CVMsuuTiU\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/_5CVMsuuTiU\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/219-EwrfceXsqIWg.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/Aparidaofficial\"},{\"site\":\"TikTok\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/196-o2g5cLUG6k5V.png\",\"color\":\"#010101\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.tiktok.com\\/@aparida_official\"},{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/arank-party-ridatsu-official.com\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Crunchyroll\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/5-AWN2pVlluCOO.png\",\"color\":\"#F88B24\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.crunchyroll.com\\/series\\/GKEH2G004\\/i-left-my-a-rank-party-to-help-my-former-students-reach-the-dungeon-depths\"},{\"site\":\"Bilibili TV\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/119-NCwGvCjFADGQ.png\",\"color\":\"#00A1D6\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.bilibili.tv\\/en\\/media\\/2122082\"},{\"site\":\"YouTube\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/13-ZwR1Xwgtyrwa.png\",\"color\":\"#FF0000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/playlist?list=PLwLSw1_eDZl03q6rAPvEC-sRXeGiy6qMM\"}],\"rankings\":[{\"rank\":51,\"type\":\"POPULAR\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":false},{\"rank\":29,\"type\":\"RATED\",\"season\":\"WINTER\",\"allTime\":false},{\"rank\":14,\"type\":\"POPULAR\",\"season\":\"WINTER\",\"allTime\":false}],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":6116,\"name\":\"Bandai Namco Pictures\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/6116\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":139034,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"A-Rank Party wo Ridatsu Shita Ore wa, Moto Oshiegotachi to Meikyuu Shinbu wo Mezasu.\",\"native\":\"A\\u30e9\\u30f3\\u30af\\u30d1\\u30fc\\u30c6\\u30a3\\u3092\\u96e2\\u8131\\u3057\\u305f\\u4ffa\\u306f\\u3001\\u5143\\u6559\\u3048\\u5b50\\u305f\\u3061\\u3068\\u8ff7\\u5bae\\u6df1\\u90e8\\u3092\\u76ee\\u6307\\u3059\\u3002\",\"english\":null},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/139034\"}},{\"relationType\":\"ALTERNATIVE\",\"node\":{\"id\":139031,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"A-Rank Party wo Ridatsu Shita Ore wa, Moto Oshiegotachi to Meikyuu Shinbu wo Mezasu.\",\"native\":\"A\\u30e9\\u30f3\\u30af\\u30d1\\u30fc\\u30c6\\u30a3\\u3092\\u96e2\\u8131\\u3057\\u305f\\u4ffa\\u306f\\u3001\\u5143\\u6559\\u3048\\u5b50\\u305f\\u3061\\u3068\\u8ff7\\u5bae\\u6df1\\u90e8\\u3092\\u76ee\\u6307\\u3059\\u3002\",\"english\":\"I Left my A-Rank Party to Help My Former Students Reach the Dungeon Depths!\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/139031\"}},{\"relationType\":\"SEQUEL\",\"node\":{\"id\":195210,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"A-Rank Party wo Ridatsu Shita Ore wa, Moto Oshiegotachi to Meikyuu Shinbu wo Mezasu. 2nd Season\",\"native\":\"A\\u30e9\\u30f3\\u30af\\u30d1\\u30fc\\u30c6\\u30a3\\u3092\\u96e2\\u8131\\u3057\\u305f\\u4ffa\\u306f\\u3001\\u5143\\u6559\\u3048\\u5b50\\u305f\\u3061\\u3068\\u8ff7\\u5bae\\u6df1\\u90e8\\u3092\\u76ee\\u6307\\u3059\\u3002\\u7b2c2\\u671f\",\"english\":null},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/195210\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":172453,\"idMal\":57719,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Akuyaku Reijou Tensei Oji-san\",\"native\":\"\\u60aa\\u5f79\\u4ee4\\u5b22\\u8ee2\\u751f\\u304a\\u3058\\u3055\\u3093\",\"english\":\"From Bureaucrat to Villainess: Dad's Been Reincarnated!\"},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2025,\"month\":1,\"day\":10},\"endDate\":{\"year\":2025,\"month\":3,\"day\":28},\"status\":\"FINISHED\",\"season\":\"WINTER\",\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Comedy\",\"Fantasy\"],\"synonyms\":[\"The Middle-Aged Man that Reincarnated as a Villainess\",\" Om-om yang Bereinkarnasi Menjadi Putri Jahat\",\"\\u4e2d\\u5e74\\u5927\\u53d4\\u8f49\\u751f\\u53cd\\u6d3e\\u5343\\u91d1\"],\"duration\":24,\"popularity\":37333,\"episodes\":12,\"source\":\"MANGA\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u8ee2\\u751f\\u304a\\u3058\\u3055\\u3093\",\"averageScore\":73,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/172453\",\"description\":\"After a traffic accident, 52-year-old civil servant Kenzaburou Tondabayashi awakens to find he's become Grace Auvergne, a duke's daughter, and more importantly the villainess of an otome game. Not wanting to get in the way of the happy endings of the young characters around him, Grace sets out to play the role of the villain, but whether it's due to Kenzaburou's memories of being an affectionate parent getting in the way or not being able to remember those pesky foreign names properly, it ends up being a lot harder than it looks... \",\"bannerImage\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/bann