p with whom she sees as family.\\n<br><br>(Source: Crunchyroll)\",\"bannerImage\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/banner\\/175409-0IT62ftb3x6i.jpg\",\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx175409-ZYYEw0H6QypN.jpg\",\"color\":\"#5dbbf1\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"_lZ6iS-5Eig\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/_lZ6iS-5Eig\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/17-R0tMgOvwvhsS.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/twitter.com\\/koishima_pr\"},{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/koishima-pr.com\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Crunchyroll\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/5-AWN2pVlluCOO.png\",\"color\":\"#F88B24\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.crunchyroll.com\\/series\\/GJ0H7QGGM\\/anyway-im-falling-in-love-with-you\"},{\"site\":\"Bilibili TV\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/119-NCwGvCjFADGQ.png\",\"color\":\"#00A1D6\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.bilibili.tv\\/en\\/media\\/2124074\"},{\"site\":\"YouTube\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/13-ZwR1Xwgtyrwa.png\",\"color\":\"#FF0000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/playlist?list=PLxSscENEp7JhJgjNYZDJJFH1R3LAsfoq5\"}],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":6143,\"name\":\"TYPHOON GRAPHICS\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/6143\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":125855,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Douse, Koishite Shimaunda.\",\"native\":\"\\u3069\\u3046\\u305b\\u3001\\u604b\\u3057\\u3066\\u3057\\u307e\\u3046\\u3093\\u3060\\u3002\",\"english\":\"Anyway, I'm Falling in Love with You.\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/125855\"}},{\"relationT