uggle erupts among forces using monsters to seize control. In the town of Centvelt, Farmagia Ten and his friends band together against the despotic new ruler, Glaza. Ten, his friends, and their home-grown monsters must stay strong to defend their freedom. <br><br>\\n(Source: Crunchyroll)\",\"bannerImage\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/banner\\/178312-C5w25vbcLKmi.jpg\",\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx178312-iGhE7xvvCReS.jpg\",\"color\":\"#35aee4\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"MfSUq7AxHis\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/MfSUq7AxHis\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/anime-farmagia.marv.jp\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/219-EwrfceXsqIWg.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/FARMAGIA_PR\"},{\"site\":\"TikTok\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/196-o2g5cLUG6k5V.png\",\"color\":\"#010101\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.tiktok.com\\/@farmagia_official\"},{\"site\":\"Crunchyroll\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/5-AWN2pVlluCOO.png\",\"color\":\"#F88B24\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.crunchyroll.com\\/series\\/GP5HJ8447\\/farmagia\"},{\"site\":\"YouTube\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/13-ZwR1Xwgtyrwa.png\",\"color\":\"#FF0000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/playlist?list=PLxSscENEp7Jju9jZyfPvPCWVljX8k4yjY\"}],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":397,\"name\":\"Bridge\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/397\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":178548,\"idMal\":59144,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Fuguushoku [Kanteishi] ga Jitsu wa Saikyou Datta: Naraku de Kitaeta Saikyou no [Shingan] de Musou Suru\",\"native\":\"\\u4e0d\\u9047\\u8077\\u3010\\u9451\\u5b9a\\u58eb\\u3011\\u304c\\u5b9f\\u306f\\u6700\\u5f37\\u3060\\u3063\\u305f\\uff5e\\u5948\\u843d\\u3067\\u935b\\u3048\\u305f\\u6700\\u5f37\\u306e\\u3010\\u795e\\u773c\\u3011\\u3067\\u7121\\u53cc\\u3059\\u308b\\uff5e\",\"english\":\"Even Given the Worthless \\u201cAppraiser\\u201d Class, I\\u2019m Actually the Strongest\"},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2025,\"month\":1,\"day\":9},\"endDate\":{\"year\":2025,\"month\":3,\"day\":27},\"status\":\"FINISHED\",\"season\":\"WINTER\",\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Adventure\",\"Comedy\",\"Drama\",\"Fantasy\",\"Romance\"],\"synonyms\":[\"FuguKan\",\"\\u3075\\u3050\\u9451\",\"\\u0110en \\u0111\\u1ee7i khi c\\u00f3 ngh\\u1ec1 [Gi\\u00e1m \\u0111\\u1ecbnh s\\u0129] nh\\u01b0ng t\\u00f4i l\\u1ea1i l\\u00e0 ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi m\\u1ea1nh nh\\u1ea5t\"],\"duration\":24,\"popularity\":53463,\"episodes\":12,\"source\":\"LIGHT_NOVEL\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u3075\\u3050\\u9451 #\\u4e0d\\u9047\\u8077 #\\u9451\\u5b9a\\u58eb\",\"averageScore\":63,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/178548\",\"description\":\"Ein has been saddled with the job of \\\"Appraiser,\\\" the weakest and least fortunate of all the jobs one can be born with, as the only power it grants is the ability to appraise things.\\n\\nTreated cruelly by all and reduced to a litter collector by his peers, Ein has grown to hate himself and lives his days in spineless self-abasement. But when he meets Yuuri, the spirit of the World Tree, and her protector, Ursula the sage, Ein's fate takes a drastic turn.<br>\\n<br>\\nWith the gift of a Spirit Eye from Yuuri and the help of Ursula in learning how to use it, Ein grows stronger and stronger, until he's ready to take Yuuri on her long-desired journey to meet her World Tree's sisters. He goes on to overcome all sorts of challenges, armed with his natural kindness and his new-found courage. <br><br> (Source: 