306b\\u98df\\u3079\\u3089\\u308c\\u308b\\u3088\\u3046\\u306b\\u306a\\u3063\\u305f\\u4ef6\\u306b\\u3064\\u3044\\u3066~\",\"english\":\"Bogus Skill <<Fruitmaster>> ~About that time I became able to eat unlimited numbers of Skill Fruits (that kill you)~\"},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2025,\"month\":1,\"day\":1},\"endDate\":{\"year\":2025,\"month\":3,\"day\":19},\"status\":\"FINISHED\",\"season\":\"WINTER\",\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Adventure\",\"Fantasy\"],\"synonyms\":[\"Kinomi Master\"],\"duration\":25,\"popularity\":40023,\"episodes\":12,\"source\":\"OTHER\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u6728\\u306e\\u5b9f\\u30de\\u30b9\\u30bf\\u30fc\",\"averageScore\":57,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/178100\",\"description\":\"In a world where eating \\u201cSkill Fruits\\u201d grants special powers, Light, a boy who seeks to become the world\\u2019s greatest adventurer, obtains the <<Fruitmaster>> skill, a bogus skill specializing in fruit cultivation that is completely useless in combat.<br>\\n<br>\\nEating a second \\u201cSkill Fruit\\u201d results in death, so there are no do-overs. Meanwhile, his childhood friend Rena, who promised to become an adventurer with him, achieves S Rank in record time, and the gap between them widens.<br>\\n<br>\\nLight spends his days farming and training with a sword, but one day, he accidentally eats a second \\u201cSkill Fruit.\\u201d<br>\\n<br>\\n\\u201cWhy am I not dying?!\\u201d<br>\\n<br>\\nLight avoids certain death and learns the incredible true power of the <<Fruitmaster>> skill: he can eat as many \\u201cSkill Fruits\\u201d as he wants! His overpowered ability allows him to gain an ability every time he eats one, for an unlimited number of times!! The worst skill ever is actually the best skill ever!!!<br>\\n<br>\\n(Source: Crunchyroll)<br><br>\\n<i>Note: Each episode streamed 1 week early on ABEMA and Crunchyroll. The original TV broadcast started on January 7, 2025.<\\/i>\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx178100-GF4dKSrkdByJ.jpg\",\"color\":\"#50c9e4\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"0XT-ygHUdBw\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/0XT-ygHUdBw\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/kinomimaster.com\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/219-EwrfceXsqIWg.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/kinomimaster_PR\"},{\"site\":\"Crunchyroll\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/5-AWN2pVlluCOO.png\",\"color\":\"#F88B24\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.crunchyroll.com\\/series\\/GZJH3D801\\/bogus-skill-fruitmaster-about-that-time-i-became-able-to-eat-unlimited-numbers-of-skill-fruits-that-kill-you\"}],\"rankings\":[{\"rank\":59,\"type\":\"POPULAR\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":false},{\"rank\":15,\"type\":\"POPULAR\",\"season\":\"WINTER\",\"allTime\":false}],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":406,\"name\":\"Asahi Production\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/406\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"ALTERNATIVE\",\"node\":{\"id\":147551,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Hazure Skill \\\"Kinomi Master\\\": Skill no Mi (Tabetara Shinu) wo Mugen ni Taberareru You ni Natta Ken Nitsuite\",\"native\":\"\\u5916\\u308c\\u30b9\\u30ad\\u30eb\\u300a\\u6728\\u306e\\u5b9f\\u30de\\u30b9\\u30bf\\u30fc\\u300b ~\\u30b9\\u30ad\\u30eb\\u306e\\u5b9f(\\u98df\\u3079\\u305f\\u3089\\u6b7b\\u306c)\\u3092\\u7121\\u9650\\u306b\\u98df\\u3079\\u3089\\u308c\\u308b\\u3088\\u3046\\u306b\\u306a\\u3063\\u305f\\u4ef6\\u306b\\u3064\\u3044\\u3066~\",\"english\":null},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/147551\"}},{\"relationType\":\"ALTERNATIVE\",\"node\":{\"id\":138104,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Hazure Skill \\u00abKinomi Master\\u00bb: Skill no Mi (Tabetara Shinu) wo Mugen ni Taberareru You ni Natta Ken ni Tsuite\",\"native\":\"\\u5916\\u308c\\u30b9\\u30ad\\u30eb\\u300a\\u6728\\u306e\\u5b9f\\u30de\\u30b9\\u30bf\\u30fc\\u300b~\\u30b9\\u30ad\\u30eb\\u306e\\u5b9f(\\u98df\\u3079\\u305f\\u3089\\u6b7b\\u306c)\\u3092\\u7121\\u9650\\u306b\\u98df\\u3079\\u3089\\u308c\\u308b\\u3088\\u3046\\u306b\\u306a\\u3063\\u305f\\u4ef6\\u306b\\u3064\\u3044\\u3066~\",\"english\":\"Bogus Skill <<Fruitmaster>> ~About that time I became able to eat unlimited numbers of Skill Fruits (that kill you)~\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/138104\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":175443,\"idMal\":58271,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Honey Lemon Soda\",\"native\":\"\\u30cf\\u30cb\\u30fc\\u30ec\\u30e2\\u30f3\\u30bd\\u30fc\\u30c0\",\"english\":\"Honey Lemon Soda\"},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2025,\"month\":1,\"day\":9},\"endDate\":{\"year\":2025,\"month\":3,\"day\":27},\"status\":\"FINISHED\",\"season\":\"WINTER\",\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Romance\"],\"synonyms\":[],\"duration\":23,\"popularity\":56258,\"episodes\":12,\"source\":\"MANGA\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u30cf\\u30cb\\u30ec\\u30e2\\u30a2\\u30cb\\u30e1\",\"averageScore\":70,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/175443\",\"description\":\"In middle school, Uka Ishimori was nicknamed \\u201cStone.\\u201d\\n<br><br>\\nIn order to change herself, she enrolled in Hachimitsu High School, known for its culture of student liberty. Seated in at the desk next to her in the same class is Kai Miura, a coolly freewheeling boy with lemon-colored hair. In truth, Uka met Kai once in middle school, and decided to attend Hachimitsu based on a single word he said to her.To Uka, the popular Kai is a distant presence.\\n<br><br>\\nYet somehow, Kai starts to look after Uka. With Kai encouraging her, Uka gradually begins to fit in with her classmates\\u2026\\n<br><br>\\nBut...Uka\\u2019s world is gradually changing with Kai\\u2019s presence. \\u2014\\n<br><br>\\nNow, I am in the center of the endlessly spreading light.\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: Crunchyroll)\",\"bannerImage\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/banner\\/175443-g0uKvQh9uFe1.jpg\",\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx175443-QpmlCJt47Rp9.jpg\",\"color\":\"#e4d643\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"D1Uck5jSeXE\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/D1Uck5jSeXE\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/honeylemon-anime.com\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/219-EwrfceXsqIWg.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/honeylemon_an\"},{\"site\":\"TikTok\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/196-o2g5cLUG6k5V.png\",\"color\":\"#010101\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/tiktok.com\\/@honeylemon_an\"},{\"site\":\"Crunchyroll\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/5-AWN2pVlluCOO.png\",\"color\":\"#F88B24\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.crunchyroll.com\\/series\\/GMEHME77W\\/honey-lemon-soda\"},{\"site\":\"Bilibili TV\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/119-NCwGvCjFADGQ.png\",\"color\":\"#00A1D6\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.bilibili.tv\\/en\\/media\\/2122416\"},{\"site\":\"iQ\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/122-EPBJ2E0oPt5C.png\",\"color\":\"#00CC36\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.iq.com\\/album\\/1ner2uzs9o1\"}],\"rankings\":[{\"rank\":76,\"type\":\"RATED\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":false},{\"rank\":37,\"type\":\"POPULAR\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":false},{\"rank\":15,\"type\":\"RATED\",\"season\":\"WINTER\",\"allTime\":false},{\"rank\":8,\"type\":\"POPULAR\",\"season\":\"WINTER\",\"allTime\":false}],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\"