"duration\":23,\"popularity\":51479,\"episodes\":12,\"source\":\"LIGHT_NOVEL\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u3044\\u305a\\u308c\\u6700\\u5f37\\u306e\\u932c\\u91d1\\u8853\\u5e2b\",\"averageScore\":66,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/177506\",\"description\":\"Not even a hero, Takumi Iruma gets accidentally mixed in with a group of heroes chosen to be summoned to another world. As compensation for the mix-up, a goddess offers him the right to choose any skill he wishes for! Hoping for a peaceful and quiet life that has nothing to do with fighting or going into battle, he chooses a seemingly boring creation skill. However, it turns out \\\"alchemy\\\" is the most powerful skill that allows him to create everything from a holy sword to flying ships! This cheat skill he unexpectedly acquired turns him into a wealthy merchant and makes him undefeatable in battles! A heartwarming adventure story about (possibly) the most powerful alchemist in another world!<br>\\n<br>\\n(Source: AlphaPolis)\",\"bannerImage\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/banner\\/177506-LOunaLIruTgy.jpg\",\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx177506-in4J0GNzjOZL.jpg\",\"color\":\"#50bbfe\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"1_KLp1C_lAQ\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/1_KLp1C_lAQ\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/izuresaikyo-pr.com\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/17-R0tMgOvwvhsS.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/twitter.com\\/izuresaikyo_pr\"},{\"site\":\"Crunchyroll\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/5-AWN2pVlluCOO.png\",\"color\":\"#F88B24\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.crunchyroll.com\\/series\\/GQWH0M1P3\\/possibly-the-