othed since childhood and trained to be queen, she always hoped Prince Clarke would fall for someone else one day. So when he shows up at a ball with another woman, Lettie excitedly retreats to the countryside to start her new life\\u2014only for Clarke to appear, determined to win her heart.<br>\\n<br>\\n(Source: Crunchyroll)\",\"bannerImage\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/banner\\/170650-TQbt75Ro1oxw.jpg\",\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx170650-iVQC67atMVj3.png\",\"color\":\"#f17843\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"8i1CkseqtxQ\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/8i1CkseqtxQ\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/kisakikyouiku.com\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/219-EwrfceXsqIWg.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/kisakikyouiku\"},{\"site\":\"Crunchyroll\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/5-AWN2pVlluCOO.png\",\"color\":\"#F88B24\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.crunchyroll.com\\/series\\/G9VHN9QQ4\\/i-want-to-escape-from-princess-lessons\"},{\"site\":\"YouTube\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/13-ZwR1Xwgtyrwa.png\",\"color\":\"#FF0000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/playlist?list=PLwLSw1_eDZl1DlUDCVK433fUMRHqlggDM\"}],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":6125,\"name\":\"EMT Squared\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/6125\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":124127,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Kisaki Kyouiku kara Nigetai Watashi\",\"native\":\"\\u5983\\u6559\\u80b2\\u304b\\u3089\\u9003\\u3052\\u305f\\u3044\\u79c1\",\"english\":\"I Want to Escape from Princess Lessons\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/