ice.\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: Kodansha US)\",\"bannerImage\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/banner\\/179696-F96hLlVTFe3B.jpg\",\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx179696-1MAqXYVXT7IT.jpg\",\"color\":\"#ffe4ae\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"OWEzSDduLps\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/OWEzSDduLps\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/kaishani-sukinahito.com\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/219-EwrfceXsqIWg.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/kaishani_suki\"},{\"site\":\"Bilibili TV\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/119-NCwGvCjFADGQ.png\",\"color\":\"#00A1D6\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.bilibili.tv\\/en\\/media\\/2121960\"},{\"site\":\"YouTube\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/13-ZwR1Xwgtyrwa.png\",\"color\":\"#FF0000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/playlist?list=PLxSscENEp7JhCFHIPcW85-IUQ-q9T1eTl\"}],\"rankings\":[{\"rank\":54,\"type\":\"RATED\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":false},{\"rank\":41,\"type\":\"POPULAR\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":false},{\"rank\":9,\"type\":\"RATED\",\"season\":\"WINTER\",\"allTime\":false},{\"rank\":11,\"type\":\"POPULAR\",\"season\":\"WINTER\",\"allTime\":false}],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":6138,\"name\":\"BLADE\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/6138\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":116333,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Kono Kaisha ni Suki na Hito ga Imasu\",\"native\":\"\\u3053\\u306e\\u4f1a\\u793e\\u306b\\u597d\\u304d\\u306a\\u4eba\\u304c\\u3044\\u307e\\u3059\",\"english\":\"I Have a Crush at Work\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/116333\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":177552,\"idMal\":58853,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Kuroiwa Medaka ni Watashi no Kawaii ga Tsuujinai\",\"native\":\"\\u9ed2\\u5ca9\\u30e1\\u30c0\\u30ab\\u306b\\u79c1\\u306e\\u53ef\\u611b\\u3044\\u304c\\u901a\\u3058\\u306a\\u3044\",\"english\":\"Medaka Kuroiwa is Impervious to My Charms\"},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2025,\"month\":1,\"day\":7},\"endDate\":{\"year\":2025,\"month\":3,\"day\":25},\"status\":\"FINISHED\",\"season\":\"WINTER\",\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Comedy\",\"Ecchi\",\"Romance\"],\"synonyms\":[\"\\u30e1\\u30c0\\u304b\\u308f\",\"Medakawa\",\"\\u041c\\u044d\\u0434\\u0430\\u043a\\u0430 \\u041a\\u0443\\u0440\\u043e\\u0438\\u0432\\u0430 \\u043d\\u0435 \\u043f\\u043e\\u043d\\u0438\\u043c\\u0430\\u0435\\u0442 \\u043c\\u043e\\u0435\\u0439 \\u043f\\u0440\\u0438\\u0432\\u043b\\u0435\\u043a\\u0430\\u0442\\u0435\\u043b\\u044c\\u043d\\u043e\\u0441\\u0442\\u0438\"],\"duration\":24,\"popularity\":49994,\"episodes\":12,\"source\":\"MANGA\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u9ed2\\u5ca9\\u30e1\\u30c0\\u30ab\\u306b\\u79c1\\u306e\\u53ef\\u611b\\u3044\\u304c\\u901a\\u3058\\u306a\\u3044 #\\u30e1\\u30c0\\u304b\\u308f\",\"averageScore\":64,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/177552\",\"description\":\"Gorgeous from head to toe! The perfect figure! To Kawai Mona, winning hearts comes as naturally as breathing... but the arrival of Kuroiwa Medaka, a new transfer student who won't even give her a second look, turns her school life upside-down! She's lived her whole life being fawned over, so why is he any different? Mona tries everything she can think of to win Medaka over, even getting a bit extreme at times! This new rom-com starring a queen bee and a celibate boy is about to burst onto the scene!<br>\\n<br>\\n(Source: Crunchyroll)\",\"bannerImage\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/banner\\/177552-iLWNEFS7t8HM.jpg\",\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.