s of wielding magic come true after he unexpectedly passes away. He wakes as Sion, a young child in another world. He and his elder sister, Marie, are the children of a lower-class noble family who govern their region. After receiving conflicting messages from their father, Sion and Marie set out on an adventure to uncover the magic.<br>\\n<br>\\n(Source: Crunchyroll)\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx179297-qaG8nCqMpR3o.jpg\",\"color\":\"#e4935d\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"nmx4cLjyOS0\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/nmx4cLjyOS0\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/magicmaker-anime.com\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/219-EwrfceXsqIWg.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/magicmakeranime\"},{\"site\":\"Crunchyroll\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/5-AWN2pVlluCOO.png\",\"color\":\"#F88B24\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.crunchyroll.com\\/series\\/GP5HJ8417\\/magic-maker-how-to-make-magic-in-another-world\"}],\"rankings\":[{\"rank\":76,\"type\":\"POPULAR\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":false},{\"rank\":23,\"type\":\"RATED\",\"season\":\"WINTER\",\"allTime\":false},{\"rank\":23,\"type\":\"POPULAR\",\"season\":\"WINTER\",\"allTime\":false}],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":37,\"name\":\"Studio DEEN\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/37\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":155781,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Magic Maker: Isekai Mahou no Tsukurikata\",\"native\":\"\\u30de\\u30b8\\u30c3\\u30af\\u30fb\\u30e1\\u30a4\\u30ab\\u30fc\\u3000\\uff0d\\u7570\\u4e16\\u754c\\u9b54\\u6cd5\\u306e\\u4f5c\\u308a\\u65b9\\uff0d\",\"english\":\"Magic Maker: How to Create Magic in Another World\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/155781\"}},{\"relationType\":\"ALTERNATIVE\",\"node\":{\"id\":155780,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Magic Maker: Isekai Mahou no Tsukurikata\",\"native\":\"\\u30de\\u30b8\\u30c3\\u30af\\u30fb\\u30e1\\u30a4\\u30ab\\u30fc\\u3000\\uff0d\\u7570\\u4e16\\u754c\\u9b54\\u6cd5\\u306e\\u4f5c\\u308a\\u65b9\\uff0d\",\"english\":\"Magic Maker -How to Create Magic in Another World-\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/155780\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":170916,\"idMal\":57152,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Mahoutsukai no Yakusoku\",\"native\":\"\\u9b54\\u6cd5\\u4f7f\\u3044\\u306e\\u7d04\\u675f\",\"english\":\"Promise of Wizard\"},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2025,\"month\":1,\"day\":6},\"endDate\":{\"year\":2025,\"month\":3,\"day\":24},\"status\":\"FINISHED\",\"season\":\"WINTER\",\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Fantasy\"],\"synonyms\":[\"MahoYaku\",\"\\u307e\\u307b\\u3084\\u304f\",\"Mhyk\"],\"duration\":24,\"popularity\":12755,\"episodes\":12,\"source\":\"VIDEO_GAME\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u30a2\\u30cb\\u30e1\\u307e\\u307b\\u3084\\u304f\",\"averageScore\":52,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/170916\",\"description\":\"On a moonlit night, Akira Masaki finds herself in a magical world where wizards and humans coexist. Every year, they must face an enormous, deadly moon that attacks the planet. Their only hope lies with the Wizards of the Sage, appointed to fight the supernatural threat. But Akira soon discovers she wasn\\u2019t summoned by chance\\u2014she was chosen to lead them in battle.<br>\\n<br>\\n(Source: Crunchyroll)<br>\\n<br>\\n<i>Note: Animation project for Mahoutsukai no Yakusoku announced during the stream event \\\"Mahoutsukai no Yakusoku 4-Shuunen Kinen Tokuban: Mahoyaku 4-Shuunen Goukon\\\" held on Nov 12, 2023.\",\"bannerImage\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/banner\\/170916-sNl06nM8nSR3.jpg\",\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx170916-B6VKOdSOBccU.jpg\",\"color\":\"#e4a150\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"NJYgaw_ZgFs\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/NJYgaw_ZgFs\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/sh-anime.shochiku.co.jp\\/mahoyaku-anime\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/17-R0tMgOvwvhsS.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/twitter.com\\/mahoyaku_anime\"},{\"site\":\"Crunchyroll\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/5-AWN2pVlluCOO.png\",\"color\":\"#F88B24\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.crunchyroll.com\\/series\\/GXJHM3GG8\\/promise-of-wizard\"}],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":839,\"name\":\"LIDENFILMS\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/839\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"ALTERNATIVE\",\"node\":{\"id\":120626,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Mahoutsukai no Yakusoku\",\"native\":\"\\u9b54\\u6cd5\\u4f7f\\u3044\\u306e\\u7d04\\u675f\",\"english\":null},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/120626\"}},{\"relationType\":\"ALTERNATIVE\",\"node\":{\"id\":187652,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Mahoutsukai no Yakusoku COMIC\",\"native\":\"\\u9b54\\u6cd5\\u4f7f\\u3044\\u306e\\u7d04\\u675f COMIC\",\"english\":null},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/187652\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":162722,\"idMal\":54717,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Mahoutsukai Precure!! MIRAI DAYS\",\"native\":\"\\u9b54\\u6cd5\\u3064\\u304b\\u3044\\u30d7\\u30ea\\u30ad\\u30e5\\u30a2\\uff01\\uff01\\uff5eMIRAI DAYS\\uff5e\",\"english\":\"Witchy Precure!! ~MIRAI DAYS~\"},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2025,\"month\":1,\"day\":12},\"endDate\":{\"year\":2025,\"month\":3,\"day\":30},\"status\":\"FINISHED\",\"season\":\"WINTER\",\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Fantasy\",\"Mahou Shoujo\",\"Slice of Life\"],\"synonyms\":[\"Mahoutsukai Precure! 2\",\"MahoPuri 2 (\\u307e\\u307b\\u30d7\\u30ea2)\",\"Maho Girls Precure! 2 \",\"Witchy PreCure! 2\"],\"duration\":24,\"popularity\":2951,\"episodes\":12,\"source\":\"ORIGINAL\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u307e\\u307b\\u30d7\\u30ea2\",\"averageScore\":72,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/162722\",\"description\":\"One of the anime projects to commemorate the 20th anniversary of the Precure franchise, this will be a direct sequel of <i>Mahoutsukai Precure!<\\/i> aimed at grown-up fans of the anime. <br><br>\\n\\nMirai Asahina, a very curious 13-year-old girl with a love for mysterious things, met a young witch named Liko during spring break.\\nLed by miracles and magic, Mirai and Liko both transformed into the Legendary Witch \\\"Precures\\\"! \\nWorking together with Mirai's treasured teddy bear Mofurun and Ha-chan, a fairy born from the \\\"Linkle Smartbook\\\", they tried to repel the chaos that was encroaching upon the \\\"Magic World\\\" and \\\"Magicless World (Human World)\\\". However, that involved the separation of everyone.<br><br>\\n\\nAfter being miraculously reunited a few years later, Mirai and the others begin to take steps towards their futures in their respective worlds. Mirai is a college student in the Magicless World. Liko, who returned to the Magic World, is a teacher at the Magic School. Mofurun, as always, is at Mirai's side. Ha-chan exists far away, watching over the world.<br><br>\\n\\nHowever, a new disaster threatening the Magic and Magicless worlds has appeared...<br>\\nDue to signs of the coming disaster, Mirai and Liko reunite for the first time in months. While attempting to resist this mysterious enemy, they both come face to face with not only their past, but their future. With the magical words \\\"Cure Up RaPaPa!\\\", their exciting tale is once again set into motion!<br><br>\\n\\n(Source: Anime News Network, Crunchyroll, edited)\",\"bannerImage\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/banner\\/162722-x8FkO0OyAq2p.jpg\",\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx162722-w30E3QgBvG7H.jpg\",\"color\":\"#506be4\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"Mdr0WF5pPgI\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/Mdr0WF5pPgI\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.toei-anim.co.jp\\/tv\\/mahotsukai_precure2\"},{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/17-R0tMgOvwvhsS.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/twitter.com\\/precure_15th\"},{\"site\":\"Crunchyroll\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/5-AWN2pVlluCOO.png\",\"color\":\"#F88B24\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.crunchyroll.com\\/series\\/GZJH3D881\\/witchy-precure-mirai-days\"}],\"rankings\":[{\"rank\":67,\"type\":\"RATED\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":false},{\"rank\":13,\"type\":\"RATED\",\"season\":\"WINTER\",\"allTime\":false}],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":18,\"name\":\"Toei Animation\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/18\"},{\"id\":37,\"name\":\"Studio DEEN\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/37\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"PREQUEL\",\"node\":{\"id\":21506,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Mahoutsukai Precure!\",\"native\":\"\\u9b54\\u6cd5\\u3064\\u304b\\u3044\\u30d7\\u30ea\\u30ad\\u30e5\\u30a2\\uff01\",\"english\":\"Witchy Precure!\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/21506\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":173333,\"idMal\":57827,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Mashin Souzouden Wataru\",\"native\":\"\\u9b54\\u795e\\u5275\\u9020\\u4f1d\\u30ef\\u30bf\\u30eb\",\"english\":\"MASHIN CREATOR WATARU\"},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2025,\"month\":1,\"day\":12},\"endDate\":{\"