ognized as \\u201cnow\\u201d. That moment is lovely.<br><br>\\n\\n(Source: YouTube description)<br><br>\\n\\n<i>Note: Premiered at the 75th Berlin International Film Festival on February 15, 2025<\\/i>\\n\\n\",\"bannerImage\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/banner\\/206071-UTKIwlGsv9NN.jpg\",\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx206071-vzOH2H4EPxFn.jpg\",\"color\":\"#aebbe4\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"vohpCZh-Qcw\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/vohpCZh-Qcw\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[],\"rankings\":[{\"rank\":83,\"type\":\"POPULAR\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":false}],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":185898,\"idMal\":61038,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Galaxy Apartment\\u2605Cosmo Hills\",\"native\":\"\\u30ae\\u30e3\\u30e9\\u30af\\u30b7\\u30fc\\u30a2\\u30d1\\u30fc\\u30c8\\u2605\\u30b3\\u30b9\\u30e2\\u30d2\\u30eb\\u30ba\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2025,\"month\":3,\"day\":9},\"endDate\":{\"year\":2025,\"month\":3,\"day\":9},\"status\":\"FINISHED\",\"season\":\"WINTER\",\"format\":\"ONA\",\"genres\":[\"Drama\",\"Sci-Fi\"],\"synonyms\":[\"Young Animator Training Project 2025\",\"Anime no Tane 2025\"],\"duration\":10,\"popularity\":166,\"episodes\":1,\"source\":\"ORIGINAL\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":null,\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/185898\",\"description\":null,\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx185898-NnuSreMijs7g.png\",\"color\":\"#d6d61a\"},\"trailer\":null,\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/animenotane.jp\\/2025-02-20\\/\"}],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":35,\"name\":\"Sev