\":\"FINISHED\",\"season\":\"WINTER\",\"format\":\"ONA\",\"genres\":[\"Comedy\",\"Fantasy\",\"Slice of Life\"],\"synonyms\":[],\"duration\":5,\"popularity\":590,\"episodes\":10,\"source\":\"VIDEO_GAME\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":null,\"averageScore\":50,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/185648\",\"description\":\"Pikachu arrives on Monpok\\u00e9 Island. There, the iconic 'mon will meet Dedenne, Ludicolo and many others.<br><br>\\n(source: Crunchyroll, edited)\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx185648-NLFMKByKkNKx.png\",\"color\":\"#e4a150\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"vmERQ5ECuVM\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/vmERQ5ECuVM\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":866,\"name\":\"Fanworks\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/866\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"PARENT\",\"node\":{\"id\":158871,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Pocket Monsters (2023)\",\"native\":\"\\u30dd\\u30b1\\u30c3\\u30c8\\u30e2\\u30f3\\u30b9\\u30bf\\u30fc (2023)\",\"english\":\"Pok\\u00e9mon Horizons: The Series\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/158871\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":174654,\"idMal\":58082,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"NEET Kunoichi to Naze ka Dousei Hajimemashita\",\"native\":\"\\u30cb\\u30fc\\u30c8\\u304f\\u30ce\\u4e00\\u3068\\u306a\\u305c\\u304b\\u540c\\u68f2\\u306f\\u3058\\u3081\\u307e\\u3057\\u305f\",\"english\":\"I'm Living With a Otaku NEET Kunoichi?!\"},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2025,\"month\":1,\"day\":5},\"endDate\":{\"year\":2025,\"month\":3,\"day\":22},\"status\":\"FINISHED\",\"season\":\"WINTER\",\"format\":\"ONA\",\"genres\":[\"Comedy\",\"Ecchi\",\"Romance\"],\"synonyms\":[\"Somehow, I Started Living With a NEET Otaku Kunoichi\",\"NEET de Otaku na Kunoichi to Naze ka Dousei Hajimemashita\"],\"duration\":12,\"popularity\":25033,\"episodes\":24,\"source\":\"MANGA\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u30cb\\u30fc\\u30c8\\u304f\\u30ce\\u4e00\",\"averageScore\":57,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/174654\",\"description\":\"In order to protect an ordinary businessman, Tsukasa Atsumi, from demons, a genius kunoichi, Shizuri Ideura, signs a master-servant contract with him on the condition that she stays with him. Despite her cool appearance of defeating demons, Shizuri is an otaku NEET who spends all her time playing video games. While Shizuri is spoiled by Tsukasa and leads a lazy cohabitation life, the quirky Kunoichi gather together... A romantic comedy about living together with a genius Kunoichi who is an otaku and a NEET! <br>\\n<br>\\n\\n(Source: HIDIVE)\\n\",\"bannerImage\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/banner\\/174654-vQMxvimEmfpw.jpg\",\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx174654-J8OduNFjRpVY.jpg\",\"color\":\"#e45d86\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"1ce6WShs6S0\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/1ce6WShs6S0\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/neet-kunoichi.com\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/17-R0tMgOvwvhsS.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/twitter.com\\/neet_kunoichi\"},{\"site\":\"HIDIVE\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/20-3nWxygrjVM5A.png\",\"color\":\"#03AEEF\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.hidive.com\\/season\\/28115\"},{\"site\":\"YouTube\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/13-ZwR1Xwgtyrwa.png\",\"color\":\"#FF0000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/playlist?list=PLxSscENEp7Jjp3CF8ZGiZ74pZiesyTl6P\"},{\"site\":\"Bilibili TV\",