ndDate\":{\"year\":2025,\"month\":1,\"day\":5},\"status\":\"FINISHED\",\"season\":\"WINTER\",\"format\":\"SPECIAL\",\"genres\":[\"Comedy\",\"Romance\"],\"synonyms\":[],\"duration\":17,\"popularity\":2917,\"episodes\":1,\"source\":\"MANGA\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u732b\\u306b\\u306a\\u308a\\u305f\\u3044\\u7530\\u4e07\\u5ddd\\u304f\\u3093\",\"averageScore\":65,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/185261\",\"description\":\"For Tamagawa, volunteering at a cat caf\\u00e9 is the only relief from his stressful job. The manager tells him to, \\\"relax and learn to be spoiled\\\", but he doesn't know what that means until a new customer, Shindo Rai, comes to the caf\\u00e9 and tells Tamagawa he wants to keep him as a cat! Enter their strange, but fateful relationship. A pure-hearted and soothing romantic comedy.\\n<br><br>\\n(Kodansha, translated)\",\"bannerImage\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/banner\\/185261-ogjsaEtVKR2f.jpg\",\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx185261-hJehR0xUg9cf.jpg\",\"color\":\"#f19335\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"PpQSs0i5Qmk\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/PpQSs0i5Qmk\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":168920,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Neko ni Naritai Tamagawa-kun\",\"native\":\"\\u732b\\u306b\\u306a\\u308a\\u305f\\u3044\\u7530\\u4e07\\u5ddd\\u304f\\u3093\",\"english\":null},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/168920\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":177778,\"idMal\":58964,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Ninja Batman vs. Yakuza League\",\"native\":\"\\u30cb\\u30f3\\u30b8\\u30e3\\u30d0\\u30c3\\u30c8\\u30de\\u30f3\\u5bfe\\u30e4\\u30af\\u30b6\\u30ea\\u30fc\\u30b0\",\"english\":\"Batman Ninja vs. Yakuza League\"},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2025,\"month\":3,\"day\":21},\"endDate\":{\"year\":2025,\"month\":3,\"day\":21},\"status\":\"FINISHED\",\"season\":\"WINTER\",\"format\":\"MOVIE\",\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Sci-Fi\"],\"synonyms\":[\"Ninja Batman tai Yakuza League\",\"Batman Ninja vs. Liga da Yakuza\",\"Batman Ninja kontra Liga Yakuzy\",\"Batman Ninja vs. Yakuza League\"],\"duration\":89,\"popularity\":4436,\"episodes\":1,\"source\":\"OTHER\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u30cb\\u30f3\\u30b8\\u30e3\\u30d0\\u30c3\\u30c8\\u30de\\u30f3 #BatmanNinja\",\"averageScore\":68,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/177778\",\"description\":\"In this sequel to Batman Ninja, the Batman family has returned to the present to discover that Japan has disappeared, and a giant island - Hinomoto - is now in the sky over Gotham City. At the top sit the Yakuza, a group of superpowered individuals who reign without honor or humanity and look suspiciously like the Justice League. Now, it\\u2019s up to Batman and his allies to save Gotham!\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: Amazon Prime Video)\\n<br><br>\\n<i>Note: Release date reflects the release in Japan. The film was released in the US on March 18, 2025<\\/i>.\",\"bannerImage\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/banner\\/177778-R1k0WEVjyeoz.jpg\",\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx177778-LF9pwTXJRY0R.jpg\",\"color\":\"#bbe45d\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"RyX5AL1NwNQ\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/RyX5AL1NwNQ\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/wwws.warnerbros.co.jp\\/batman-ninja\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Amazon Prime Video\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/21-bDoNIomehkOx.png\",\"color\":\"#FF9900\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.amazon.com\\/dp\\/B0DX1X29CB\"}],\"rankings\":[{\"rank\":29,\"type\":\"RATED\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":false},{\"rank\":22,\"type\":\"POPULAR\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":false}],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":437,\"name\":\"Kamikaze Douga\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/437\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"PREQUEL\",\"node\":{\"id\":100248,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Ninja Batman\",\"native\":\"\\u30cb\\u30f3\\u30b8\\u30e3\\u30d0\\u30c3\\u30c8\\u30de\\u30f3\",\"english\":\"Batman Ninja\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/100248\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":192928,\"idMal\":61327,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Nomo no Kuni\",\"native\":\"\\u30ce\\u30e2\\u306e\\u56fd\",\"english\":\"The Land of NOMO\"},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2025,\"month\":3,\"day\":28},\"endDate\":{\"year\":2025,\"month\":3,\"day\":28},\"status\":\"FINISHED\",\"season\":\"WINTER\",\"format\":\"ONA\",\"genres\":[\"Adventure\",\"Fantasy\",\"Mystery\"],\"synonyms\":[],\"duration\":34,\"popularity\":551,\"episodes\":1,\"source\":\"ORIGINAL\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":null,\"averageScore\":60,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/192928\",\"description\":\"Once upon a time, there was a girl named \\u201cSora\\u201d. She loved to sing, but one day, something happened that made her scared to sing in front of others. As days passed, she forgot how to sing, and even how to laugh. Then, one day, she and her little brother \\u201cDaichi\\u201d stumbled upon a mysterious pond.<br><br>\\nAt a pond called \\u201cKagamiike\\u201d: Mirror Pond, Sora discovered a mystical butterfly glowing with aurora colors. As she watched it flutter freely, she suddenly felt a connection. The butterfly\\u2019s magical glow seemed to resonate with something deep inside her. Unable to resist, Sora reached out toward the butterfly. But she lost her balance and tumbled headfirst into the pond. Daichi, trying to help her, ended up falling in too...<br><br>\\n\\nBeyond the surface of the Mirror Pond, a world of wonder and mystery awaited. As Sora and Daichi stared in amazement, a quirky girl named \\u201cRococo\\u201d appeared before them. Before long, the three of them set off on an adventure through \\u201cThe Land of NOMO\\u201d. Along the way, Sora begins to face the many feelings she had kept hidden deep within her heart.<br><br>\\n\\n(Part of Panasonic Group Pavilion project for Expo 2025).\",\"bannerImage\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/banner\\/192928-wXHCIKra60al.jpg\",\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx192928-akbttQVo3Mdi.png\",\"color\":\"#bbd678\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"2puErJ6wnmU\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/2puErJ6wnmU\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/the-land-of-nomo.panasonic\\/en\\/about\\/\"},{\"site\":\"YouTube\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/13-ZwR1Xwgtyrwa.png\",\"color\":\"#FF0000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/watch?v=2puErJ6wnmU\"}],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":6251,\"name\":\"monofilmo\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/6251\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":187380,\"idMal\":60790,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"ONE PIECE: Original Episode\\/Luffy, Law\",\"native\":\"ONE PIECE \\u30aa\\u30ea\\u30b8\\u30ca\\u30eb\\u30a8\\u30d4\\u30bd\\u30fc\\u30c9\\uff0f\\u30eb\\u30d5\\u30a3\\u3001\\u30ed\\u30fc\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2025,\"month\":1,\"day\":19},\"endDate\":{\"year\":2025,\"month\":1,\"day\":19},\"status\":\"FINISHED\",\"season\":\"WINTER\",\"format\":\"SPECIAL\",\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Adventure\",\"Fantasy\"],\"synonyms\":[],\"duration\":5,\"popularity\":1101,\"episodes\":1,\"source\":\"ORIGINAL\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#