D MOON\",\"native\":\"\\u304a\\u3057\\u308a\\u305f\\u3093\\u3066\\u3044 \\u30b9\\u30bf\\u30fc\\u30fb\\u30a2\\u30f3\\u30c9\\u30fb\\u30e0\\u30fc\\u30f3\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2025,\"month\":3,\"day\":20},\"endDate\":{\"year\":2025,\"month\":3,\"day\":20},\"status\":\"FINISHED\",\"season\":\"WINTER\",\"format\":\"MOVIE\",\"genres\":[\"Comedy\",\"Mystery\"],\"synonyms\":[],\"duration\":76,\"popularity\":92,\"episodes\":1,\"source\":\"OTHER\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":null,\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/185643\",\"description\":\"Story begins when Koala asks Butt Detective to find a missing relative who disappeared from an idol contest. The case takes Butt Detective to Stardust Island, the site of the contest, and also the home of the international criminal organization Phantom Thief Academy, headed by Phantom Thief G. Here, the organization advances its secret conspiracy, codenamed the Dark Age Plan. Butt Detective enters Stardust Island under the guise of an idol. At the same time, he joins forces with Phantom Thief U, who is out to steal back the valuable Moonlight Stone from Phantom Thief G. The story will also reveal more about Brown's past.\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: Anime News Network, edited)\\n\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/medium\\/b185643-GdoqcxGGXqq5.png\",\"color\":\"#f1d628\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"B1aHxqkJNXs\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/B1aHxqkJNXs\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/oshiri-movie.com\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/17-R0tMgOvwvhsS.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/twitter.com\\/o_tantei\"},{\"site\":\"Instagram\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/48-VFlxaXGaNqXk.png\",\"color\":\"#833AB4\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.instagram.com\\/oshiri_tantei_movie\\/\"}],\"rankings\":[{\"rank\":78,\"type\":\"POPULAR\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":false}],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":18,\"name\":\"Toei Animation\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/18\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"PARENT\",\"node\":{\"id\":100790,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Oshiri Tantei\",\"native\":\"\\u304a\\u3057\\u308a\\u305f\\u3093\\u3066\\u3044\",\"english\":null},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/100790\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":187236,\"idMal\":60987,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Princess Connect! Michibiki no Hatsuhana: Fiore Storia\",\"native\":\"\\u30d7\\u30ea\\u30f3\\u30bb\\u30b9\\u30b3\\u30cd\\u30af\\u30c8\\uff01 \\u5c0e\\u304d\\u306e\\u521d\\u82b1\\u3000- Fiore Storia -\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2025,\"month\":2,\"day\":28},\"endDate\":{\"year\":2025,\"month\":2,\"day\":28},\"status\":\"FINISHED\",\"season\":\"WINTER\",\"format\":\"ONA\",\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Adventure\",\"Comedy\",\"Fantasy\"],\"synonyms\":[],\"duration\":26,\"popularity\":1629,\"episodes\":1,\"source\":\"VIDEO_GAME\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u30d7\\u30ea\\u30b3\\u30cdR\",\"averageScore\":63,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/187236\",\"description\":\"In the 2030s, VR technology spread around the world with the arrival of the VR-based network device \\u2018mimi\\u2019.<br>\\nOne of the most popular of these was the VR online game \\u2018Legends of Astrum\\u2019.\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: Cygames, translated)\\n<br><br>\\n<i>Note: Originally was showcased during the 7th anniversary live stream of the game Princess Connect! Re:Dive on February 9, 2025. A complete version has been released later with added scenes on February 28, 2025.<\\/i>\",\"bannerImage\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/banner\\/187236-emuCTOCda6cp.jpg\",\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx187236-tFSyyAliXxLH.jpg\",\"color\":\"#f1ae43\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"lDxF3SSvwhc\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/lDxF3SSvwhc\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/17-R0tMgOvwvhsS.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/priconne_redive\"},{\"site\":\"YouTube\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/13-ZwR1Xwgtyrwa.png\",\"color\":\"#FF0000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/watch?v=lDxF3SSvwhc\"}],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":6290,\"name\":\"G-angle\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/6290\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"PARENT\",\"node\":{\"id\":122808,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Princess Connect! Re:Dive Season 2\",\"native\":\"\\u30d7\\u30ea\\u30f3\\u30bb\\u30b9\\u30b3\\u30cd\\u30af\\u30c8\\uff01Re:Dive Season 2\",\"english\":\"Princess Connect! Re:Dive Season 2\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/122808\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":179878,\"idMal\":59419,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Project Sekai: Kowareta SEKAI to Utaenai MIKU\",\"native\":\"\\u30d7\\u30ed\\u30b8\\u30a7\\u30af\\u30c8\\u30bb\\u30ab\\u30a4 \\u58ca\\u308c\\u305f\\u30bb\\u30ab\\u30a4\\u3068\\u6b4c\\u3048\\u306a\\u3044\\u30df\\u30af\",\"english\":\"COLORFUL STAGE! The Movie: A Miku Who Can't Sing\"},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2025,\"month\":1,\"day\":17},\"endDate\":{\"year\":2025,\"month\":1,\"day\":17},\"status\":\"FINISHED\",\"season\":\"WINTER\",\"format\":\"MOVIE\",\"genres\":[\"Drama\",\"Music\"],\"synonyms\":[\"Project Sekai Movie\",\"\\u5287\\u5834\\u7248 \\u30d7\\u30ed\\u30bb\\u30ab\",\"Gekijouban Proseka\",\"Colorful Stage La Pel\\u00edcula: Miku no puede cantar\",\"Colorful Stage! \\u0e40\\u0e14\\u0e2d\\u0e30\\u0e21\\u0e39\\u0e1f\\u0e27\\u0e35\\u0e48: \\u0e21\\u0e34\\u0e01\\u0e38\\u0e17\\u0e35\\u0e48\\u0e44\\u0e23\\u0e49\\u0e40\\u0e2a\\u0e35\\u0e22\\u0e07\\u0e40\\u0e1e\\u0e25\\u0e07\",\"Colorful Stage! O Filme: Uma Miku Que N\\u00e3o Sabe Cantar\"],\"duration\":105,\"popularity\":20151,\"episodes\":1,\"source\":\"VIDEO_GAME\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u5287\\u5834\\u7248\\u30d7\\u30ed\\u30bb\\u30ab\",\"averageScore\":76,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/179878\",\"description\":\"Set in modern day Shibuya, Ichika Hoshino, a high school girl and street musician, encounters an unknown version of Hatsune Miku after hearing a Miku song that she'd never heard before in a CD store. Ichika learns that this version of Miku is having trouble reaching people with her songs, so together they team up to try to touch the hearts of their audience through music.<br><br>\\n\\n(Source: Crunchyroll News, edited)\",\"bannerImage\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/banner\\/179878-4z2dGmOfLe1a.jpg\",\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx179878-jG5GTXhe2vou.jpg\",\"color\":\"#43a1f1\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"e1TrAhX3qnY\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/e1TrAhX3qnY\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/219-EwrfceXsqIWg.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/pjsekai_movie\"},{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/sh-anime.shochiku.co.jp\\/pjsekai-movie\\/\"}],\"rankings\":[{\"rank\":268,\"type\":\"RATED\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":true},{\"rank\":13,\"type\":\"RATED\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":false},{\"rank\":9,\"type\":\"POPULAR\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":false}],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":132,\"name\":\"