            "text": "{\"data\":{\"Page\":{\"pageInfo\":{\"hasNextPage\":false,\"total\":20},\"media\":[{\"id\":164172,\"idMal\":55071,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Amagami-san Chi no Enmusubi\",\"native\":\"\\u7518\\u795e\\u3055\\u3093\\u3061\\u306e\\u7e01\\u7d50\\u3073\",\"english\":\"Tying the Knot with an Amagami Sister\"},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2024,\"month\":10,\"day\":2},\"endDate\":{\"year\":2025,\"month\":3,\"day\":26},\"status\":\"FINISHED\",\"season\":\"FALL\",\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Comedy\",\"Drama\",\"Ecchi\",\"Romance\",\"Supernatural\"],\"synonyms\":[\"Matchmaking of the Amagami Household\",\"\\u0e14\\u0e49\\u0e32\\u0e22\\u0e41\\u0e14\\u0e07\\u0e1c\\u0e39\\u0e01\\u0e23\\u0e31\\u0e01\\u0e1a\\u0e49\\u0e32\\u0e19\\u0e2d\\u0e32\\u0e21\\u0e32\\u0e01\\u0e32\\u0e21\\u0e34\",\"\\u7d50\\u7de3\\u7518\\u795e\\u795e\\u793e\",\"\\u7518\\u795e\\u5bb6\\u7684\\u8fde\\u7406\\u679d\",\"\\u0631\\u0628\\u0637 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0639\\u0642\\u062f \\u0645\\u0639 \\u0623\\u062e\\u0648\\u0627\\u062a \\u0623\\u0645\\u0627\\u063a\\u0627\\u0645\\u064a\"],\"duration\":24,\"popularity\":45244,\"episodes\":24,\"source\":\"MANGA\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u7518\\u795e\\u3055\\u3093\\u3061\\u306e\\u7e01\\u7d50\\u3073 #amagami_anime\",\"averageScore\":73,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/164172\",\"description\":\"Uryuu Kamihate is a high school student striving to enter Kyoto University\\u2019s medical school. After being raised at an orphanage, Uryuu is taken in by the chief priest at Amagami Shrine, where he begins to live as a freeloader\\u2014and to cohabit with Yae, Yuna, and Asahi, the three beautiful shrine maiden sisters! What\\u2019s more, the condition he must meet in order to live at the shrine for free is to marry into the family and inherit the shrine! How will Uryuu overcome his marriage meetings with the three sisters as well as the many challenges that Amagami Shrine faces? So begins a miraculous rom-com about living under the same roof with three shrine maidens!<br>\\n<br>\\n(Source: Crunchyroll, edited)\",\"bannerImage\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/banner\\/164172-ceuofxXerReI.jpg\",\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx164172-GY2aqItIuqtR.jpg\",\"color\":\"#e47850\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"pwb10_z0zvw\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/pwb10_z0zvw\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/17-R0tMgOvwvhsS.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/twitter.com\\/amagami_anime\"},{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/amagami-anime.com\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Crunchyroll\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/5-AWN2pVlluCOO.png\",\"color\":\"#F88B24\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.crunchyroll.com\\/series\\/G24H1NWJ0\\/tying-the-knot-with-an-amagami-sister\"},{\"site\":\"Bilibili TV\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/119-NCwGvCjFADGQ.png\",\"color\":\"#00A1D6\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.bilibili.tv\\/en\\/media\\/2116670\"}],\"rankings\":[{\"rank\":66,\"type\":\"RATED\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":false},{\"rank\":83,\"type\":\"POPULAR\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":false},{\"rank\":18,\"type\":\"RATED\",\"season\":\"FALL\",\"allTime\":false},{\"rank\":17,\"type\":\"POPULAR\",\"season\":\"FALL\",\"allTime\":false}],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":6289,\"name\":\"Drive\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/6289\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":128160,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Amagami-san Chi no Enmusubi\",\"native\":\"\\u7518\\u795e\\u3055\\u3093\\u3061\\u306e\\u7e01\\u7d50\\u3073\",\"english\":\"Tying the Knot with an Amagami Sister\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/128160\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":170942,\"idMal\":57181,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Ao no Hako\",\"native\":\"\\u30a2\\u30aa\\u306e\\u30cf\\u30b3\",\"english\":\"Blue Box\"},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2024,\"month\":10,\"day\":3},\"endDate\":{\"year\":2025,\"month\":3,\"day\":20},\"status\":\"FINISHED\",\"season\":\"FALL\",\"format\":\"ONA\",\"genres\":[\"Romance\",\"Slice of Life\",\"Sports\"],\"synonyms\":[\"\\u0627\\u0644\\u0635\\u0646\\u062f\\u0648\\u0642 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0623\\u0632\\u0631\\u0642\",\"\\u9752\\u4e4b\\u7bb1\",\"\\ud478\\ub978 \\uc0c1\\uc790\",\"La caja azul\",\"\\u0e01\\u0e25\\u0e48\\u0e2d\\u0e07\\u0e23\\u0e31\\u0e01\\u0e27\\u0e31\\u0e22\\u0e43\\u0e2a\",\"Niebieskie pude\\u0142ko\"],\"duration\":24,\"popularity\":129432,\"episodes\":25,\"source\":\"MANGA\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u30a2\\u30cb\\u30cf\\u30b3\",\"averageScore\":81,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/170942\",\"description\":\"<i>Do these sports-crossed lovers have a chance?<\\/i>\\n<br><br>\\nTaiki Inomata loves badminton, but he has a long way to go before he can reach nationals. When Taiki sees upperclassman Chinatsu Kano practicing her heart out on the girls\\u2019 basketball team, he falls for her hard. After an unexpected turn of events brings the two closer together, sports might not be the first thing on their minds anymore!<br><br>(Source: TMS Anime)<br><br>\\n<i>Note: The series streamed a week in advance on Netflix Japan starting with episode 2 released alongside episode 1.<\\/i>\",\"bannerImage\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/banner\\/170942-v2GO5YNO0Q5I.jpg\",\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx170942-KKcLfQzV57nG.jpg\",\"color\":\"#5daee4\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"uvvYMBLY-w4\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/uvvYMBLY-w4\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/17-R0tMgOvwvhsS.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/twitter.com\\/aonohako_PR\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/aonohako-anime.com\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Netflix\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/10-rVGPom8RCiwH.png\",\"color\":\"#E50914\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.netflix.com\\/title\\/81663323\"}],\"rankings\":[{\"rank\":36,\"type\":\"RATED\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":true},{\"rank\":14,\"type\":\"POPULAR\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":true},{\"rank\":6,\"type\":\"RATED\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":false},{\"rank\":1,\"type\":\"POPULAR\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":false}],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":94,\"name\":\"Telecom Animation Film\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/94\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":132182,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Ao no Hako\",\"native\":\"\\u30a2\\u30aa\\u306e\\u30cf\\u30b3\",\"english\":\"Blue Box\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/132182\"}},{\"relationType\":\"OTHER\",\"node\":{\"id\":184816,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Teenage Blue\",\"native\":\"\\u30c6\\u30a3\\u30fc\\u30f3\\u30a8\\u30a4\\u30b8\\u30d6\\u30eb\\u30fc\",\"english\":null},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/184816\"}},{\"relationType\":\"SEQUEL\",\"node\":{\"id\":189123,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Ao no Hako Season 2\",\"native\":\"\\u30a2\\u30aa\\u306e\\u30cf\\u30b3 Season\\uff12\",\"english\":\"Blue Box Season 2\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/189123\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":169258,\"idMal\":56647,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Ao no Miburo\",\"native\":\"\\u9752\\u306e\\u30df\\u30d6\\u30ed\",\"english\":\"Blue Miburo\"},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2024,\"month\":10,\"day\":19},\"endDate\":{\"year\":2025,\"month\":3,\"day\":29},\"status\":\"FINISHED\",\"season\":\"FALL\",\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Drama\"],\"synonyms\":[\"The Blue Wolves of Mibu\"],\"duration\":24,\"popularity\":14780,\"episodes\":24,\"source\":\"MANGA\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u9752\\u306e\\u30df\\u30d6\\u30ed\",\"averageScore\":64,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/169258\",\"description\":\"It's 1863, the twilight of the shogunate, and Japan is on the cusp of monumental change. The streets of the nation's capital are soaked in blood as political upheaval and rising tensions between masterless, wandering ronin and government samurai set the stage for one of the most turbulent times in Japan's history. Young orphan Nio is no stranger to the harsh realities of the world, and yet he can't help but cling to his burning passion for justice and desire to change the world for the better.<br><br>\\n\\nOne day, he crosses paths with two men who will become central figures of the coming revolution: Hijikata Toshizo and Okita Souji, two of the founding members of a group of hated ronin known as the Miburo\\u2014who would later become known as the Shinsengumi. Inspired by the efforts of the so-called \\\"Blues Wolves of Mibu,\\\" Nio decides to join the ranks to help carve a path to the world he wishes to see. But with new betrayals and reversals every day, will Nio be able to stay true to his conscience?<br><br>\\n\\n(Source: Kodansha USA, edited)\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx169258-kj8qoomfAKsB.jpg\",\"color\":\"#50aee4\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"Os9UR-v24UU\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/Os9UR-v24UU\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/17-R0tMgOvwvhsS.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/twitter.com\\/miburo_anime\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/miburoanime.com\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Crunchyroll\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/5-AWN2pVlluCOO.png\",\"color\":\"#F88B24\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.crunchyroll.com\\/series\\/GXJHM3GP8\\/blue-miburo\"},{\"site\":\"OceanVeil\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/249-CFCxdC7MiNX3.png\",\"color\":\"#00D0D3\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/oceanveil.net\\/anime_titles\\/322\"}],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":6288,\"name\":\"Maho Film\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/6288\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":138883,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Ao no Miburo\",\"native\":\"\\u9752\\u306e\\u30df\\u30d6\\u30ed\",\"english\":\"The Blue Wolves of Mibu\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/138883\"}},{\"relationType\":\"SEQUEL\",\"node\":{\"id\":189258,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Ao no Miburo: Serizawa Ansatsu-hen\",\"native\":\"\\u9752\\u306e\\u30df\\u30d6\\u30ed \\u82b9\\u6ca2\\u6697\\u6bba\\u7de8\",\"english\":\"Blue Miburo Season 2\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/189258\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":151514,\"idMal\":52215,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Chi. Chikyuu no Undou ni Tsuite\",\"native\":\"\\u30c1\\u3002-\\u5730\\u7403\\u306e\\u904b\\u52d5\\u306b\\u3064\\u3044\\u3066-\",\"english\":\"Orb: On the Movements of the Earth\"},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2024,\"month\":10,\"day\":5},\"endDate\":{\"year\":2025,\"month\":3,\"day\":15},\"status\":\"FINISHED\",\"season\":\"FALL\",\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Drama\"],\"synonyms\":[\"Chi: About the Movement of the Earth\",\"\\u0e2a\\u0e38\\u0e23\\u0e34\\u0e22\\u0e30\\u0e1b\\u0e23\\u0e32\\u0e0a\\u0e0d\\u0e4c \\u0e17\\u0e24\\u0e29\\u0e0e\\u0e35\\u0e2a\\u0e35\\u0e40\\u0e25\\u0e37\\u0e2d\\u0e14\",\"O ruchach Ziemi\",\"Du mouvement de la Terre\",\"Tierra, sangre, conocimiento: Sobre el movimiento de la Tierra\",\"Ketzer - T\\u00f6dliches Wissen \\u00fcber die Bewegung der Erde\",\"\\u05e2\\u05dc \\u05ea\\u05e0\\u05d5\\u05e2\\u05ea \\u05db\\u05d3\\u05d5\\u05e8 \\u05d4\\u05d0\\u05e8\\u05e5\",\"Il movimento della Terra\",\"\\u041f\\u0440\\u043e \\u0440\\u0443\\u0445 \\u0417\\u0435\\u043c\\u043b\\u0456\"],\"duration\":25,\"popularity\":108812,\"episodes\":25,\"source\":\"MANGA\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u30a2\\u30cb\\u30e1\\u306e\\u30c1\",\"averageScore\":86,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/151514\",\"description\":\"The setting is 15th-century Europe. It was a time when heretical ideas lead those to who possessed such a mindset to being burned at the stake for their beliefs.<br><br>\\n\\nThe protagonist, Rafa\\u0142, a child prodigy, is expected to major in theology, the most important subject at the time, at the university where he plans to skip a grade. One day, however, he comes across a mysterious man, and is now studying a possible \\\"truth\\\" in the midst of heretical thought!<br><br>\\n(Source: Shogakukan, translated)\",\"bannerImage\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/banner\\/151514-mwWSGTynCLkl.jpg\",\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx151514-Y0d82Ah2ZOHX.jpg\",\"color\":null},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"EBosY5GPpfw\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/EBosY5GPpfw\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/219-EwrfceXsqIWg.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/chikyu_chi\"},{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/anime-chi.jp\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Netflix\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/10-rVGPom8RCiwH.png\",\"color\":\"#E50914\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.netflix.com\\/title\\/81765022\"}],\"rankings\":[