":2025,\"month\":3,\"day\":30},\"status\":\"FINISHED\",\"season\":\"FALL\",\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Adventure\",\"Comedy\",\"Drama\",\"Fantasy\"],\"synonyms\":[],\"duration\":24,\"popularity\":13498,\"episodes\":21,\"source\":\"MANGA\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#ONEPIECE\",\"averageScore\":77,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/183423\",\"description\":\"A condensed and remastered reairing of the <i>Fish-Man Island Saga<\\/i> (episodes 517-574) from <i>ONE PIECE<\\/i>, with updated visuals, a new ending song, and brand-new episode previews.<br><br>\\n\\nThe Straw Hats reunite at Sabaody! The promised day has arrived. The Straw Hats have made it back to Sabaody Archipelago after two arduous years of separation. In the very same place where they once lost to Pacifista, the Straw Hats have proven themselves to be stronger and ready to begin their journey to the New World. With the Thousand Sunny now equipped to travel underwater, the next stop is the Fish-Man Island. \\u201cOne Piece Log: Fish-Man Island Saga\\u201d is a special edited version of the original arc from \\u201cOne Piece\\u201d, in an abridged 21-episode story with an enhanced contemporary visual look.<br><br>\\n(Source: Crunchyroll)\",\"bannerImage\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/banner\\/183423-kYnannPuKynK.jpg\",\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx183423-6Iiu194UDxD0.jpg\",\"color\":\"#f1bb35\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"RSM5Heu-lKw\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/RSM5Heu-lKw\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/one-piece.com\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Crunchyroll\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/5-AWN2pVlluCOO.png\",\"color\":\"#F88B24\",\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/www.crunchyroll.com\\/one-piece\"},{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/17-R0tMgOvwvhsS.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/twitter.com\\/Eiichiro_Staff\\/\"}],\"rankings\":[{\"rank\":36,\"type\":\"RATED\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":false},{\"rank\":9,\"type\":\"RATED\",\"season\":\"FALL\",\"allTime\":false}],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":18,\"name\":\"Toei Animation\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/18\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":30013,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"ONE PIECE\",\"native\":\"ONE PIECE\",\"english\":\"One Piece\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/30013\"}},{\"relationType\":\"PARENT\",\"node\":{\"id\":21,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"ONE PIECE\",\"native\":\"ONE PIECE\",\"english\":\"ONE PIECE\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/21\"}},{\"relationType\":\"PREQUEL\",\"node\":{\"id\":182469,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"ONE PIECE FAN LETTER\",\"native\":\"ONE PIECE FAN LETTER\",\"english\":\"ONE PIECE FAN LETTER\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/182469\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":179292,\"idMal\":59512,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Punirunes Puni 2\",\"native\":\"\\u3077\\u306b\\u308b\\u3093\\u305a \\u3077\\u306b\\uff12\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2024,\"month\":10,\"day\":6},\"endDate\":{\"year\":2025,\"month\":3,\"day\":30},\"status\":\"FINISHED\",\"season\":\"FALL\",\"format\":\"TV_SHORT\",\"genres\":[\"Slice of Life\"],\"synonyms\":[],\"duration\":12,\"popularity\":192,\"episodes\":25,\"source\":\"VIDEO_GAME\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u3077\\u306b\\u308b\\u3093\\u305a\",\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/179292\",\"description\":\"Second season of <i>Punirunes<\\/i>.\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx179292-j