OST CONCERT : missing Songs\"},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2026,\"month\":4,\"day\":6},\"endDate\":{\"year\":2026,\"month\":6,\"day\":29},\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"season\":\"SPRING\",\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Music\",\"Supernatural\"],\"synonyms\":[\"\\u0e42\\u0e01\\u0e2a\\u0e15\\u0e4c\\u0e04\\u0e2d\\u0e19\\u0e40\\u0e2a\\u0e34\\u0e23\\u0e4c\\u0e15 : \\u0e1a\\u0e17\\u0e40\\u0e1e\\u0e25\\u0e07\\u0e17\\u0e35\\u0e48\\u0e2b\\u0e32\\u0e22\\u0e44\\u0e1b\"],\"duration\":24,\"popularity\":3319,\"episodes\":12,\"source\":\"OTHER\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#GHOSTCONCERT\",\"averageScore\":50,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/201090\",\"description\":\"The year is 2045, in a world where songs have been banned. Instead of humans playing instruments and creating music, a music app titled \\\"MiucS\\\" is in charge of these things. High school student Seria goes out with her friends one day, but she happens to hear someone singing, which is supposed to be prohibited. What she finds is a lone ghost, a \\\"Great Ghost\\\" who has appeared from outside this world. Now Seria must decide whether to stay silent or risk everything to bring music back to the world.\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: Anime News Network, Crunchyroll, edited)\",\"bannerImage\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/banner\\/201090-YIO0HtbUiCwC.jpg\",\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx201090-HzQKUjjvde32.jpg\",\"color\":\"#e4ae50\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"4_CsA45Rsnk\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/4_CsA45Rsnk\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/ghostconcert-anime.com\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/17-R0tMgOvwvhsS.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/GHOSTCONCERT_PJ\"},{\"site\":\"Crunchyroll\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/5-AWN2pVlluCOO.png\",\"color\":\"#F88B24\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.crunchyroll.com\\/series\\/GT00374796\\/ghost-concert--missing-songs\"},{\"site\":\"YouTube\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/13-ZwR1Xwgtyrwa.png\",\"color\":\"#FF0000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/playlist?list=PLxSscENEp7JgpcAwuayL8qIjFf0EVbNw0\"}],\"rankings\":[{\"rank\":97,\"type\":\"RATED\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":false}],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":6292,\"name\":\"ENGI\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/6292\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[{\"episode\":7,\"airingAt\":1779031800},{\"episode\":8,\"airingAt\":1779636600}]}},{\"id\":195333,\"idMal\":61943,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Haibara-kun no Tsuyokute Seishun New Game\",\"native\":\"\\u7070\\u539f\\u304f\\u3093\\u306e\\u5f37\\u304f\\u3066\\u9752\\u6625\\u30cb\\u30e5\\u30fc\\u30b2\\u30fc\\u30e0\",\"english\":\"Haibara's Teenage New Game+\"},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2026,\"month\":4,\"day\":3},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"season\":\"SPRING\",\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Romance\",\"Slice of Life\"],\"synonyms\":[\"Haibara\\u2019s Teenage New Game+\"],\"duration\":24,\"popularity\":15867,\"episodes\":12,\"source\":\"LIGHT_NOVEL\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u7070\\u539f\\u304f\\u3093\",\"averageScore\":64,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/195333\",\"description\":\"We all have embarrassing memories or deep regrets from high school, right? Socially anxious college senior Natsuki Haibara sure does. When he thinks back on that time of his life, all he has are fleeting fantasies of a happy adolescence that could have been. Imagine his bewilderment and surprise, then, when he inexplicably finds himself seven years in the past\\u2014one month before his first year of high school! Can Haibara avoid his previous mistakes, make his way to the top of the school social pyramid, and end up with the girl of his dreams? Or will he be forced to relive three years of solitude as the most hated guy in school? He\\u2019ll need all the help he can get in order to succeed, from a workout regimen to online how-to guides, a childhood friend, and plenty of sheer willpower. Watch as Haibara takes a second shot at his teenage years!\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: J-Novel Club)\\n<br><br>\\n<i>Note: The first 4 episodes had an advance screening on March 15th, 2026. The start date reflects the start of the regular series broadcasting.<\\/i>\\n\\n\",\"bannerImage\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/banner\\/195333-66Rnkl0TzxtO.jpg\",\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx195333-KUIF1eqOdVdd.png\",\"color\":\"#1aa1ff\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"MPJrey_y_DU\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/MPJrey_y_DU\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/17-R0tMgOvwvhsS.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/haibara_anime\"},{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/haibarakun-anime.com\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Crunchyroll\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/5-AWN2pVlluCOO.png\",\"color\":\"#F88B24\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.crunchyroll.com\\/series\\/GT00371668\\/haibaras-teenage-new-game\"}],\"rankings\":[{\"rank\":65,\"type\":\"RATED\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":false},{\"rank\":77,\"type\":\"POPULAR\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":false},{\"rank\":30,\"type\":\"POPULAR\",\"season\":\"SPRING\",\"allTime\":false}],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":126,\"name\":\"Studio Comet\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/stud