":1779195600},{\"episode\":8,\"airingAt\":1779800400}]}},{\"id\":182483,\"idMal\":60028,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Hime Kishi wa Barbaroi no Yome\",\"native\":\"\\u59eb\\u9a0e\\u58eb\\u306f\\u86ee\\u65cf\\u306e\\u5ac1\",\"english\":\"The Warrior Princess and the Barbaric King\"},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2026,\"month\":4,\"day\":9},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"season\":\"SPRING\",\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Comedy\",\"Fantasy\",\"Romance\"],\"synonyms\":[\"The Barbarian\\u2019s Bride\",\"The Bride of Babaroi\",\"Himekishi wa Barbaroi no Yome\",\"\\u30d0\\u30eb\\u3088\\u3081\",\"BaruYome\",\"\\u041f\\u0440\\u0438\\u043d\\u0446\\u0435\\u0441\\u0441\\u0430-\\u0440\\u044b\\u0446\\u0430\\u0440\\u044c \\u2014 \\u043d\\u0435\\u0432\\u0435\\u0441\\u0442\\u0430 \\u0432\\u0430\\u0440\\u0432\\u0430\\u0440\\u0430\"],\"duration\":24,\"popularity\":34180,\"episodes\":12,\"source\":\"MANGA\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u30d0\\u30eb\\u3088\\u3081\",\"averageScore\":67,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/182483\",\"description\":\"Serafina, the West\\u2019s fiercest knight, expected torture when captured by barbarians. Instead, she got a marriage proposal! Marrying her sworn enemy is a hard no! But after seeing her wedding captor\\u2019s culture and very pretty face, she may be tempted to swap her sword for a wedding veil. Get ready for the ultimate enemies-to-maybe-lovers arc.\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: Crunchyroll)\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx182483-La7chs6htDWr.jpg\",\"color\":\"#50bbf1\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"oGSDv7XSZA4\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/oGSDv7XSZA4\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/himekishi-anime.com\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/219-EwrfceXsqIWg.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/himekishi_anime\"},{\"site\":\"Crunchyroll\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/5-AWN2pVlluCOO.png\",\"color\":\"#F88B24\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.crunchyroll.com\\/series\\/GT00362253\\/the-warrior-princess-and-the-barbaric-king\"}],\"rankings\":[{\"rank\":58,\"type\":\"RATED\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":false},{\"rank\":31,\"type\":\"POPULAR\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":false},{\"rank\":29,\"type\":\"RATED\",\"season\":\"SPRING\",\"allTime\":false},{\"rank\":12,\"type\":\"POPULAR\",\"season\":\"SPRING\",\"allTime\":false}],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":755,\"name\":\"Jumondou\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/755\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":128319,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Hime Kishi wa Barbaroi no Yome\",\"native\":\"\\u59eb\\u9a0e\\u58eb\\u306f\\u86ee\\u65cf\\u306e\\u5ac1\",\"english\":\"The Barbarian\\u2019s Bride\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/128319\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[{\"episode\":6,\"airingAt\":1778761800},{\"episode\":7,\"airingAt\":1779366600}]}},{\"id\":169228,\"idMal\":56646,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Hokuto no Ken: FIST OF THE NORTH STAR\",\"native\":\"\\u5317\\u6597\\u306e\\u62f3 -FIST OF THE NORTH STAR-\",\"english\":\"FIST OF THE NORTH STAR: HOKUTO NO KEN\"},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2026,\"month\":4,\"day\":11},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"season\":\"SPRING\",\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Drama\",\"Sci-Fi\"],\"synonyms\":[\"El pu\\u00f1o de la Estrella del Norte: HOKUTO NO KEN\"],\"duration\":24,\"popularity\":4985,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"MANGA\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u5317\\u6597\\u306e\\u62f3\\u30a2\\u30cb\\u30e1 #FISTOFTHENORTHSTAR \",\"averageScore\":57,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/169228\",\"description\":\"In the year 199X, the world is engulfed in a nuclear inferno! The seas have vanished. The earth lies in ruins. It seems all life has been wiped out...but humanity has not perished!<br><br>\\n\\nAcross the scorched and broken land, survivors cling to hope, desperately searching for food and water. However, their hopes are trampled underfoot by violence. Might makes right in this world, and the weak are crushed without mercy.<br><br>\\n\\nFrom the depths of that despair, a lone man with seven scars on his chest emerges. His name is Kenshiro, heir to the legendary assassination art Hokuto Shinken. As he roams the wasteland in pursuit of his sworn enemy Shin, who stole his fianc\\u00e9e Yuria, Kenshiro answers the cries of the oppressed, becoming a beacon of hope in a world of despair.<br><br>\\n\\nStanding in his path are brutal survivors of the apocalypse, their ambitions twisted by power and greed. In a world where the weak are prey and prayers go unheard, Kenshiro forges a path with his iron fists!<br><br>\\n\\n(Source: Official Website)\",\"bannerImage\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/banner\\/169228-L0wA8BGp54fa.jpg\",\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx169228-y79xDpZ29Vv4.jpg\",\"color\":\"#f1bb28\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"Gux_dYHDMK4\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/Gux_dYHDMK4\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/hokuto-anime.com\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/17-R0tMgOvwvhsS.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/twitter.com\\/hokutonokeninfo\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Amazon Prime Video\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/21-bDoNIomehkOx.png\",\"color\":\"#FF9900\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.amazon.co.jp\\/dp\\/B0G4BLNYJJ\"}],\"rankings\":[{\"rank\":90,\"type\":\"RATED\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":false}],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":73,\"name\":\"TMS Entertainment\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/73\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":31149,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Hokuto no Ken\",\"native\":\"\\u5317\\u6597\\u306e\\u62f3\",\"english\":\"Fist of the North Star\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/31149\"}},{\"relationType\":\"ALTERNATIVE\",\"node\":{\"id\":967,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Hokuto no Ken\",\"native\":\"\\u5317\\u6597\\u306e\\u62f3\",\"english\":\"Fist of the North Star\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/967\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[{\"episode\":8,\"airingAt\":1778860800},{\"episode\":9,\"airingAt\":1779465600}]}},{\"id\":171110,\"idMal\":57466,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Honzuki no Gekokujou: Ryoushu no Youjo\",\"native\":\"\\u672c\\u597d\\u304d\\u306e\\u4e0b\\u524b\\u4e0a \\u9818\\u4e3b\\u306e\\u990a\\u5973\",\"english\":\"Ascendance of a Bookworm: Adopted Daughter of an Archduke\"},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2026,\"month\":4,\"day\":4},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"season\":\"SPRING\",\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Drama\",\"Fantasy\",\"Slice of Life\"],\"synonyms\":[\"Ascendance of a Bookworm Season 4\",\"\\u672c\\u597d\\u304d\\u306e\\u4e0b\\u524b\\u4e0a \\u53f8\\u66f8\\u306b\\u306a\\u308b\\u305f\\u3081\\u306b\\u306f\\u624b\\u6bb5\\u3092\\u9078\\u3093\\u3067\\u3044\\u3089\\u308c\\u307e\\u305b\\u3093 \\u7b2c4\\u671f\",\"Honzuki no Gekokujou: Shisho ni Naru Tame ni wa Shudan wo Erandeiraremasen 4th Season\"],\"duration\":24,\"popularity\":27805,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"LIGHT_NOVEL\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u672c\\u597d\\u304d\\u306e\\u4e0b\\u524b\\u4e0a\",\"averageScore\":77,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/171110\",\"description\":\"Anime adaptation of Part 3 of <i>Honzuki no Gekokujou<\\/i>.\\n<br><br>\\nFollowing a disastrous encounter with a noble, Myne finally resolves to say goodbye to her family and friends in the lower city, changing her name to \\u201cRozemyne\\u201d and beginning her new life as the adopted daughter of Ehrenfest\\u2019s archduke. However, her days as an archnoble in noble society are brutal, as she is put through rigorous etiquette and magic training on top of her duties as High Bishop and forewoman. It all proves too much for a weak little seven-year-old girl... Or it would have, had the High Priest not offered her the keys to the temple\\u2019s book room as a reward. If she could get her hands on those, she\\u2019d be able to read all sorts of precious books! Her name may have changed, but Rozemyne\\u2019s passion for books remains the same as she charges into a whole new world! The detailed setting expands as the printing industry grows in size. Here begins Part 3 of this biblio-fantasy for book lovers everywhere!\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: J-Novel Club) \",\"bannerImage\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/banner\\/171110-lgtmKokpevUM.jpg\",\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx171110-7zOdInS6DQNL.jpg\",\"color\":\"#5daee4\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"rtPF6rjrdSU\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/rtPF6rjrdSU\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/booklove-anime.jp\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/17-R0tMgOvwvhsS.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/twitter.com\\/anime_booklove\"},{\"site\":\"Crunchyroll\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/5-AWN2pVlluCOO.png\",\"color\":\"#F88B24\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.crunchyroll.com\\/series\\/G6793XKZY\\/ascendance-of-a-bookworm\"}],\"rankings\":[{\"rank\":24,\"type\":\"RATED\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":false},{\"rank\":45,\"type\":\"POPULAR\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":false},{\"rank\":12,\"type\":\"RATED\",\"season\":\"SPRING\",\"allTime\":false},{\"rank\":22,\"type\":\"POPULAR\",\"season\":\"SPRING\",\"allTime\":false}],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":858,\"name\":\"WIT STUDIO\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/858\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":110801,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Honzuki no Gekokujou: Shisho ni Naru Tame ni wa Shudan wo Erandeiraremasen Dai 3-bu - Ryoushu no Youjo\",\"native\":\"\\u672c\\u597d\\u304d\\u306e\\u4e0b\\u524b\\u4e0a~\\u53f8\\u66f8\\u306b\\u306a\\u308b\\u305f\\u3081\\u306b\\u306f\\u624b\\u6bb5\\u3092\\u9078\\u3093\\u3067\\u3044\\u3089\\u308c\\u307e\\u305b\\u3093~\\u7b2c\\u4e09\\u90e8\\u300c\\u9818\\u4e3b\\u306e\\u990a\\u5973\\u300d\",\"english\":\"Ascendance of a Bookworm: Part 3\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/110801\"}},{\"relationType\":\"PREQUEL\",\"node\":{\"id\":121176,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Honzuki no Gekokujou: Shisho ni Naru Tame ni wa Shudan wo Erandeiraremasen 3rd Season\",\"native\":\"\\u672c\\u597d\\u304d\\u306e\\u4e0b\\u524b\\u4e0a \\u53f8\\u66f8\\u306b\\u306a\\u308b\\u305f\\u3081\\u306b\\u306f\\u624b\\u6bb5\\u3092\\u9078\\u3093\\u3067\\u3044\\u3089\\u308c\\u307e\\u305b\\u3093 \\u7b2c3\\u671f\",\"english\":\"Ascendance of a Bookworm Season 3\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/121176\"}},{\"relationType\":\"ALTERNATIVE\",\"node\":{\"id\":110805,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Honzuki no Gekokujou: Shisho ni Naru Tame ni wa Shudan wo Erandeiraremasen Dai 3-bu - Ryouchi ni Hon wo Hirogeyou!\",\"native\":\"\\u672c\\u597d\\u304d\\u306e\\u4e0b\\u524b\\u4e0a~\\u53f8\\u66f8\\u306b\\u306a\\u308b\\u305f\\u3081\\u306b\\u306f\\u624b\\u6bb5\\u3092\\u9078\\u3093\\u3067\\u3044\\u3089\\u308c\\u307e\\u305b\\u3093~ \\u7b2c\\u4e