Ao\",\"native\":\"\\u30ad\\u30eb\\u30a2\\u30aa\",\"english\":\"Kill Blue \"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/163495\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[{\"episode\":6,\"airingAt\":1778940000},{\"episode\":7,\"airingAt\":1779544800}]}},{\"id\":181284,\"idMal\":59835,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Kirio Fanclub\",\"native\":\"\\u9727\\u5c3e\\u30d5\\u30a1\\u30f3\\u30af\\u30e9\\u30d6\",\"english\":\"Kirio Fan Club\"},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2026,\"month\":4,\"day\":3},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"season\":\"SPRING\",\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Comedy\",\"Romance\",\"Slice of Life\"],\"synonyms\":[\"KirioFC\",\"\\u0e04\\u0e34\\u0e23\\u0e34\\u0e42\\u0e2d\\u0e30\\u0e41\\u0e1f\\u0e19\\u0e04\\u0e25\\u0e31\\u0e1a\"],\"duration\":24,\"popularity\":7455,\"episodes\":12,\"source\":\"MANGA\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u9727\\u5c3e\\u30d5\\u30a1\\u30f3\\u30af\\u30e9\\u30d6 #KirioFanClub\",\"averageScore\":59,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/181284\",\"description\":\"For Aimi and Nami, the answer is to cry tears of joy for being able to pinpoint at a distance the object of their affections, Kirio, from a single toot. These are the kinds of deep, philosophical questions the two friends\\/rivals in romance pose to each other to prove their love for this boy who hardly seems to know they exist. That won\\u2019t stop them from conducting nightly rituals to entice him into their dreams, though, or listing out what exactly they like about him, down to the very last organ. But when push comes to shove, will they choose their hilarious friendship over a shot at love? \\n<br><br>\\n(Source: Kodansha USA)\",\"bannerImage\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/banner\\/181284-BthvQRasKf46.jpg\",\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx181284-JJafhd5gDT53.jpg\",\"color\":\"#5da1e4\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"n3c6bAOhVUg\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/n3c6bAOhVUg\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/kirio-fc.com\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/219-EwrfceXsqIWg.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/kirio_fc\"},{\"site\":\"HIDIVE\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/20-3nWxygrjVM5A.png\",\"color\":\"#03AEEF\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.hidive.com\\/season\\/35227\"},{\"site\":\"YouTube\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/13-ZwR1Xwgtyrwa.png\",\"color\":\"#FF0000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/playlist?list=PLxSscENEp7JgMGXyhUEr1I_5ryXN436vi\"}],\"rankings\":[{\"rank\":88,\"type\":\"RATED\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":false}],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":41,\"name\":\"Satelight\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/41\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":171282,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Kirio Fanclub\",\"native\":\"\\u9727\\u5c3e\\u30d5\\u30a1\\u30f3\\u30af\\u30e9\\u30d6\",\"english\":\"Kirio Fan Club\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/171282\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[{\"episode\":7,\"airingAt\":1778772360},{\"episode\":8,\"airingAt\":1779377160}]}},{\"id\":209940,\"idMal\":63709,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Komekami! Girls\",\"native\":\"\\u3053\\u3081\\u304b\\u307f\\u3063\\uff01Girls\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2026,\"month\":4,\"day\":3},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"season\":\"SPRING\",\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Comedy\"],\"synonyms\":[\"\\u3053\\u3081\\u304b\\u307f\\u3063\\uff01\\u30ac\\u30fc\\u30eb\\u30ba\"],\"duration\":23,\"popularity\":803,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"OTHER\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u3053\\u3081\\u304b\\u307f\\u3063\",\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/209940\",\"description\":\"This is the story of the seven-sister unit \\\"Komekami! Girls,\\\" children of the rice deity, born from the tradition: \\\"In a single grain of rice, seven gods reside.\\\"<br><br>\\n\\nWhen their mother (the deity of rice, or the rice-god queen) was called back in haste to the celestial realm and no longer able to return to the earthly realm they search for her traces using Usa City (Oita Prefecture) as their base, and teleport to Hachiman shrines throughout Kyushu island. As they solve local problems, they learn about food, take part in cooking battles, and grow.\",\"bannerImage\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/banner\\/209940-5otPJXyKJkbf.jpg\",\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx209940-AmmMcfBXmB3c.jpg\",\"color\":\"#a15028\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"Xqc-0SgApHw\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/Xqc-0SgApHw\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/219-EwrfceXsqIWg.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/komekami_girls\"},{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/komekamigirls.com\\/\"},{\"site\":\"YouTube\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/13-ZwR1Xwgtyrwa.png\",\"color\":\"#FF0000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/@komekami_girls\"},{\"site\":\"Instagram\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/48-VFlxaXGaNqXk.png\",\"color\":\"#833AB4\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.instagram.com\\/komekami_girls\\/\"}],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":7798,\"name\":\"Daily Plan.net\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/7798\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[{\"episode\":7,\"airingAt\":1778777400},{\"episode\":8,\"airingAt\":1779382200}]}},{\"id\":186497,\"idMal\":60852,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Koori no Jouheki\",\"native\":\"\\u6c37\\u306e\\u57ce\\u58c1\",\"english\":\"The Ramparts of Ice\"},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2026,\"month\":4,\"day\":2},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"season\":\"SPRING\",\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Comedy\",\"Romance\",\"Slice of Life\"],\"synonyms\":[\"Parede de Gelo\",\"\\u0421\\u0442\\u0435\\u043d\\u044b \\u0438\\u0437\\u043e \\u043b\\u044c\\u0434\\u0430\",\"\\u0e1b\\u0e23\\u0e32\\u0e01\\u0e32\\u0e23\\u0e19\\u0e49\\u0e33\\u0e41\\u0e02\\u0e47\\u0e07\\u0e41\\u0e2b\\u0e48\\u0e07\\u0e2b\\u0e31\\u0e27\\u0e43\\u0e08\"],\"duration\":24,\"popularity\":38682,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"MANGA\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u6c37\\u306e\\u57ce\\u58c1\",\"averageScore\":77,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/186497\",\"description\":\"Socially inept, Higawa Koyuki maintains a wall between herself and other people. She spends her time in high school alone, until she meets Amamiya Minato, a boy who keeps trying to close the distance between them for some reason?!\\n<BR><BR>\\nThe loner Koyuki, the popular Miki, the boundary-less Minato, and the kind basketball player Youta. This is the story about four complicated and confused young people and their mixed up lives!\\n<BR><BR>\\n(Source: Margaret, translated)\",\"bannerImage\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/banner\\/186497-naXtQFMHJaR1.jpg\",\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx186497-uwPrNPphXvjP.jpg\",\"color\":\"#e49343\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"a7ah5by0Ffw\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/a7ah5by0Ffw\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\"