"Slice of Life\"],\"synonyms\":[\"\\u0e22\\u0e32\\u0e21\\u0e40\\u0e21\\u0e37\\u0e48\\u0e2d\\u0e04\\u0e38\\u0e08\\u0e34\\u0e21\\u0e30\\u0e02\\u0e31\\u0e1a\\u0e02\\u0e32\\u0e19\"],\"duration\":24,\"popularity\":3772,\"episodes\":12,\"source\":\"MANGA\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u30af\\u30b8\\u30de\\u6b4c\\u3048\\u3070\\u5bb6\\u307b\\u308d\\u308d\",\"averageScore\":56,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/177508\",\"description\":\"In the fall of his first year of junior high school, Arata Kouda encountered a strange thing----. In this home comedy, a mysterious creature named \\u201cKujima\\u201d brings new life to the Konohda family, where the atmosphere is slightly tense due to the concern for the eldest son, a ronin student who is preparing for the entrance examinations! By the way, the creature, who calls himself Kujima, speaks normal language and eats the same food as humans (or insects). Did he come from outer space, or did he...!<br>\\n<br>\\n(Source: Crunchyroll)\",\"bannerImage\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/banner\\/177508-AAws5SPLJL2S.jpg\",\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx177508-Ajz9UrU5SsQ0.jpg\",\"color\":\"#e4ae1a\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"rc17AA0hVI8\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/rc17AA0hVI8\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/219-EwrfceXsqIWg.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/kujima_anime\"},{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/kujima-anime.com\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Crunchyroll\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/5-AWN2pVlluCOO.png\",\"color\":\"#F88B24\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.crunchyroll.com\\/series\\/GT00371849\\/kujima-why-sing-when-you-can-warble\"},{\"site\":\"YouTube\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/13-ZwR1Xwgtyrwa.png\",\"color\":\"#FF0000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/playlist?list=PLxSscENEp7Jgh7HSGQ8_OD4-vXd6pcrbq\"}],\"rankings\":[{\"rank\":91,\"type\":\"RATED\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":false}],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":101,\"name\":\"Studio Hibari\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/101\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":144868,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Kujima Utaeba Ie Hororo\",\"native\":\"\\u30af\\u30b8\\u30de\\u6b4c\\u3048\\u3070\\u5bb6\\u307b\\u308d\\u308d\",\"english\":null},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/144868\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[{\"episode\":6,\"airingAt\":1778765400},{\"episode\":7,\"airingAt\":1779370200}]}},{\"id\":196974,\"idMal\":62171,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Kuroneko to Majo no Kyoushitsu\",\"native\":\"\\u9ed2\\u732b\\u3068\\u9b54\\u5973\\u306e\\u6559\\u5ba4\",\"english\":\"The Classroom of the Black Cat and a Witch\"},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2026,\"month\":4,\"day\":12},\"endDate\":{\"year\":2026,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"season\":\"SPRING\",\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Fantasy\"],\"synonyms\":[\"The Classroom of a Black Cat and a Witch\",\"\\u0427\\u0451\\u0440\\u043d\\u0430\\u044f \\u043a\\u043e\\u0448\\u043a\\u0430 \\u0438 \\u043a\\u043b\\u0430\\u0441\\u0441 \\u0432\\u0435\\u0434\\u044c\\u043c\"],\"duration\":24,\"popularity\":15258,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"MANGA\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u9ed2\\u732b\\u3068\\u9b54\\u5973\\u306e\\u6559\\u5ba4\",\"averageScore\":63,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/196974\",\"description\":\"Spica Virgo is an apprentice witch, but can\\u2019t use any magic. She needs someone to be her master in order to get into the academy of her dreams, but she has no money and no connections. Suddenly, a mysterious talking black cat that can use magic appears before her!! Spica wants to learn magic, and the black cat wants his curse broken\\u2014goals on the same path. Therefore, a secret master-apprentice relationship was born! But the key to breaking the curse is kissing his\\u2026?! A clumsy witch and the teachings of a black cat\\u2014the magic academy fantasy starts here!!\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: K Manga)\",\"bannerImage\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/banner\\/196974-wOXpVEgXm7aR.jpg\",\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx196974-mZk1uyrx0XNx.png\",\"color\":\"#50aef1\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"uJhshLlQs60\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/uJhshLlQs60\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/219-EwrfceXsqIWg.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/witch_classroom\"},{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/witch-classroom.com\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Crunchyroll\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/5-AWN2pVlluCOO.png\",\"color\":\"#F88B24\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.crunchyroll.com\\/series\\/GT00374357\\/the-classroom-of-a-black-cat-and-a-witch\"},{\"site\":\"YouTube\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/13-ZwR1Xwgtyrwa.png\",\"color\":\"#FF0000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/playlist?list=PLxSscENEp7Jh2Aq9dnBrcdmlUPfq5VQtL\"}],\"rankings\":[{\"rank\":67,\"type\":\"RATED\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":false},{\"rank\":82,\"type\":\"POPULAR\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":false}],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":839,\"name\":\"LIDENFILMS\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/839\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":146181,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Kuroneko to Majo no Kyoushitsu\",\"native\":\"\\u9ed2\\u732b\\u3068\\u9b54\\u5973\\u306e\\u6559\\u5ba4\",\"english\":\"The Classroom of a Black Cat and a Witch\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/146181\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[{\"episode\":6,\"airingAt\":1779028200},{\"episode\":7,\"airingAt\":1779633000}]}},{\"id\":197754,\"idMal\":62331,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"LIAR GAME\",\"native\":\"LIAR GAME\",\"english\":\"LIAR GAME\"},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2026,\"month\":4,\"day\":7},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"season\":\"SPRING\",\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Drama\",\"Psychological\"],\"synonyms\":[\" \\u30e9\\u30a4\\u30a2\\u30fc\\u30b2\\u30fc\\u30e0\",\"\\u0418\\u0433\\u0440\\u0430 \\u043b\\u0436\\u0435\\u0446\\u043e\\u0432\"],\"duration\":24,\"popularity\":29660,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"MANGA\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u30e9\\u30a4\\u30a2\\u30fc\\u30b2\\u30fc\\u30e0 #LIARGAME\",\"averageScore\":60,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/197754\",\"description\":\"Wishing she would live up to the ideal, Kanzaki Nao's father named her thusly for \\u201chonesty\\u201d. Nao has more than lived up to her father's wishes--even exceeding them and earning the label of \\\"a foolishly honest girl\\\". This makes Nao the least qualified candidate for the high stakes 'Liar Game', where winning requires deceiving the opponent out of their money and losing means receiving massive debt. However, that doesn't stop a box containing a hundred million yen in cash and a card informing her of her participation in the game from arriving at her doorstep, nor does it stop her from being promptly tricked out of the entire sum of money. Upon hearing that a genius swindler, responsible for the bankruptcy of a major corporation, is being released from jail, Nao goes to the swindler, Shinichi Akiyama, to enlist his help. With that, the two are drawn into the dark, greed-filled, and deceptive world of the Liar 