,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Replica Datte, Koi wo Suru.\",\"native\":\"\\u30ec\\u30d7\\u30ea\\u30ab\\u3060\\u3063\\u3066\\u3001\\u604b\\u3092\\u3059\\u308b\",\"english\":\"Even a Replica Can Fall in Love\"},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2026,\"month\":4,\"day\":7},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"season\":\"SPRING\",\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Drama\",\"Romance\",\"Supernatural\"],\"synonyms\":[\"\\u0414\\u0430\\u0436\\u0435 \\u043a\\u043e\\u043f\\u0438\\u044f \\u0441\\u043f\\u043e\\u0441\\u043e\\u0431\\u043d\\u0430 \\u0432\\u043b\\u044e\\u0431\\u0438\\u0442\\u044c\\u0441\\u044f\"],\"duration\":24,\"popularity\":11482,\"episodes\":13,\"source\":\"LIGHT_NOVEL\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u30ec\\u30d7\\u30ea\\u30b3\",\"averageScore\":66,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/186744\",\"description\":\"When she doesn\\u2019t feel well, when there\\u2019s a test, when she doesn\\u2019t want to go to school... I take her place. I\\u2019m her replica. I\\u2019m not meant for anything else. But that changed when I fell in love. I wear my hair up so the boy I fell for knows it\\u2019s me. We skip school and promise to meet again tomorrow, and every day after. I\\u2019m her replica. Everything about me is borrowed and empty, but my heart is mine.<br>\\n<br>\\n(Source: Crunchyroll)\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx186744-nFH4y2slUrO4.jpg\",\"color\":\"#f1f1c9\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"WsT7OO91jXo\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/WsT7OO91jXo\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/219-EwrfceXsqIWg.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/REPLICO_dengeki\"},{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/replico.jp