            "text": "{\"data\":{\"Page\":{\"pageInfo\":{\"hasNextPage\":false,\"total\":54},\"media\":[{\"id\":195600,\"idMal\":62001,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Yomi no Tsugai\",\"native\":\"\\u9ec4\\u6cc9\\u306e\\u30c4\\u30ac\\u30a4\",\"english\":\"Daemons of the Shadow Realm\"},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2026,\"month\":4,\"day\":4},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"season\":\"SPRING\",\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Adventure\",\"Comedy\",\"Fantasy\"],\"synonyms\":[\"\\u30e8\\u30df\\u30c4\\u30ac\",\"YomiTsuga\",\"Pasangan dari Alam Baka\",\"\\u0e22\\u0e21\\u0e25\\u0e41\\u0e2b\\u0e48\\u0e07\\u0e22\\u0e21\\u0e42\\u0e25\\u0e01\",\"Daemons do Reino das Sombras\",\"Esp\\u00edritus del Inframundo\"],\"duration\":24,\"popularity\":83197,\"episodes\":24,\"source\":\"MANGA\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u9ec4\\u6cc9\\u306e\\u30c4\\u30ac\\u30a4 #\\u30e8\\u30df\\u30c4\\u30ac\",\"averageScore\":78,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/195600\",\"description\":\"In a remote mountain village under the watchful eyes of two stone guardians, the young Yuru contentedly lives off the land while staying close to the only family he has left\\u2014Asa, his precious twin sister. Asa, meanwhile, carries out a mysterious \\u201cduty\\u201d on behalf of the village while locked in a cage. Why is Asa a prisoner? And what other secrets does Yuru\\u2019s otherwise idyllic home hide?\\n<br><br>(Source: Square Enix)\",\"bannerImage\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/banner\\/195600-UxHvDXwzJxlP.jpg\",\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx195600-moI0UFArtOme.jpg\",\"color\":\"#e49335\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"XCyj9KKKjUI\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/XCyj9KKKjUI\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.