 just end up whetting yours!\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: Crunchyroll)\\n<br><br>\\n<i>Note: Maid-san wa Taberu dake was streamed a week in advance on dAnimestore, ABEMA, and U-Next starting with episode 2. Episode 1 was streamed on April 1, 2026. Regular broadcasting began on April 5, 2026.<\\/i>\",\"bannerImage\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/banner\\/197868-wBmzwZ3Ay4bD.jpg\",\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx197868-sm5jcjPKWhNL.png\",\"color\":\"#e49343\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"lPLmZANPhrM\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/lPLmZANPhrM\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/meitabe-anime.com\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/219-EwrfceXsqIWg.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/lovetoeat_maid\"},{\"site\":\"Crunchyroll\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/5-AWN2pVlluCOO.png\",\"color\":\"#F88B24\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.crunchyroll.com\\/series\\/GT00375170\\/the-food-diary-of-miss-maid\"}],\"rankings\":[{\"rank\":22,\"type\":\"RATED\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":false},{\"rank\":24,\"type\":\"POPULAR\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":false}],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":6125,\"name\":\"EMT Squared\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/6125\"},{\"id\":207,\"name\":\"Magic Bus\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/207\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":114010,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Maid-san wa Taberu dake\",\"native\":\"\\u30e1\\u30a4\\u30c9\\u3055\\u3093\\u306f\\u98df\\u3079\\u308b\\u3060\\u3051\",\"english\":\"The Food Diary of Miss Maid\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/114010\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[{\"episode\":8,\"airingAt\":1779022800},{\"episode\":9,\"airingAt\":1779627600}]}},{\"id\":210234,\"idMal\":63304,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Mamonogurai no Boukensha: Ore Dake Mamono wo Kuratte Tsuyoku Naru\",\"native\":\"\\u9b54\\u7269\\u55b0\\u3089\\u3044\\u306e\\u5192\\u967a\\u8005 ~\\u4ffa\\u3060\\u3051\\u9b54\\u7269\\u3092\\u55b0\\u3089\\u3063\\u3066\\u5f37\\u304f\\u306a\\u308b~\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2026,\"month\":4,\"day\":3},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"season\":\"SPRING\",\"format\":\"TV_SHORT\",\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Adventure\",\"Fantasy\"],\"synonyms\":[\"Monster Eater\"],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":5373,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"LIGHT_NOVEL\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u9b54\\u7269\\u55b0\\u3089\\u3044\\u306e\\u5192\\u967a\\u8005\",\"averageScore\":38,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/210234\",\"description\":\"Rudd\\u2019s a nobody-- just an E-Rank adventurer with a seemingly useless talent of status immunity. An outcast in a city obsessed with labyrinth crawling, he\\u2019s stuck scraping by as a \\u201cgrubby forager,\\u201d navigating guild politics and backstabbing adventurers just to survive. But when a betrayal leaves him for dead without any supplies or help, he does the unthinkable and consumes the flesh of fallen monsters...\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: WEBTOON)\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx210234-MZaMjdbBzEHz.jpg\",\"color\":\"#e4505d\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"tXZbVN3xc7U\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/tXZbVN3xc7U\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/animationid.com\\/mamonogurai\\/\"}],\"rankings\":[{\"rank\":11,\"type\":\"RATED\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":false},{\"rank\":4,\"type\":\"POPULAR\",