"Drama\",\"Ecchi\",\"Romance\",\"Supernatural\"],\"synonyms\":[],\"duration\":6,\"popularity\":10349,\"episodes\":8,\"source\":\"MANGA\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u8309\\u8389\\u82b1\\u3061\\u3083\\u3093\\u306e\\u597d\\u611f\\u5ea6\\u306f\\u3076\\u3063\\u58ca\\u308c\\u3066\\u3044\\u308b\",\"averageScore\":49,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/202523\",\"description\":\"Confessing to my childhood friend Marika was impossible for someone as unpopular as me. So, I did what any desperate boy would do\\u2014I wished upon a shooting star! When I woke up, that dream had come true?! I could see a love meter for people, just like in a love simulation game. Once I realized this was real and not a dream I went straight to see Marika. Her love meter was so low it had broken and practically fallen all the way to hell! If she hated me so much why was she so nice?! Is this how she really felt or...?!\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: Coolmic)\\n<br><br>\\n<i>Note: Episode 1 received an advanced distribution on AnimeFesta on March 13th, 2026. The start date reflects the start of the regular series broadcasting.<\\/i>\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx202523-NHeyiypiPnGP.jpg\",\"color\":\"#e44378\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"Ohd23eSaOaw\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/Ohd23eSaOaw\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/219-EwrfceXsqIWg.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/marikowa_off\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/marikowa.af-original.com\"},{\"site\":\"OceanVeil\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/249-CFCxdC7MiNX3.png\",\"color\":\"#00D0D3\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/oceanveil.net\\/anime_titles\\/398\"},{\"site\":\"OceanVeil\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/249-CFCxdC7MiNX3.png\",\"color\":\"#00D0D3\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/oceanveil.net\\/anime_titles\\/399\"}],\"rankings\":[{\"rank\":6,\"type\":\"RATED\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":false},{\"rank\":1,\"type\":\"POPULAR\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":false},{\"rank\":4,\"type\":\"RATED\",\"season\":\"SPRING\",\"allTime\":false},{\"rank\":1,\"type\":\"POPULAR\",\"season\":\"SPRING\",\"allTime\":false}],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":7575,\"name\":\"studio LEO\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/7575\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":188743,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Marika-chan no Koukando wa Bukkowareteiru\",\"native\":\"\\u8309\\u8389\\u82b1\\u3061\\u3083\\u3093\\u306e\\u597d\\u611f\\u5ea6\\u306f\\u3076\\u3063\\u58ca\\u308c\\u3066\\u3044\\u308b\",\"english\":\"Marika's Love Meter Malfunction\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/188743\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[{\"episode\":6,\"airingAt\":1779033600},{\"episode\":7,\"airingAt\":1779638400}]}},{\"id\":198369,\"idMal\":62387,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Meitantei Conan: Highway no Datenshi\",\"native\":\"\\u540d\\u63a2\\u5075\\u30b3\\u30ca\\u30f3 \\u30cf\\u30a4\\u30a6\\u30a7\\u30a4\\u306e\\u5815\\u5929\\u4f7f\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2026,\"month\":4,\"day\":10},\"endDate\":{\"year\":2026,\"month\":4,\"day\":10},\"status\":\"FINISHED\",\"season\":\"SPRING\",\"format\":\"MOVIE\",\"genres\":[\"Mystery\"],\"synonyms\":[\"Meitantei Conan Movie 29\",\"Detective Conan Movie 29\",\"Detective Conan: Fallen Angel of the Highway\"],\"duration\":109,\"popularity\":1491,\"episodes\":1,\"source\":\"MANGA\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u540d\\u63a2\\u5075\\u30b3\\u30ca\\u30f3\",\"averageScore\":55,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/198369\",\"description\":\"The 29th <i>Detective Conan<\\/i> movie.\\n<br><br>\\nConan, Ran, Sonoko, and Kogoro were heading to Yokohama's Minato Mirai district with motorcycle enthusiast Masumi Sera for the Kanagawa Motorcycle Festival. Then, a mysterious black motorcycle appeared, leaping over the car carrying Conan and the others. And chasing it was Chihaya Hagiwara of the Kanagawa Prefectural Police Traffic Mobile Unit\\u2014the \\u201cGoddess of the Wind\\u201d Ran had once seen. However, after a fierce car chase, Chihaya's motorcycle was wrecked, and she let the target slip away at the last moment. After arriving at the Yokohama festival venue, Conan and the others witnessed the unveiling of a new police motorcycle equipped with cutting-edge technology, named \\\"Angel.\\\" Amidst this, reports surfaced that a runaway \\\"black motorcycle\\\" had now appeared in central Tokyo, evading pursuit by the Metropolitan Police Department. The purpose of the rampage remains unknown, but the vehicle's body bears a striking resemblance to \\\"Angel.\\\" Police have dubbed the black Angel bike \\\"Lucifer\\\" and continue their pursuit.\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: Official website, translated)\",\"bannerImage\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/banner\\/198369-MmvnBvHzuB3D.jpg\",\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx198369-80jGPuTziEa7.png\",\"color\":\"#5dbbe4\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"CsxkouRl7Yo\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/CsxkouRl7Yo\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/17-R0tMgOvwvhsS.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/twitter.com\\/conan_movie\"},{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.conan-movie.jp\\/2026\"},{\"site\":\"Facebook\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/38-JvMCwgmWvF6Z.png\",\"color\":\"#4267B2\",\"ur