\\uc724\\ubb34\\uace1\",\"Il prisma dell'amore\",\"\\u0388\\u03c1\\u03c9\\u03c4\\u03b1\\u03c2 \\u039c\\u03ad\\u03c3\\u03b1 \\u03b1\\u03c0\\u03cc \\u03ad\\u03bd\\u03b1 \\u03a0\\u03c1\\u03af\\u03c3\\u03bc\\u03b1\",\"Le Prisme de l'amour\",\"\\u7a1c\\u93e1\\u6200\\u66f2\",\"\\u68f1\\u955c\\u604b\\u66f2\",\"\\u062d\\u0628\\u0651 \\u064a\\u0645\\u0631 \\u0639\\u0628\\u0631 \\u0645\\u0646\\u0634\\u0648\\u0631 \\u0632\\u062c\\u0627\\u062c\\u064a \",\"\\u041f\\u0440\\u0438\\u0437\\u043c\\u0430 \\u043b\\u044e\\u0431\\u0432\\u0438\"],\"duration\":24,\"popularity\":28313,\"episodes\":20,\"source\":\"ORIGINAL\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u30d7\\u30ea\\u30ba\\u30e0\\u8f2a\\u821e\\u66f2 #prismrondo #LoveThroughAPrism\",\"averageScore\":84,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/202955\",\"description\":\"Yoko Kamio, whose manga <i>\\\"Boys Over Flowers\\\"<\\/i> enraptured readers around the globe, brings a brand-new classic to viewers worldwide. Set at a London art academy in the opening decade of the 1900s, the Netflix Series <i>\\\"Love Through a Prism\\\"<\\/i> follows Lili Ichijoin, a girl enchanted by painting, as she chases her dreams and experiences youth. This ensemble coming-of-age story about young people striving for prismatic radiance against the odds is about to begin.<br><br>\\n(Source: Netflix)\",\"bannerImage\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/banner\\/202955-NGyGdH5wvSpB.jpg\",\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/medium\\/b202955-TFyTd1zFT1v7.jpg\",\"color\":\"#e4bb43\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"oLXSfFqTnXg\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/oLXSfFqTnXg\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Netflix\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/10-rVGPom8RCiwH.png\",\"color\":\"#E50914\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.netflix.com\\/title\\/81498882\"}],\"r