            "text": "{\"data\":{\"Page\":{\"pageInfo\":{\"hasNextPage\":true,\"total\":5000},\"media\":[{\"id\":208225,\"idMal\":63537,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"\\\"Kimi wo Aisuru Ki wa nai\\\" to Itta Jiki Koushaku-sama ga Naze ka Dekiai Shitekimasu\",\"native\":\"\\u300c\\u304d\\u307f\\u3092\\u611b\\u3059\\u308b\\u6c17\\u306f\\u306a\\u3044\\u300d\\u3068\\u8a00\\u3063\\u305f\\u6b21\\u671f\\u516c\\u7235\\u69d8\\u304c\\u306a\\u305c\\u304b\\u6eba\\u611b\\u3057\\u3066\\u304d\\u307e\\u3059\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2026,\"month\":7,\"day\":null},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Fantasy\",\"Romance\"],\"synonyms\":[\"The Duke\\u2019s Son Claims He Won\\u2019t Love Me Yet Showers Me with Adoration\"],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":1696,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"MANGA\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":null,\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/208225\",\"description\":\"Elsa, the daughter of a fallen aristocrat, receives news. It was a marriage proposal from Julius, a very elite nobleman. Elsa is wondering,\\\" Why would such a distinguished man marry me\\\"? But after the wedding, Julius, who had been kind and gentle up to that point, changed completely! In a cold voice, he tells her,\\\" I have no intention of loving you\\\".\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: MangaPlaza)\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx208225-l8IE89iX9t8T.png\",\"color\":\"#f1f1bb\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"kxqImT2NJvE\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/kxqImT2NJvE\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"TikTok\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/196-o2g5cLUG6k5V.png\",\"color\":\"#010101\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.tiktok.com\\/@kimiai_official\"