:30012,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"BLEACH\",\"native\":\"BLEACH\",\"english\":\"Bleach\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/30012\"}},{\"relationType\":\"PREQUEL\",\"node\":{\"id\":169755,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"BLEACH: Sennen Kessen-hen - Soukoku-tan\",\"native\":\"BLEACH \\u5343\\u5e74\\u8840\\u6226\\u7bc7-\\u76f8\\u524b\\u8b5a-\",\"english\":\"BLEACH: Thousand-Year Blood War - The Conflict\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/169755\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":199408,\"idMal\":62289,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Buchigire Reijou wa Houfuku wo Chikaimashita.: Madousho no Chikara de Sokoku wo Tataki Tsubushimasu\",\"native\":\"\\u30d6\\u30c1\\u5207\\u308c\\u4ee4\\u5b22\\u306f\\u5831\\u5fa9\\u3092\\u8a93\\u3044\\u307e\\u3057\\u305f\\u3002\\u3000\\uff5e\\u9b54\\u5c0e\\u66f8\\u306e\\u529b\\u3067\\u7956\\u56fd\\u3092\\u53e9\\u304d\\u6f70\\u3057\\u307e\\u3059\\uff5e\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2026,\"month\":7,\"day\":null},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Drama\",\"Fantasy\"],\"synonyms\":[\"A Livid Lady\\u2019s Guide to Getting Even: How I Crushed My Homeland with My Mighty Grimoires\"],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":2750,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"LIGHT_NOVEL\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u30d6\\u30c1\\u5207\\u308c\\u4ee4\\u5b22\",\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/199408\",\"description\":\"Elizabeth Leiston, daughter of the influential prime minister, is a picture-perfect lady on the path to becoming the future queen of the Kingdom of Haldoria. But her life takes a sudden turn for the worst when her fianc\\u00e9 makes a show of publicly calling off their engagement. Soon after, he throws her in jail and starts spreading nasty rumors about her. The encouragement Elizabeth receives from her loyal waiting maid, Mireille, and her inner fury are all she needs to reconsider her goals. Why should she continue devoting herself to a country that doesn\\u2019t respect her when she can trample over it instead? She will get even with those who wronged her and bring down the damned kingdom, even if it\\u2019s the last thing she does! Luckily, Elizabeth is no damsel in distress and has seven powerful magic grimoires she won\\u2019t hesitate to use. Get ready because this ruthless lady is out for blood!\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: J-Novel Club)\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx199408-ocRWG4pRWl8f.png\",\"color\":\"#f1ae35\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"DIeeesNOthA\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/DIeeesNOthA\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/219-EwrfceXsqIWg.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/buchigire_anime\"},{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/buchigire-anime.com\\/\"}],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":126,\"name\":\"Studio Comet\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/126\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"ALTERNATIVE\",\"node\":{\"id\":166824,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Buchigire Reijou wa Houfuku wo Chikaimashita.: Madousho no Chikara de Sokoku wo Tataki Tsubushimasu\",\"native\":\"\\u30d6\\u30c1\\u5207\\u308c\\u4ee4\\u5b22\\u306f\\u5831\\u5fa9\\u3092\\u8a93\\u3044\\u307e\\u3057\\u305f\\u3002\\u3000\\uff5e\\u9b54\\u5c0e\\u66f8\\u306e\\u529b\\u3067\\u7956\\u56fd\\u3092\\u53e9\\u304d\\u6f70\\u3057\\u307e\\u3059\\uff5e\",\"english\":\"A Livid Lady\\u2019s Guide to Getting Even: How I Crushed My Homeland with My Mighty Grimoires\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/166824\"}},{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":147275,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Buchigire Reijou 