null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Drama\",\"Romance\"],\"synonyms\":[\"Though I Am an Inept Villainess: Tale of the Butterfly-Rat Body Swap in the Maiden Court\",\"Futsutsuka\"],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":6464,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"LIGHT_NOVEL\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u3075\\u3064\\u3064\\u304b\\u306a\\u60aa\\u5973\",\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/188139\",\"description\":\"As maidens from the Five Clans battle for the Crown Prince\\u2019s heart, jealous Keigetsu uses forbidden magic to swap bodies with the beloved Reirin. Switching places does not guarantee happiness for Keigetsu with her new body's ill health leaving her hanging on the verge of death. Meanwhile, Reirin, now wearing the face of a scorned outcast, must answer for Keigetsu\\u2019s crimes in a dangerous trial.\\n<br><br>\\nThe unlikely pair become increasingly entangled in each other\\u2019s lives and they will need to work together to survive after discovering the dark conspiracies brewing beneath the palace's genial surface. To confront the deadly threats lurking in the shadows, Reirin must embrace her new identity and defy their expectations of the court's inept villainess.<br><br>\\n(Source: Crunchyroll)\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx188139-ldRLGjjXFA15.png\",\"color\":\"#ff5d43\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"h1VGTiNBNt4\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/h1VGTiNBNt4\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/futsutsuka.net\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/219-EwrfceXsqIWg.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/futsutsuka_PR\"},{\