\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Comedy\",\"Fantasy\"],\"synonyms\":[],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":2387,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"LIGHT_NOVEL\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u30aa\\u30fc\\u30eb\\u30ef\\u30fc\\u30af\\u30b9\\u30e1\\u30a4\\u30c9\",\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/192800\",\"description\":\"\\u201cI will become the world\\u2019s most wonderful maid!\\u201d <br><br>\\nWith her skirt fluttering in black and white, the girl shouted. Her name is Melody. A reincarnated former Japanese girl, she now pursues her dream in her new life, working as an all-purpose maid for a poor count\\u2019s family in the kingdom of Th\\u00e9olas. When she makes it, even cheap tea turns into a luxury brew, and a dilapidated mansion is quickly restored to new! Cleaning, serving, hunting, DIY\\u2014leave it all to her and her powerful magic. Unbeknownst to Melody, this world is actually an otome game, and she is the most powerful and invincible heroine, the saint! Yet, she remains oblivious to this fact. Romance with handsome men? Attacks by the Demon Lord? Work comes first! A fantasy of misunderstood work that unknowingly shatters destiny!\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: Seven Seas Entertainment)\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx192800-ukroJjX3tX7H.jpg\",\"color\":\"#e45da1\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"TlC4LJSA13Y\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/TlC4LJSA13Y\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/17-R0tMgOvwvhsS.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/allworks_maid\"},{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/all-works-maid-anime.com\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Crunchyroll\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/5-AWN2pVlluCOO.png\",\"color\":\"#F88B24\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/crunchyroll.com\"}],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":6125,\"name\":\"EMT Squared\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/6125\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":128801,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Heroine? Seijo? Iie, All Works Maid desu (ko)!\",\"native\":\"\\u30d2\\u30ed\\u30a4\\u30f3\\uff1f\\u8056\\u5973\\uff1f\\u3044\\u3044\\u3048\\u3001\\u30aa\\u30fc\\u30eb\\u30ef\\u30fc\\u30af\\u30b9\\u30e1\\u30a4\\u30c9\\u3067\\u3059\\uff08\\u8a87\\uff09\\uff01\",\"english\":\"Heroine? Saint? No, I\\u2019m an All-Works Maid (And Proud of It)!\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/128801\"}},{\"relationType\":\"ALTERNATIVE\",\"node\":{\"id\":133953,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Heroine? Seijo? Iie, All Works Maid desu (ko)! @COMIC\",\"native\":\"\\u30d2\\u30ed\\u30a4\\u30f3\\uff1f\\u8056\\u5973\\uff1f\\u3044\\u3044\\u3048\\u3001\\u30aa\\u30fc\\u30eb\\u30ef\\u30fc\\u30af\\u30b9\\u30e1\\u30a4\\u30c9\\u3067\\u3059\\uff08\\u8a87\\uff09\\uff01\\uff20COMIC\",\"english\":\"Heroine? Saint? No, I\\u2019m an All-Works Maid (And Proud of It)!\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/133953\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":195833,\"idMal\":62031,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Honoo no Toukyuujyo Dodge Danko\",\"native\":\"\\u708e\\u306e\\u95d8\\u7403\\u5973 \\u30c9\\u30c3\\u30b8\\u5f3e\\u5b50\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2026,\"month\":7,\"day\":null},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Comedy\",\"Sports\"],\"synonyms\":[],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":383,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"MANGA\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u30c9\\u30c3\\u30b8\\u5f3e\\u5b50\\u30a2\\u30cb\\u30e1\",\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/195833\",\"description\":\"The sequel to the legendary dodgeball manga <i>Honou no Toukyuuji Dodge Danpei<\\/i>! In this modern version of the hot-blooded dodgeball story, Danpei's daughter, Danko, follows in his footsteps, struggling to build a dodgeball team with the strongest fighting spirit in the modern age of 2025! Can Danko overcome the apathetic attitude of today's world? \\n<BR><BR>\\n(Source: Corocoro, translated)\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx195833-VejCdIj1VbJG.png\",\"color\":\"#43bbf1\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"eQ8GH0w2sZo\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/eQ8GH0w2sZo\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/dodge-danko.com\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/219-EwrfceXsqIWg.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/dodge_danko\"}],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":7693,\"name\":\"CUE\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/7693\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":158458,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Honoo no Toukyuujyo Dodge Danko\",\"native\":\"\\u708e\\u306e\\u95d8\\u7403\\u5973 \\u30c9\\u30c3\\u30b8\\u5f3e\\u5b50\",\"english\":null},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/158458\"}},{\"relationType\":\"PREQUEL\",\"node\":{\"id\":2228,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Honoo no Toukyuuji: Dodge Danpei\",\"native\":\"\\u708e\\u306e\\u95d8\\u7403\\u5150\\u30fb\\u30c9\\u30c3\\u30b8\\u5f3e\\u5e73\",\"english\":null},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/2228\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":196356,\"idMal\":62102,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Ibitte Konai Gibo to Gishi\",\"native\":\"\\u3044\\u3073\\u3063\\u3066\\u3053\\u306a\\u3044\\u7fa9\\u6bcd\\u3068\\u7fa9\\u59c9\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2026,\"month\":7,\"day\":null},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Comedy\",\"Slice of Life\"],\"synonyms\":[\"My Stepmother and Stepsisters Aren\\u2019t Wicked\",\"My mother-in-law and sister-in-law who don't bully me.\"],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":1592,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"MANGA\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":null,\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/196356\",\"description\":\"Miya is the illegitimate child of a prominent family. When her mother dies and her father\\u2019s estate agrees to take her in, she\\u2019s convinced she knows what awaits her in her new home: a life of servitude and misery at the hands of her wicked stepmother and stepsisters. Yet when she finally meets the women she expects to treat her like dirt, they actually end up being\\u2026sweet?! A hilarious and heartfelt comedy that\\u2019s sure to put a smile on your face!\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: Seven Seas Entertainment)\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx196356-TCzvR9Fht79a.jpg\",\"color\":\"#e44350\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"2DqmMItlgfQ\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/2DqmMItlgfQ\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/ibikona-anime.com\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/17-R0tMgOvwvhsS.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/ibikona_anime\"}],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":7683,\"name\":\"NEWON\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/7683\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":137202,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Ibitte Konai Gibo to Gishi\",\"native\":\"\\u3044\\u3073\\u30