: Kodansha USA)\",\"bannerImage\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/banner\\/187260-HMkLPy3ZvzW1.jpg\",\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx187260-ZGbR8hF953lj.jpg\",\"color\":\"#86aee4\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"OYIv6-LQGCY\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/OYIv6-LQGCY\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/kimishinu-anime.com\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/17-R0tMgOvwvhsS.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/anime_kimishinu\"}],\"rankings\":[{\"rank\":50,\"type\":\"POPULAR\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":false},{\"rank\":4,\"type\":\"POPULAR\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"allTime\":false}],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":7475,\"name\":\"ROLL2\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/7475\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":104045,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Kimi ga Shinu made Koi wo Shitai\",\"native\":\"\\u304d\\u307f\\u304c\\u6b7b\\u306c\\u307e\\u3067\\u604b\\u3092\\u3057\\u305f\\u3044\",\"english\":\"I Want to Love You Till Your Dying Day\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/104045\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":200637,\"idMal\":62811,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Kimi no Koto ga Dai Dai Dai Dai Daisuki na 100-nin no Kanojo 3rd Season\",\"native\":\"\\u541b\\u306e\\u3053\\u3068\\u304c\\u5927\\u5927\\u5927\\u5927\\u5927\\u597d\\u304d\\u306a100\\u4eba\\u306e\\u5f7c\\u5973 \\u7b2c3\\u671f\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2026,\"month\":7,\"day\":5},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Comedy\",\"Ecchi\",\"Romance\"],\"synonyms\":[\"The 100 Girlfriends Who Really,