png\",\"color\":\"#f1e45d\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"XBqUZYpEcfk\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/XBqUZYpEcfk\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/kaikigumi.com\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/17-R0tMgOvwvhsS.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/kaikigumi\"}],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":6074,\"name\":\"C-Station\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/6074\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":162148,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Let's Go Kaikigumi\",\"native\":\"\\u30ec\\u30c3\\u30c4\\u30b4\\u30fc\\u602a\\u5947\\u7d44\",\"english\":null},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/162148\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[{\"episode\":1,\"airingAt\":1783193400},{\"episode\":2,\"airingAt\":1783798200}]}},{\"id\":197715,\"idMal\":62322,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"LV999 no Murabito\",\"native\":\"LV999\\u306e\\u6751\\u4eba\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2026,\"month\":7,\"day\":null},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Adventure\",\"Comedy\",\"Fantasy\"],\"synonyms\":[\"The Villager of Level 999\"],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":5026,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"LIGHT_NOVEL\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":null,\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/197715\",\"description\":\"In this world, the concept of levels exist. Other than those who live off defeating monsters, most people are only around Level 1 to 5. What's more, not just anyone can go out to hunt monsters; it's heavily influenced by one's role anointed by god. There are eight such eligible roles. Warriors. Fighters. Clerics. Magicians. Rogues. Merchants. Hunters. Sorcerers. Those blessed with extraordinary power are divided into three types. Royalty. Heroes. Sages. But for the majority of the population, they have no such powers and live by farming or running shops. Towns are developed by those with the weakest role\\u2026Villagers.\\n<br><br>\\nFor the powerless Villagers going out to hunt monsters is equivalent to committing suicide. But one day, a certain two-year-old child given the role of Villager notices something.\\n<br><br>\\nOnce you defeat a monster\\u2026 you can earn great wealth.\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx197715-KLFLxU24U1uL.png\",\"color\":\"#5daef1\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"IMKro1SWUzw\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/IMKro1SWUzw\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/lv999-anime.com\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/17-R0tMgOvwvhsS.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/lv999_anime\"}],\"rankings\":[{\"rank\":26,\"type\":\"POPULAR\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"allTime\":false}],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":112,\"name\":\"Brain's Base\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/112\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":86763,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"LV999 no Murabito\",\"native\":\"LV999\\u306e\\u6751\\u4eba\",\"english\":null},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/86763\"}},{\"relationType\":\"ALTERNATIVE\",\"node\":{\"id\":99410,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"LV999 no Murabito\",\"native\":\"LV999\\u306e\\u6751\\u4eba\",\"english\":\"The Level 999 Villager\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/99410\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":185875,\"idMal\":60637,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Magical Girl Lyrical Nanoha EXCEEDS Gun Blaze Vengeance\",\"native\":\"\\u9b54\\u6cd5\\u5c11\\u5973\\u30ea\\u30ea\\u30ab\\u30eb\\u306a\\u306e\\u306f EXCEEDS Gun Blaze Vengeance\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2026,\"month\":7,\"day\":5},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Comedy\",\"Drama\",\"Fantasy\",\"Mahou Shoujo\"],\"synonyms\":[\"NANOHA EXGV\"],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":3049,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"ORIGINAL\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u306a\\u306e\\u306fEXGV #\\u306a\\u306e\\u306f #nanoha #\\u306a\\u306e\\u306f20th\",\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/185875\",\"description\":\"Thirty years ago, the world was nearly destroyed by the sudden appearance of unknown \\\"invasive alien species.\\\"\\n<br><br>\\nHumans and these \\u201cinvasive species\\u201d continue to vie for living space, and while humanity\\u2019s safety is currently barely secured, the world could be destroyed at any moment. Living in fear of death and destruction, people go about their daily lives as if trying to avert their eyes from danger and disaster.\\n<br><br>\\nIn this world, the United Nations Hazardous Species Investigation Agency, \\\"EXCEEDS,\\\" has begun operations to ward off crises and disasters caused by invasive species.\\n<br><br>\\nThe story begins on the island nation of \\\"Mizuho\\\" in the Far East. Shina Hisase is a young invasive species extermination hunter living on a remote island. What incident will befall Shina, who wishes only to live quietly with her younger sister Setsuna, her sole remaining family member?\\n<br><br>\\n<i>Note: The first episode aired with a runtime of ~60 minutes as opposed to the standard 24 minute long episode.<\\/i>\",\"bannerImage\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/banner\\/185875-kHVsTIJKPVRJ.jpg\",\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx185875-86GIL6o4uhdK.png\",\"color\":\"#e4860d\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"0kgUsF8R7JM\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/0kgUsF8R7JM\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/219-EwrfceXsqIWg.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/exgv_official\"},{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/nanoha.com\\/EXGV\\/\"}],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":35,\"name\":\"Seven Arcs\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/35\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"PREQUEL\",\"node\":{\"id\":99614,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Mahou Shoujo Lyrical Nanoha Detonation\",\"native\":\"\\u9b54\\u6cd5\\u5c11\\u5973\\u30ea\\u30ea\\u30ab\\u30eb\\u306a\\u306e\\u306f Detonation\",\"english\":\"Magical Girl Lyrical Nanoha Detonation\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/99614\"}},{\"relationType\":\"PREQUEL\",\"node\":{\"id\":187575,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Mahou Shoujo Lyrical Nanoha EXCEEDS\",\"native\":\"\\u9b54\\u6cd5\\u5c11\\u5973\\u30ea\\u30ea\\u30ab\\u30eb\\u306a\\u306e\\u306f EXCEEDS\",\"english\":null},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/187575\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[{\"episode\":1,\"airingAt\":1783180800},{\"episode\":2,\"airingAt\":1783785600}]}},{\"id\":196219,\"idMal\":62080,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Mujikaku Seijo wa Kyou mo Muishiki ni Chikara wo Tare Nagasu\",\"native\":\"\\u7121\\u81ea\\u899a\\u8056\\u5973\\u306f\\u4eca\\u65e5\\u3082\\u7121\\u610f\\u8b58\\u306b\\u529b\\u3092\\u5782\\u308c\\u6d41\\u3059\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2026,\"month\":7,\"day\":null},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Drama\",\"Fantasy\",\"Romance\"],\"synonyms\":[\"The Oblivious Saint Can't Contain Her Power Glossary\"],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":1898,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"LIGHT_NOVEL\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\" #\\u7121\\u81ea\\u899a\\u8056\\u5973\",\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/196219\",\"description\":\"Lady Carolina, the overlooked daughter of a powerful duke, has always believed herself to be the black sheep amid her illustrious kin. Her father is the distinguished prime minister; her elder sister, a prodigious mage destined to become their nation\\u2019s next Saint. In comparison, Carolina resigns herself to a quiet existence in their shadows until a sudden and unexpected royal decree alters her destiny, thrusting her into a political marriage with the formidable \\u201cBloodthirsty Prince\\u201d of the neighboring Empire of Malcosias. Determined to prove her worth, Carolina takes a bold step into a world fraught with both political and mortal peril. As royal obligations intertwine with hints of true love and the stirrings of her own latent power, Carolina moves ever closer to understanding what it truly means to be exceptional.\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: J-Novel Club)\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx196219-DDDl1gkhj6hO.png\",\"color\":\"#35aef1\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"q95fc3ip9nQ\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/q95fc3ip9nQ\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/219-EwrfceXsqIWg.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/mujikaku_seijo\"},{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/mujikaku-seijo.com\\/\"}],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":207,\"name\":\"Magic Bus\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/207\"},{\"id\":6945,\"name\":\"