,\"\\u0411\\u0435\\u0433\\u043b\\u044b\\u0439 \\u0441\\u0430\\u043c\\u0443\\u0440\\u0430\\u0439\"],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":12790,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"MANGA\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u9003\\u3052\\u82e5 #\\u9003\\u3052\\u4e0a\\u624b\\u306e\\u82e5\\u541b\",\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/182616\",\"description\":\"The second season of <i>Nige Jouzu no Wakagimi<\\/i>.\",\"bannerImage\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/banner\\/182616-kmIqMEUsLYrO.jpg\",\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx182616-ZOCgArw9cgqI.jpg\",\"color\":\"#e45050\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"ZKY5R3r5a3M\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/ZKY5R3r5a3M\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/17-R0tMgOvwvhsS.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/twitter.com\\/nigewaka_anime\"},{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/219-EwrfceXsqIWg.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/_elusivesamurai\"},{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/nigewaka.run\\/\"}],\"rankings\":[{\"rank\":94,\"type\":\"POPULAR\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":false},{\"rank\":15,\"type\":\"POPULAR\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"allTime\":false}],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":6222,\"name\":\"CloverWorks\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/6222\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":128666,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Nige Jouzu no Wakagimi\",\"native\":\"\\u9003\\u3052\\u4e0a\\u624b\\u306e\\u82e5\\u541b\",\"english\":\"The Elusive Samurai\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/128666\"}},{\"relationType\":\"PREQUEL\",\"node\":{\"id\":162896,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Nige Jouzu no Wakagimi\",\"native\":\"\\u9003\\u3052\\u4e0a\\u624b\\u306e\\u82e5\\u541b\",\"english\":\"The Elusive Samurai\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/162896\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":103303,\"idMal\":62856,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Nijuuseiki Denki Mokuroku: Eureka\\u30fbEvrika\",\"native\":\"\\u4e8c\\u5341\\u4e16\\u7d00\\u96fb\\u6c23\\u76ee\\u9332-\\u30e6\\u30fc\\u30ec\\u30ab\\u30fb\\u30a8\\u30f4\\u30ea\\u30ab-\",\"english\":\"Sparks of Tomorrow\"},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2026,\"month\":7,\"day\":5},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Adventure\",\"Romance\"],\"synonyms\":[\"20th Century Electricity Catalogue\",\"Twentieth Century Electrical Records\",\"A Luz do Futuro\"],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":20135,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"NOVEL\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u4e8c\\u5341\\u4e16\\u7d00\\u96fb\\u6c23\\u76ee\\u9332 #sparks_of_tomorrow\",\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/103303\",\"description\":\"The novel takes place in the summer of 1907, the 40th year of the Meiji era. 15-year-old Inako Momokawa lives in the Fushimi area of Kyoto, and is the second daughter of a sake brewer. Nothing she does ever comes out right, and she receives a scolding from her father every day. Her only relief is the trust she places in her prayers to the gods. One day while at Fushimi Inari shrine, she meets a freewheeling young man named Kihachi Sakamoto. He rejects the gods, and boasts of the incoming age of electricity. <br><br>\\n\\nThe topic of marriage suddenly comes up in Inako's household. Her father is one-sidedly making all the decisions for her, and Inako is about to give up hope. It is then that Kihachi draws out Inako's true feelings of wanting to run away from her family. The only way to stop her marriage is to find an unusual book called the \\\"Electricity Catalog.\\\" The book is a prediction book about electricity that Kihachi wrote when he was a child, but his older brother Seiroku took the book, and its current whereabouts are unknown. Inako and Kihachi together go in search of the book across Kyoto and Shiga prefectures.<br><br>\\n\\n(Source: Anime News Network)\",\"bannerImage\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/banner\\/103303-K73aVOqkCPqL.jpg\",\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx103303-qWzNx2EaWT78.jpg\",\"color\":\"#e48643\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"7ObipYqbOd8\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/7ObipYqbOd8\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/www.kyotoanimation.co.jp\\/books\\/20thdenmoku\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/219-EwrfceXsqIWg.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/denkimokuroku\"},{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/denkimokuroku.jp\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/denkimokuroku.jp\\/en\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Instagram\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/48-VFlxaXGaNqXk.png\",\"color\":\"#833AB4\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.instagram.com\\/denkimokuroku\"},{\"site\":\"TikTok\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/196-o2g5cLUG6k5V.png\",\"color\":\"#010101\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.tiktok.com\\/@denkimokuroku_\"},{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.threads.com\\/@denkimokuroku\"},{\"site\":\"Bluesky\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/241-sKyRMwhzfSAu.png\",\"color\":\"#0085FF\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/bsky.app\\/profile\\/sparks-of-tmr.bsky.social\"},{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/219-EwrfceXsqIWg.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/Sparks_of_Tmr\"},{\"site\":\"Netflix\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/10-rVGPom8RCiwH.png\",\"color\":\"#E50914\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.netflix.com\\/title\\/\"}],\"rankings\":[{\"rank\":61,\"type\":\"POPULAR\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":false},{\"rank\":7,\"type\":\"POPULAR\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"allTime\":false}],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":2,\"name\":\"Kyoto Animation\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/2\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"OTHER\",\"node\":{\"id\":157175,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Kyoto Animation:  Meiji-hen\",\"native\":\"\\u4eac\\u90fd\\u30a2\\u30cb\\u30e1\\u30fc\\u30b7\\u30e7\\u30f3 CM\\u300c\\u660e\\u6cbb\\u7de8\\u300d\",\"english\":null},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/157175\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[{\"episode\":1,\"airingAt\":1783260000},{\"episode\":2,\"airingAt\":1783864800}]}},{\"id\":194219,\"idMal\":61814,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Oni no Hanayome\",\"native\":\"\\u9b3c\\u306e\\u82b1\\u5ac1 \",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2026,\"month\":7,\"day\":null},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Drama\",\"Fantasy\",\"Romance\"],\"synonyms\":[\"The Ogre's Bride\",\"OniHana\"],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":2069,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"LIGHT_NOVEL\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u9b3c\\u306e\\u82b1\\u5ac1\",\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/194219\",\"description\":\"A Japanese-style ayakashi Cinderella story! \\\"You're the bride I've been searching for all this time.\\\" The ayakashi and humans coexist in harmony. The ayakashi, having superior abilities and beautiful appearances, sometimes find their partner among human women, making them their \\\"bride\\\". The bride, in exchange for bringing prosperity, receives absolute love from the ayakashi. Yuzu is constantly compared to her sister, a bride of a demon fox, and is resented by her family every day. One day, when Yuzu just couldn't take things anymore, a man appears before her on a bridge. This man is the most beautiful man Yuzu has ever seen... and he's calling her his wife?! \\\"Just be quiet and let me hold you.\\\" The most powerful, \\\"cold-hearted\\\" ayakashi is pouring his heart out for Yuzu?!<br><br>\\n(Source: MangaPlaza)\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx194219-qf7L0SfVi6nc.jpg\",\"color\":\"#f1931a\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"gK4DX0X_snw\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/gK4DX0X_snw\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/219-EwrfceXsqIWg.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/onihana_anime\"},{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/onihana-anime.com\\/\"}],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":6867,\"name\":\"Colored Pencil Animation Japan\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/6867\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"ALTERNATIVE\",\"node\":{\"id\":172089,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Oni no Hanayome\",\"native\":\"\\u9b3c\\u306e\\u82b1\\u5ac1\",\"english\":\"The Ogre's Bride\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/172089\"}},{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":172091,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Oni no Hanayome\",\"native\":\"\\u9b3c\\u306e\\u82b1\\u5ac1 \",\"english\":null},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/172091\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":204466,\"idMal\":63150,\"ti