            "text": "{\"data\":{\"Page\":{\"pageInfo\":{\"hasNextPage\":false,\"total\":59},\"media\":[{\"id\":207254,\"idMal\":null,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Thunder 3\",\"native\":\"\\u30b5\\u30f3\\u30c0\\u30fc\\uff13\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2026,\"month\":7,\"day\":null},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Adventure\",\"Drama\",\"Sci-Fi\"],\"synonyms\":[],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":418,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"MANGA\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u30b5\\u30f3\\u30c0\\u30fc\\uff13\",\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/207254\",\"description\":\"Three ordinary schoolboys come into possession of a DVD that supposedly opens a gateway to a parallel universe, but when their backs are turned Pyontaro's little sister Futaba passes through and gets kidnapped by the aliens that have overrun that version of Earth! Discovering that their cartoonish bodies make them supermen in the hyper-realistic parallel universe, the boys set out to rescue Futaba.\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: Kodansha USA)\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx207254-StcuNpmZTDCL.jpg\",\"color\":\"#1a93e4\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"AUwRm1MjUTk\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/AUwRm1MjUTk\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/219-EwrfceXsqIWg.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/thunder3_pyon\"},{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/thunder3-anime.com\"},{\"site\":\"TikTok\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/196-o2g5cLUG6k5V.png\",\"color\":\"#010101\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.tiktok.com\\/@thunder3_pyon\"}],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":148439,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Thunder 3\",\"native\":\"\\u30b5\\u30f3\\u30c0\\u30fc3\",\"english\":\"Thunder 3\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/148439\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":202269,\"idMal\":62936,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Toumei na Yoru ni Kakeru Kimi to, Me ni Mienai Koi wo Shita.\",\"native\":\"\\u900f\\u660e\\u306a\\u591c\\u306b\\u99c6\\u3051\\u308b\\u541b\\u3068\\u3001\\u76ee\\u306b\\u898b\\u3048\\u306a\\u3044\\u604b\\u3092\\u3057\\u305f\\u3002\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2026,\"month\":7,\"day\":null},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Drama\",\"Romance\"],\"synonyms\":[\"Love Unseen Beneath the Clear Night Sky\"],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":4131,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":null,\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#anime_kakekoi #\\u304b\\u3051\\u604b\",\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/202269\",\"description\":\"On an April night in Tokyo, still too early for fireworks, university student Kakeru Sorano meets a woman named Koharu Fuyutsuki. She is a beautiful girl who stands out from the crowd, laughs a lot, and exudes a warmth that contrasts sharply with Kakeru's own introversion. But there was something Kakeru didn't know at first\\u2014she can't see.<br>\\n<br>\\nUnlike Kakeru, Koharu hasn't given up on anything, even with her blindness. She attends university daily, shows interest in clubs, makes friends\\u2014and dreams of launching fireworks one day. Kakeru wonders why, when she can't see them...but maybe it doesn't matter. And maybe he can start moving forward, too, for the girl who's always been by his side<br>\\n<br>\\n(Source: Yen Press)\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx202269-YLPqiMg2nsTr.jpg\",\"color\":\"#aea1e4\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"HZW_fbHDsT8\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/HZW_fbHDsT8\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/219-EwrfceXsqIWg.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/anime_kakekoi\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/sh-anime.shochiku.co.jp\\/kakekoi\\/\"}],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":6443,\"name\":\"Makaria\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/6443\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":175916,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Toumei na Yoru ni Kakeru Kimi to, Me ni Mienai Koi wo Shita.\",\"native\":\"\\u900f\\u660e\\u306a\\u591c\\u306b\\u99c6\\u3051\\u308b\\u541b\\u3068\\u3001\\u76ee\\u306b\\u898b\\u3048\\u306a\\u3044\\u604b\\u3092\\u3057\\u305f\\u3002\",\"english\":\"Love Unseen Beneath the Clear Night Sky\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/175916\"}},{\"relationType\":\"ALTERNATIVE\",\"node\":{\"id\":181168,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Toumei na Yoru ni Kakeru Kimi to, Me ni Mienai Koi wo Shita.\",\"native\":\"\\u900f\\u660e\\u306a\\u591c\\u306b\\u99c6\\u3051\\u308b\\u541b\\u3068\\u3001\\u76ee\\u306b\\u898b\\u3048\\u306a\\u3044\\u604b\\u3092\\u3057\\u305f\\u3002\",\"english\":null},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/181168\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":180136,\"idMal\":59741,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Tsuihou Sareta Tensei Juukishi wa Game Chishiki de Musou Suru\",\"native\":\"\\u8ffd\\u653e\\u3055\\u308c\\u305f\\u8ee2\\u751f\\u91cd\\u9a0e\\u58eb\\u306f\\u30b2\\u30fc\\u30e0\\u77e5\\u8b58\\u3067\\u7121\\u53cc\\u3059\\u308b\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2026,\"month\":7,\"day\":3},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Fantasy\"],\"synonyms\":[\"The Exiled Reincarnated Heavy Knight Is Unrivaled in Game Knowledge\",\"The Exiled Heavy Knight Knows How to Game the System\",\"Juukishi\"],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":9350,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"MANGA\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u8ee2\\u751f\\u91cd\\u9a0e\\u58eb\",\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/180136\",\"description\":\"The day a child turns fifteen, they undergo the Ritual of Divine Blessing. Already descended from a line of master swordsman, Elymas was supposed to succeed his father. However, he pulls the defective class, the Heavy Knight, and not only loses his status as future head of the household, but he's also exiled. With their unbalanced stats and seemingly useless skills, Heavy Knights are spoked of as a class for cowards and the lazy. However, Elymas knows the truth. The world he lives in is the same as the one of the game he used to play... It is the Heavy Knight that is the most powerful class of them all. Using memories from his past life, Elymas has set out to effectively conquer this entire world.<br>\\n<br>\\n(Source: K Manga)\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx180136-gtMTCRlOD4OE.jpg\",\"color\":\"#50c9fe\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"g8rvdawGAfc\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/g8rvdawGAfc\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/sh-anime.shochiku.co.jp\\/jukishi-anime\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/219-EwrfceXsqIWg.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/jukishi_anime\"}],\"rankings\":[{\"rank\":18,\"type\":\"POPULAR\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"allTime\":false}],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":309,\"name\":\"GoHands\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/309\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"ALTERNATIVE\",\"node\":{\"id\":150194,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Tsuihou Sareta Tensei Juukishi wa Game Chishiki de Musou Suru\",\"native\":\"\\u8ffd\\u653e\\u3055\\u308c\\u305f\\u8ee2\\u751f\\u91cd\\u9a0e\\u58eb\\u306f\\u30b2\\u30fc\\u30e0\\u77e5\\u8b58\\u3067\\u7121\\u53cc\\u3059\\u308b\",\"english\":null},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/150194\"}},{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":150193,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Tsuihou Sareta Tensei Juukishi wa Game Chishiki de Musou Suru\",\"native\":\"\\u8ffd\\u653e\\u3055\\u308c\\u305f\\u8ee2\\u751f\\u91cd\\u9a0e\\u58eb\\u306f\\u30b2\\u30fc\\u30e0\\u77e5\\u8b58\\u3067\\u7121\\u53cc\\u3059\\u308b\",\"english\":\"The Exiled Heavy Knight Knows How to Game the System\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/150193\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[{\"episode\":1,\"airingAt\":1783005960},{\"episode\":2,\"airingAt\":1783610760}]}},{\"id\":203490,\"idMal\":63061,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Uchi no Otouto-domo ga Sumimasen\",\"native\":\"\\u3046\\u3061\\u306e\\u5f1f\\u3069\\u3082\\u304c\\u3059\\u307f\\u307e\\u305b\\u3093\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2026,\"month\":7,\"day\":4},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Comedy\",\"Romance\",\"Slice of Life\"],\"synonyms\":[],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":1295,\"episodes\":24,\"source\":\"MANGA\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u3046\\u3061\\u5f1f\\u30a2\\u30cb\\u30e1\",\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/203490\",\"description\":\"The manga centers on high school student Ito Hazui. During her spring break at the end of her first year of high school, Ito's mother remarries, and Ito moves to live with her new family, becoming Ito Narita. Upon arriving at her new house, Ito is shocked to learn she now has four younger step-brothers. Ito tries her hardest to get along with all of the new members of her family, but the eldest brother Gen is a bit cold to her. However, under his aloof facade, he occasionally shows his kindness.\\n<BR><BR>\\n(Source: Anime News Network)\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx203490-D6GOKA0OWblB.jpg\",\"color\":\"#fef150\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"Mqbl2gcETcc\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/Mqbl2gcETcc\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/uchioto-anime.com\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/219-EwrfceXsqIWg.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/uchioto_anime\"}],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":6075,\"name\":\"Lay-duce\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/6075\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":117345,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Uchi no Otoutodomo ga Sumimasen\",\"native\":\"\\u3046\\u3061\\u306e\\u5f1f\\u3068\\u3099\\u3082\\u304b\\u3099\\u3059\\u307f\\u307e\\u305b\\u3093\",\"english\":null},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/117345\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[{\"episode\":1,\"airingAt\":1783090800},{\"episode\":2,\"airingAt\":1783695600}]}},{\"id\":207674,\"idMal\":63468,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Ushiro no Shoumen Kamui-san\",\"native\":\"\\u3046\\u3057\\u308d\\u306e\\u6b63\\u9762\\u30ab\\u30e0\\u30a4\\u3055\\u3093\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2026,\"month\":7,\"day\":null},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Comedy\",\"Ecchi\",\"Supernatural\"],\"synonyms\":[\"Kamui-san Directly Behind You\",\"\\u5f9e\\u5f8c\\u9762\\u4f86\\u7684\\u795e\\u5a01\\u5148\\u751f\",\"\\u0e04\\u0e38\\u0e13\\u0e04\\u0e32\\u0e21\\u0e38\\u0e22\\u0e25\\u0e38\\u0e22\\u0e2b\\u0e25\\u0e31\\u0e07\\u0e1c\\u0e35\"],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":789,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"MANGA\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u30a2\\u30cb\\u30e1\\u30ab\\u30e0\\u30a4\\u3055\\u3093\",\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/207674\",\"description\":\"Shizuka is a normal high school girl with the ability to see ghosts. Due to her peculiar tendency to attract ghosts, she works as an assistant to Kamui, a famous psychic. Kamui takes pride in his top-notch psychic abilities, but the way he exorcises ghosts is rather unusual!\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: Shogakukan, translated)\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx207674-ZRbpzoqzO0tB.png\",\"color\":\"#50bbe4\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"E38a1CztXa4\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/E38a1CztXa4\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/219-EwrfceXsqIWg.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/anime_kamuisan\"},{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/kamuisan.deregula.com\\/\"}],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":6117,\"name\":\"Zero-G\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/6117\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":123898,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Ushiro no Shoumen Kamui-san\",\"native\":\"\\u3046\\u3057\\u308d\\u306e\\u6b63\\u9762\\u30ab\\u30e0\\u30a4\\u3055\\u3093\",\"english\":null},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/123898\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":206521,\"idMal\":63347,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"World Is Dancing\",\"native\":\"\\u30ef\\u30fc\\u30eb\\u30c9 \\u30a4\\u30ba \\u30c0\\u30f3\\u30b7\\u30f3\\u30b0\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2026,\"month\":7,\"day\":2},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Drama\"],\"synonyms\":[],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":5705,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"MANGA\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u30ef\\u30fc\\u30eb\\u30c9\\u30a4\\u30ba\\u30c0\\u30f3\\u30b7\\u30f3\\u30b0 \",\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/206521\",\"description\":\"Born into a life of acting and dance with a traveling theater troupe in 14th-century Japan, 12-year old Oniyasha has one problem\\u2014he doesn't know what the point of any of it is. \\\"Why must I step with the left foot here instead of the right? Why is one performance good and another, bad? Why do people dance at all?\\\" It all seems perfectly arbitrary, until a chance encounter in a run-down shack sets him down a path to revolutionizing the art form and influencing much of Japanese culture to come. A fictionalized account of the early life of Zeami Motokiyo (Oniyasha), the founder of modern Noh theater\\u2014the world's oldest surviving theater art\\u2014this coming-of-age artist's journey vividly brings to life a man far ahead of his time during one of Japan's most culturally and socially vibrant eras.<br><br>\\n\\n(Source: Kodansha Comics)\",\"bannerImage\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/banner\\/206521-zCIAGsiIkh6G.jpg\",\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx206521-ecJuDgjth84C.png\",\"color\":\"#e45d78\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"Zu45LJG7Chs\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/Zu45LJG7Chs\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/sh-anime.shochiku.co.jp\\/worldisdancing-anime\\/en\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/219-EwrfceXsqIWg.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/wid_anime\"},{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/sh-anime.shochiku.co.jp\\/worldisdancing-anime\\/\"}],\"rankings\":[{\"rank\":24,\"type\":\"POPULAR\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"allTime\":false}],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":7805,\"name\":\"Cypic\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/7805\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":131824,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"World Is Dancing\",\"native\":\"\\u30ef\\u30fc\\u30eb\\u30c9 \\u30a4\\u30ba \\u30c0\\u30f3\\u30b7\\u30f3\\u30b0\",\"english\":\"The World Is Dancing\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/131824\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[{\"episode\":1,\"airingAt\":1782997200},{\"episode\":2,\"airingAt\":1783602000}]}},{\"id\":207141,\"idMal\":63403,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Yani Neko\",\"native\":\"\\u30e4\\u30cb\\u306d\\u3053\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2026,\"month\":7,\"day\":3},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Comedy\",\"Slice of Life\"],\"synonyms\":[\"Chainsmoker Cat\"],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":6644,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"MANGA\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u30e4\\u30cb\\u306d\\u3053\",\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/207141\",\"description\":\"Yani is a catgirl with a seriously bad smoking habit. She smokes so much that her apartment smells like ash and is littered with cigarette butts\\u2014and plenty of other trash! Every time she tries to quit, she becomes weak to the cravings and gives in almost instantly. Will she ever get her life together, or is she doomed to live as a chainsmoking slob forever? \\n<BR><BR>\\n(Source: Seven Seas Entertainment)\",\"bannerImage\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/banner\\/207141-MvHAS2YVfJzL.jpg\",\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx207141-qaJCCdx1DWtK.jpg\",\"color\":\"#f1ae00\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"7tfxuLFVu7o\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/7tfxuLFVu7o\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/yanineko-anime.com\"},{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/219-EwrfceXsqIWg.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/yanineko_anime\"},{\"site\":\"YouTube\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/13-ZwR1Xwgtyrwa.png\",\"color\":\"#FF0000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/@yanineko_anime\"}],\"rankings\":[{\"rank\":22,\"type\":\"POPULAR\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"allTime\":false}],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":6180,\"name\":\"Bibury Animation Studios\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/6180\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":162552,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Yani Neko\",\"native\":\"\\u30e4\\u30cb\\u306d\\u3053\",\"english\":\"Chainsmoker Cat\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/162552\"}},{\"relationType\":\"SIDE_STORY\",\"node\":{\"id\":208105,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Yani Neko Mini\",\"native\":\"\\u30e4\\u30cb\\u306d\\u3053 \\u30df\\u30cb\",\"english\":null},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/208105\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[{\"episode\":1,\"airingAt\":1783006200},{\"episode\":2,\"airingAt\":1783611000}]}},{\"id\":209800,\"idMal\":63047,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Yoroi Shinden Samurai Troopers Part 2\",\"native\":