here he feels like himself. But when he is about to be separated from Ben-chan due to being sent to a children's home, Minato prays to a Shiranuhi, a mysterious light floating above the sea, to grant him one wish. His wish, filled with hatred towards his father, eventually becomes a curse.<br><br>\\n(Source: Anime News Network)<br><br>\\n<i>Note: Initially teased at AnimeJapan 2024 in the CoMix Wave Films booth, a visual of this project was shown off with a description being a new animation project by a \\\"rookie director\\\".<\\/i>\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx176373-GkYDehw14rxJ.jpg\",\"color\":\"#f1c978\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"ixva4keCFsU\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/ixva4keCFsU\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/219-EwrfceXsqIWg.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/shiranuhi_movie\"},{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/gaga.ne.jp\\/shiranuhi\\/\"}],\"rankings\":[{\"rank\":38,\"type\":\"POPULAR\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":false}],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":291,\"name\":\"CoMix Wave\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/291\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[{\"episode\":1,\"airingAt\":1787238000}]}},{\"id\":206682,\"idMal\":63356,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Soreike! Anpanman: Pantan to Yakusoku no Hoshi\",\"native\":\"\\u305d\\u308c\\u3044\\u3051\\uff01\\u30a2\\u30f3\\u30d1\\u30f3\\u30de\\u30f3\\u3000\\u30d1\\u30f3\\u30bf\\u30f3\\u3068\\u7d04\\u675f\\u306e\\u661f\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2026,\"month\":6,\"day\":26},\"endDate\":{\"year\":2026,\"month\":6,\"day\":26},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"format\":\"MOVIE\",\"genres\":[\"Comedy\",\"Fantasy\"],\"synonyms\":[],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":49,\"episodes\":1,\"source\":\"ORIGINAL\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u6620\\u753b\\u30a2\\u30f3\\u30d1\\u30f3\\u30de\\u30f3\",\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/206682\",\"description\":\"Pantan is a red panda who seeks to find the treasure thought to be in a rainbow star in the night sky, in order to keep a promise made to an adventurer long ago. When Pantan and Anpanman encounter each other, Anpanman lends his abilities to help out Pantan.\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: Anime News Network)\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx206682-CV51UmTvQJ84.png\",\"color\":\"#1a436b\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"aq_wssZBWKw\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/aq_wssZBWKw\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/anpan-movie.com\\/2026\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/219-EwrfceXsqIWg.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/anpanman_movie\"}],\"rankings\":[{\"rank\":52,\"type\":\"POPULAR\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":false}],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"PARENT\",\"node\":{\"id\":1960,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Sore Ike! Anpanman\",\"native\":\"\\u305d\\u308c\\u3044\\u3051!\\u30a2\\u30f3\\u30d1\\u30f3\\u30de\\u30f3\",\"english\":null},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/1960\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[{\"episode\":1,\"airingAt\":1782399600}]}},{\"id\":211308,\"idMal\":64012,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"THE RIBBON HERO\",\"native\":\"THE RIBBON HERO\",\"english\":\"THE RIBBON HERO\"},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2026,\"month\":8,\"day\":null},\"endDate\":{\"year\":2026,\"month\":8,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"format\":\"MOVIE\",\"genres\":[],\"synonyms\":[\"\\u30ea\\u30dc\\u30f3\\u3078\\u30fc\\u30ed\\u30fc\"],\"duration\":109,\"popularity\":1903,\"episodes\":1,\"source\":null,\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#RIBBONHERO #\\u30ea\\u30dc\\u30f3\\u30d2\\u30fc\\u30ed\\u30fc\",\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/211308\",\"description\":\"Inspired by Osamu Tezuka's legendary manga \\\"Princess Knight,\\\" witness a lone hero attempt to overcome their harsh destiny in THE RIBBON HERO.<br><br>\\n(Source: Netflix)\",\"bannerImage\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/banner\\/211308-rt6JyaaKkF6n.jpg\",\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx211308-DHKjEEttkfkT.jpg\",\"color\":\"#785df1\"},\"trailer\":null,\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Netflix\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/10-rVGPom8RCiwH.png\",\"color\":\"#E50914\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.netflix.com\\/title\\/81493703\"},{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.theribbonhero.com\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/219-EwrfceXsqIWg.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/the_ribbon_hero\"}],\"rankings\":[{\"rank\":28,\"type\":\"POPULAR\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":false}],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":6912,\"name\":\"OUTLINE\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/6912\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"PARENT\",\"node\":{\"id\":31676,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Ribbon no Kishi\",\"native\":\"\\u30ea\\u30dc\\u30f3\\u306e\\u9a0e\\u58eb\",\"english\":\"Princess Knight\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/31676\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":208754,\"idMal\":null,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Unanswered\\/\\/butterfly: Sword Art Online\",\"native\":\"Unanswered\\/\\/butterfly: Sword Art Online\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2026,\"month\":7,\"day\":10},\"endDate\":{\"year\":2026,\"month\":7,\"day\":10},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"format\":\"MOVIE\",\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Adventure\"],\"synonyms\":[],\"duration\":110,\"popularity\":2664,\"episodes\":1,\"source\":\"VIDEO_GAME\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":null,\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/208754\",\"description\":\"The world\\u2019s first full-dive VRMMO, Sword Art Online\\u2014known as SAO. What was meant to be a dream come true has instead transformed into a deadly game where dying in the virtual world means dying in reality.<br><br>\\nEmirun and Rex, who once knew each other in the real world, reunite by chance within SAO. They join a scouting party to learn how to survive in this unforgiving world. One day, however, they encounter a mysterious PK (Player Killer) known only as the Black Swordsman. When Emirun rushes to the scene, she finds Rex collapsed in despair, and the Black Swordsman standing over him. The one who wiped out their entire scouting party\\u2014was the Black Swordsman.<br><br>\\nDetermined to avenge their fallen comrades, Emirun and Rex seek out the legendary prodigy swordswoman Asuna, and begin intense training under her guidance. In a death game where even players turn against one another, what new beginning will these two reach at the end of their struggle\\u2026?<br><br>(Source: Official Site, translated)<br><br>\\n<i>Note: Released as part of the Echoes of Aincrad: Sword Art Online's game limited edition.<\\/i>\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx208754-333Nyh5abrqS.png\",\"color\":\"#e4a150\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"tv1EZbG8pLI\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/tv1EZbG8pLI\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/eoa.sao-game.jp\\/unanswered_butterfly\\/\"}],\"rankings\":[{\"rank\":23,\"type\":\"POPULAR\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":false}],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":6067,\"name\":\"POLYGON PICTURES\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/6067\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"ALTERNATIVE\",\"node\":{\"id\":51479,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Sword Art Online\",\"native\":\"\\u30bd\\u30fc\\u30c9\\u30a2\\u30fc\\u30c8\\u30fb\\u30aa\\u30f3\\u30e9\\u30a4\\u30f3\",\"english\":\"Sword Art Online\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/51479\"}},{\"relationType\":\"ALTERNATIVE\",\"node\":{\"id\":11757,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Sword Art Online\",\"native\":\"\\u30bd\\u30fc\\u30c9\\u30a2\\u30fc\\u30c8\\u30fb\\u30aa\\u30f3\\u30e9\\u30a4\\u30f3\",\"english\":\"Sword Art Online\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/11757\"}},{\"relationType\":\"ALTERNATIVE\",\"node\":{\"id\":208753,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Unanswered\\/\\/butterfly: Sword Art Online\",\"native\":\"Unanswered\\/\\/butterfly: Sword Art Online\",\"english\":null},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/208753\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[{\"episode\":1,\"airingAt\":1783609200}]}}]}}}"
