RYO! meet with Tetsudou Musume\"],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":675,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"ORIGINAL\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u3066\\u3064\\u308a\\u3087\\u30fc\",\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/199594\",\"description\":\"Misaki has often felt the urge to break free from everyday life and set out on a journey somewhere far away. Even though she doesn\\u2019t yet know what she wants to become, she longs to find something she can truly be passionate about.<br><br>\\nAt the start of a new chapter on a lively campus, she meets the members of the Railway Travel Research Club\\u2014known as the \\u201cTetsuryo Club.\\u201d As her world unfolds along the railway lines, Misaki\\u2019s heart begins to race with excitement!<br><br>\\nAs TETSUDOU MUSUME celebrates its 20th anniversary, the Tetsuryo Club sets off on a journey through the world where the Railway Girls work, in search of moments of wonder.\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: Pony Canyon Anime)\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx199594-KyZW6uaMiQWg.jpg\",\"color\":\"#f1ae1a\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"lXmAdRvMlbI\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/lXmAdRvMlbI\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/219-EwrfceXsqIWg.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/tetsuryo_anime\"},{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/tetsuryo-anime.com\\/\"}],\"rankings\":[{\"rank\":28,\"type\":\"POPULAR\",\"season\":\"FALL\",\"allTime\":false}],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":6634,\"name\":\"East Fish Studio\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/6634\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"OTHER\",\"node\":{\"id\":44196,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Tetsudou Musume: Terminal Memory\",\"native\":\"\\u9244\\u9053\\u3080\\u3059\\u3081\\uff5eTerminal Memory\\uff5e\",\"english\":null},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/44196\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":186742,\"idMal\":61014,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Toaru Anbu no ITEM\",\"native\":\"\\u3068\\u3042\\u308b\\u6697\\u90e8\\u306e\\u5c11\\u5973\\u5171\\u68f2\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2026,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":\"FALL\",\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Sci-Fi\"],\"synonyms\":[\"A Certain Dark Side's Item\"],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":2870,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"LIGHT_NOVEL\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u5c11\\u5973\\u5171\\u68f2 #\\u30a2\\u30a4\\u30c6\\u30e0 #\\u3068\\u3042\\u308b\",\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/186742\",\"description\":\"This is a story of four girls living in the \\\"Dark Side\\\" of Academy City.<br>\\n<br>\\nIn Academy City where \\\"ESP\\\" has been recognized as a general science. Behind the peace, there is a Dark Side organization that undertakes missions that cannot be made public.<br>\\n<br>\\n\\\"ITEM\\\" is an elite unit consisting of four girls. Takitsubo Rikou is able to read and track the AIM fields emitted by those with abilities. Frenda Seivelun, who excels in combat using explosives and traps.<br>\\n<br>\\nKinuhata Saiai, who can manipulate nitrogen at will and plays a defensive role. And one of the 7 Espers that Academy City is proud of: Mugino Shizuri. They live freely in the darkness of the Academy City, and quietly set their sights on their target...!<br>\\n<br>\\nThis is a story of encounter, friendship, and darkness that eventually leads to a terrible incident!<br>\\n<br>\\n(Source: Kadokawa, translated)\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\