ht\"],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":5417,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"MANGA\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\" #\\u96e8\\u591c\\u306e\\u6708\",\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/184321\",\"description\":\"One day, while rushing to a piano lesson, a girl named Saki collides with someone on the street. As Saki collects herself, the stranger picks up the sheet music Saki dropped, hands it to Saki together with a band-aid, and continues on her way\\u2014all without saying a word. Saki is left wondering about the identity of the tall, lovely stranger, only to discover the next day that she is one of her classmates at her new high school. The girl\\u2019s name is Kanon, and though she is hearing impaired, she refuses any kind of support or \\u201cspecial treatment\\u201d from her teachers or classmates. Over the course of the year, Saki slowly grows closer to Kanon and begins to chip away at her cold exterior.\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: Kodansha USA)\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx184321-WERMIJAUlhf0.jpg\",\"color\":\"#86bbe4\"},\"trailer\":null,\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/219-EwrfceXsqIWg.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/anime_amayo\"},{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/amayonotsuki.jp\\/\"}],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":7263,\"name\":\"CompTown\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/7263\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":136109,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Amayo no Tsuki\",\"native\":\"\\u96e8\\u591c\\u306e\\u6708\",\"english\":\"The Moon on a Rainy Night\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/136109\"}},{\"relationType\":\"CHARACTER\",\"node\":{\"id\":173523,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Egao no Taenai Shokuba desu.\",\"native\":\"\\u7b11\\u9854\\u306e\\u305f\\u3048\\u306a\\u3044\\u8077\\u5834\\u3067\\u3059\\u3002\",\"english\":\"A Mangaka's Weirdly Wonderful Workplace\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/173523\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":211258,\"idMal\":null,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Arafou Kenja no Isekai Seikatsu Nikki\",\"native\":\"\\u30a2\\u30e9\\u30d5\\u30a9\\u30fc\\u8ce2\\u8005\\u306e\\u7570\\u4e16\\u754c\\u751f\\u6d3b\\u65e5\\u8a18\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":null,\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Adventure\",\"Fantasy\"],\"synonyms\":[\"The Diary of a Middle-Aged Sage's Carefree Life in Another World\"],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":481,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"LIGHT_NOVEL\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":null,\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/211258\",\"description\":\"Satoshi Oosako was a player of the VRRPG \\\"Sword and Sorcery\\\" who defeated the Evil God and died for his troubles. When he awoke again he found himself in a strange unknown forest. Furthermore he possessed his avatar's body and abilities. In other words, he was a cheat. Can a 40-year-old virgin live peacefully in this world?<br><br>\\n\\n(Source: Shousetsuka ni Narou, translated)\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx211258-nY111T5KZCr2.png\",\"color\":\"#d678bb\"},\"trailer\":null,\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/arafo-kenja.com\\/\"}],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":7808,\"name\":\"YANCHESTER\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/7808\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"ALTERNATIVE\",\"node\":{\"id