{\"romaji\":\"Death March Kara Hajimaru Isekai Kyousoukyoku\",\"native\":\"\\u30c7\\u30b9\\u30de\\u30fc\\u30c1\\u304b\\u3089\\u306f\\u3058\\u307e\\u308b\\u7570\\u4e16\\u754c\\u72c2\\u60f3\\u66f2\",\"english\":\"Death March to the Parallel World Rhapsody\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/97907\"}},{\"relationType\":\"ALTERNATIVE\",\"node\":{\"id\":86511,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Death March Kara Hajimaru Isekai Kyousoukyoku\",\"native\":\"\\u30c7\\u30b9\\u30de\\u30fc\\u30c1\\u304b\\u3089\\u306f\\u3058\\u307e\\u308b\\u7570\\u4e16\\u754c\\u72c2\\u60f3\\u66f2\",\"english\":\"Death March to the Parallel World Rhapsody\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/86511\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":203275,\"idMal\":null,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Demons' Crest\",\"native\":\"\\u30c7\\u30e2\\u30f3\\u30ba\\u30fb\\u30af\\u30ec\\u30b9\\u30c8\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2026,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":null,\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Adventure\",\"Fantasy\"],\"synonyms\":[\"\\u30c7\\u30e2\\u30af\\u30ec\",\"DemoKure\"],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":1082,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"LIGHT_NOVEL\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u30c7\\u30e2\\u30af\\u30ec\",\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/203275\",\"description\":\"Sixth-grader Yuuma Ashihara and his twin sister, Sawa, are playing Actual Magic , a brand-new virtual reality MMORPG, when it suddenly begins fusing with the real world. Amid all the chaos and confusion, it becomes clear that death is lurking around every corner, including when Yuuma runs into his classmate Sumika. Before, she was one of the cutest girls in his class, but she\\u2019s since undergone a terrible metamorphosis\\u2014into one of the game\\u2019s horrifying monsters! From the author of Sword Art Online and Accel World comes a story beyond VR and AR, where gaming and reality are one and the same\\u2026and staying alive is just the beginning!\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: Yen Press)\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx203275-bjK35q8Rh9w3.png\",\"color\":\"#0dbbe4\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"llzkRQ9gM1I\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/llzkRQ9gM1I\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/demonscrest-anime.com\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/17-R0tMgOvwvhsS.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/demonscrestPR\"}],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":10,\"name\":\"Production I.G\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/10\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"ALTERNATIVE\",\"node\":{\"id\":155848,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Demons' Crest\",\"native\":\"\\u30c7\\u30e2\\u30f3\\u30ba\\u30fb\\u30af\\u30ec\\u30b9\\u30c8\",\"english\":null},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/155848\"}},{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":154372,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Demons' Crest\",\"native\":\"\\u30c7\\u30e2\\u30f3\\u30ba\\u30fb\\u30af\\u30ec\\u30b9\\u30c8\",\"english\":\"Demons' Crest\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/154372\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":6504,\"idMal\":null,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Despera\",\"native\":\"\\u3067\\u3059\\u307a\\u3089\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":null,\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Drama\",\"Sci-Fi\"],\"synonyms\":[],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":3145,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"OTHER\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":null,\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/6504\",\"description\":\"The story centers around Ain, a 14-year-old girl who builds devices despite the lack of the scientific background required for them. \\n<br><br>\\nThe science-fiction story is set in Japan's Taisho era in 1922 \\u2014 one year before the 1923 Great Kanto earthquake in the Tokyo area.\",\"bannerImage\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/banner\\/6504-gHr7UdQ57oD1.jpg\",\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx6504-hZ8PYSEFN8l7.jpg\",\"color\":\"#bb781a\"},\"trailer\":null,\"externalLinks\":[],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":184356,\"idMal\":63316,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Dogul Wang\",\"native\":\"\\ub3c4\\uad74\\uc655\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2026,\"month\":7,\"day\":null},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":null,\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Adventure\",\"Fantasy\"],\"synonyms\":[\"Tomb Raider King\",\"Toukutsuou\",\"\\u76d7\\u6398\\u738b\"],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":4048,\"episodes\":11,\"source\":\"MANGA\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"KR\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u76d7\\u6398\\u738b\",\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/184356\",\"description\":\"In the year 2025, mysterious tombs appeared all over the world, each housing an ancient relic granting supernatural abilities. The lucky few who quickly obtained these relics ruled over powerful monopolies. Others came to serve them, such as Jooheon Suh, a \\u201craider\\u201d who hid in tombs to steal relics. Betrayed by his employer, Jooheon is left to die but instead finds himself transported 15 years in the past. Armed with years of tough raiding experience and knowledge of what is to come in the world of relics, does Jooheon hav