":[\" The Strongest Man, Born From Misfortune \",\"Unluckiness to the Strongest Man\"],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":434,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"OTHER\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":null,\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/199006\",\"description\":\"\\\"Fortune and Misfortune are two sides of the same coin?! Reverse any adversary and cease redemption!!\\\" \\n<br><br>\\nSiegbert is reborn after an unfortunate accident in his previous life. His new family is warm and welcoming... so much so it seems as though he may no longer be an unlucky person. In this world, he can finally live a quiet, peaceful life... or so he thought. It seems that he actually holds an insanely high luck stat in this new world...?\\n<br><br>\\n\\\"Every chance is a manifestation of good fortune. If you can cease the chances, your wishes shall be granted...\\\" Conquering each \\\"chance\\\" granted by his good fortune, will he now cease redemption on the generational legacy this family has yet to fulfill?!\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: MangaPlaza)\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx199006-VxjFapEbgfVy.png\",\"color\":\"#f1c95d\"},\"trailer\":null,\"externalLinks\":[],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"ALTERNATIVE\",\"node\":{\"id\":141541,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Fuun Kara no Saikyou Otoko\",\"native\":\"\\u4e0d\\u904b\\u304b\\u3089\\u306e\\u6700\\u5f37\\u7537\",\"english\":\"The Strongest Man, Born From Misfortune\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/141541\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":206401,\"idMal\":63337,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"FX Senshi Kurumi-chan\",\"native\":\"FX\\u6226\\u58eb\\u304f\\u308b\\u307f\\u3061\\u3083\\u3093\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2026,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":null,\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Drama\",\"Slice of Life\"],\"synonyms\":[\"FX Fighter Kurumi-chan\"],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":2460,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"MANGA\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#FX\\u6226\\u58eb\\u304f\\u308b\\u307f\\u3061\\u3083\\u3093\",\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/206401\",\"description\":\"A story about the slightly dangerous(!?) investment activities of three soft and fluffy JDs!<br>\\n<br>\\nEvery time the chart moves by 1mm in the wrong direction, I can feel the tears overflowing! A heart-stopping college-girl FX-trading comic for all those who want to have fun and make money!<br>\\n<br>\\n(Source: Kadokawa, translated)\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx206401-tToJHZcMGrvp.jpg\",\"color\":\"#e44378\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"Hg3mStr7UpI\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/Hg3mStr7UpI\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/fxkurumi-info.com\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/219-EwrfceXsqIWg.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/fxkurumi_info\"}],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":911,\"name\":\"Passione\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/911\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":128364,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"FX Senshi Kurumi-chan\",\"native\":\"FX\\u6226\\u58eb\\u304f\\u308b\\u307f\\u3061\\u3083\\u3093\",\"english\":null},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/128364\"}},{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":210896,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"FX Senshi Kurumi-chan\",\"native\":\"FX\\u6226\\u58eb\\u304f\\u308b\\u307f\\u3061\\u308