":\"MANGA\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u30b8\\u30e3\\u30a4\\u30a2\\u30f3\\u30c8\\u304a\\u5b22\\u69d8\",\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/187303\",\"description\":\"Fujido Oriko is the buxom young head of the Fujido Zaibatsu, a group that has a monopoly on Japan's vending machine industry. And serving at her side is her personal butler, the eccentric Dr. Sebastion.\\n<br><br>\\nWhen a monster suddenly attacks the city, Dr. Sebastion slips his ojou-sama an experimental energy drink his team in R&D has been developing. As a result, she quickly finds herself growing into a giantess, matching the attacking kaiju in size! Will she be able to stop his rampage, or at the very least, keep her dignity intact?\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx187303-sBqHPBQyki2o.jpg\",\"color\":\"#781a1a\"},\"trailer\":null,\"externalLinks\":[],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":103,\"name\":\"Tatsunoko Production\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/103\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":140569,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Giant Ojou-sama\",\"native\":\"\\u30b8\\u30e3\\u30a4\\u30a2\\u30f3\\u30c8\\u304a\\u5b22\\u69d8\",\"english\":null},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/140569\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":202906,\"idMal\":63016,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"GIRL CRUSH\",\"native\":\"\\u30ac\\u30fc\\u30eb\\u30af\\u30e9\\u30c3\\u30b7\\u30e5\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":null,\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Drama\"],\"synonyms\":[],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":1599,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"MANGA\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u30ac\\u30fc\\u30eb\\u30af\\u30e9\\u30c3\\