            "text": "{\"data\":{\"Page\":{\"pageInfo\":{\"hasNextPage\":true,\"total\":5000},\"media\":[{\"id\":205130,\"idMal\":63215,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Histori\\u00e9\",\"native\":\"\\u30d2\\u30b9\\u30c8\\u30ea\\u30a8\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":null,\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Adventure\",\"Drama\",\"Psychological\"],\"synonyms\":[],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":2144,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"MANGA\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u30d2\\u30b9\\u30c8\\u30ea\\u30a8\",\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/205130\",\"description\":\"After shocking the world with Parasyte, Hitoshi Iwaaki is back with a series he's been aching to tackle since even before his pro manga debut! A historical epic set in ancient times, Historie tells the story of Eumenes, a young man with quick wits and a vast destiny to fulfill. In time, he'll become a famed army commander and personal secretary to Alexander the Great\\u2014but the road to this glory is fraught with danger\\u2026 \\\"<br><br>(Source: K Manga)\",\"bannerImage\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/banner\\/205130-BDtd2yGv1a7O.jpg\",\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx205130-0cH9SpPcEHSh.png\",\"color\":\"#1a5078\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"ZNXhIx7L0n4\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/ZNXhIx7L0n4\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/219-EwrfceXsqIWg.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/historie_off\"},{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.historie.info\\/\"}],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":839,\"name\":\"LIDENFILMS\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/839\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":32924,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Historie\",\"native\":\"\\u30d2\\u30b9\\u30c8\\u30ea\\u30a8\",\"english\":\"Historie\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/32924\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":211538,\"idMal\":64064,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Hokuhokusei ni Kumo to Ike\",\"native\":\"\\u5317\\u5317\\u897f\\u306b\\u66c7\\u3068\\u5f80\\u3051\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":null,\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Adventure\",\"Mystery\",\"Slice of Life\"],\"synonyms\":[\"Go with the Clouds, North-by-Northwest\"],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":1112,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"MANGA\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u5317\\u5317\\u897f\\u306b\\u66c7\\u3068\\u5f80\\u3051\",\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/211538\",\"description\":\"The story takes place in Iceland, at land\\u2019s end, 64\\u00b0N.<br>\\nKei Miyama is a 17-year-old with three secrets: he can talk to cars, he can\\u2019t handle pretty girls, and he works as a private investigator. One case has him searching for a beloved dog, another involves reuniting a woman with a man she fell for at first sight. And then comes a case that strikes close to home\\u2014searching for his own little brother.<br>\\nTag along as this globe-spanning journey unfolds\\u2026\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: Kodansha USA)\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx211538-9DIgBfTibfZh.jpg\",\"color\":\"#5078e4\"},\"trailer\":null,\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/219-EwrfceXsqIWg.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/hokuhokusei_pr\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/hokuhokusei-pr.com\\/\"}],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":87020,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Hokuhokusei ni Kumo to Ike\",\"native\":\"\\u5317\\u5317\\u897f\\u306b\\u66c7\\u3068\\u5f80\\u3051\",\"english\":\"Go with the Clouds, North-by-Northwest\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/87020\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":208609,\"idMal\":63601,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Hone Dragon no Mana Musume\",\"native\":\"\\u9aa8\\u30c9\\u30e9\\u30b4\\u30f3\\u306e\\u30de\\u30ca\\u5a18\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":null,\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Adventure\",\"Fantasy\"],\"synonyms\":[],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":798,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"MANGA\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u9aa8\\u30c9\\u30e9\\u30b4\\u30f3 #\\u9aa8\\u30c9\\u30e9\\u30b4\\u30f3\\u306e\\u30de\\u30ca\\u5a18\",\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/208609\",\"description\":\"In the Forest of Scraps, a place where all manner of things are discarded, an old dragon sleeps away his final days\\u2014that is, until an abandoned child suddenly appears before him. The tiny human is Eve, and despite being only five years of age, she has somehow endured the many dangers that surround them. In an act of pity, the dragon decides to raise her as his own...but his time is still running out.<br><br>\\n\\nAfter five years together, he takes his last breath, leaving his precious daughter on her own. Little does the dragon know, Eve is capable of more than he realizes, and their reunion may be sooner than he thinks\\u2026<br><br>\\n\\n(Source: J-Novel Club)\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx208609-eMhZ6KDsRR9r.jpg\",\"color\":\"#43bbe4\"},\"trailer\":null,\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/honedora.com\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/219-EwrfceXsqIWg.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/honedragon_pj\"}],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":95,\"name\":\"Doga Kobo\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/95\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":127910,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Hone Dragon no Mana Musume\",\"native\":\"\\u9aa8\\u30c9\\u30e9\\u30b4\\u30f3\\u306e\\u30de\\u30ca\\u5a18\",\"english\":\"The Skull Dragon's Precious Daughter\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/127910\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":186336,\"idMal\":60829,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"IDOLiSH7 4th Season\",\"native\":\"\\u30a2\\u30a4\\u30c9\\u30ea\\u30c3\\u30b7\\u30e5\\u30bb\\u30d6\\u30f3 \\u30a2\\u30cb\\u30e14\\u671f\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":null,\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[],\"synonyms\":[],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":1152,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":null,\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u30a2\\u30a4\\u30ca\\u30ca #\\u30a2\\u30cb\\u30ca\\u30ca4\\u671f\",\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/186336\",\"description\":\"The fourth season of <i>IDOLiSH7.<\\/i>\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx186336-vLdQxIum0BSy.jpg\",\"color\":\"#1aaee4\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"EZgQotlNbdY\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/EZgQotlNbdY\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"PREQUEL\",\"node\":{\"id\":128890,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"IDOLiSH7: Third BEAT! Part 2\",\"native\":\"\\u30a2\\u30a4\\u30c9\\u30ea\\u30c3\\u30b7\\u30e5\\u30bb\\u30d6\\u30f3 Third BEAT! \\u7b2c2\\u30af\\u30fc\\u30eb\",\"english\":\"IDOLiSH7 Third BEAT! Part 2\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/128890\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":163790,\"idMal\":null,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Igye Geomwang Saengjongi\",\"native\":\"\\uc774\\uacc4 \\uac80\\uc655 \\uc0dd\\uc874\\uae30\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":null,\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Adventure\",\"Comedy\",\"Fantasy\"],\"synonyms\":[\"Latna Saga: Survival of a Sword King\"],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":1275,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"NOVEL\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"KR\",\"hashtag\":null,\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/163790\",\"description\":\"After being recently discharged from military service and just drifting through life, Hanbin Ryu is suddenly transported to another world. However, his \\u201cguide line,\\u201d the system bestowed upon him to help with his survival and growth, was filled with errors, causing him to be stuck in the tutorial stage for over 20 years. When he is finally released from this personal hell, he finds everyone has turned against otherworlders like him. Just how will this low-level, super-tutorial newbie survive?<br><br>(Source: Tapas)\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/medium\\/default.jpg\",\"color\":null},\"trailer\":null,\"externalLinks\":[],\"rankings