o-pr.com\\/wp\"}],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":119704,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Izure Saikyou no Renkinjutsushi?\",\"native\":\"\\u3044\\u305a\\u308c\\u6700\\u5f37\\u306e\\u932c\\u91d1\\u8853\\u5e2b\\uff1f\",\"english\":null},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/119704\"}},{\"relationType\":\"PREQUEL\",\"node\":{\"id\":177506,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Izure Saikyou no Renkinjutsushi?\",\"native\":\"\\u3044\\u305a\\u308c\\u6700\\u5f37\\u306e\\u932c\\u91d1\\u8853\\u5e2b\\uff1f\",\"english\":\"Possibly the Greatest Alchemist of All Time\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/177506\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":209116,\"idMal\":null,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"J\\u21d4M\",\"native\":\"J\\u21d4M\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":null,\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Comedy\"],\"synonyms\":[\"J\\u21d4M \\u30b8\\u30a7\\u30a4\\u30a8\\u30e0\",\"JM\"],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":699,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"MANGA\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":null,\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/209116\",\"description\":\"J is a professional hitman...he was orphan and raised by a syndicate as an assassin. He was too good, killed too many people, knew too much about the syndicate.\\nWhen the syndicate tried to erase him, they were backfired...when three syndicates were wiped out completely, J became \\\"untouchable.\\\"<br><br>\\n\\nMegumi, a girl in third grade, was bullied by her classmates because she is half-Japanese, half-American and gets good grades. One day, when they bumped their heads...their bodies were switched. Now J is inside a cute girl's body...and Megumi is inside the tough guy's body.<br><br>\\n\\nNow they must hide that they are not who they were and keep their everyday life look the same as before.\\nJ never knew how hard a girl's life is, and Megumi enjoys her new life!?<br><br>\\n\\n(Source: BookWalker)\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx209116-n1TnXuBx0kF5.jpg\",\"color\":null},\"trailer\":null,\"externalLinks\":[],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":163827,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"J\\u21d4M\",\"native\":\"J\\u21d4M \\u30b8\\u30a7\\u30a4\\u30a8\\u30e0\",\"english\":\"JM\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/163827\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":204579,\"idMal\":63174,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Jirai nan desu ka? Chihara-san\",\"native\":\"\\u5730\\u96f7\\u306a\\u3093\\u3067\\u3059\\u304b\\uff1f\\u5730\\u539f\\u3055\\u3093\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2026,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":null,\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Comedy\",\"Romance\",\"Slice of Life\"],\"synonyms\":[\"That Girl Is Cute... But Dangerous?\",\"Jirai Nandesuka? Chihara-san\"],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":3853,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"MANGA\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u30a2\\u30cb\\u30e1\\u5730\\u539f\\u3055\\u3093\",\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/204579\",\"description\":\"The girl sitting next to me at the start of the new semester is the rumored \\\"landmine\\\" girl\\u2026 but\\u2026 is Chihara-san really the \\\"landmine\\\" that everyone says she is?<br>\\n<br>\\n(Source: Ganma!, translated)\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx204579-eIieS4KuQN9x.jpg\",\"color\":\"#f12850\"},\"trailer\":null,\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/chiharasan-anime.com\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/219-EwrfceXsqIWg.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/chihara_anime\"}],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":118,\"name\":\"SynergySP\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/118\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":137714,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Jirai nan desu ka? Chihara-san\",\"native\":\"\\u5730\\u96f7\\u306a\\u3093\\u3067\\u3059\\u304b\\uff1f\\u5730\\u539f\\u3055\\u3093\",\"english\":\"Are You a Landmine, Chihara-san?\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/137714\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":202564,\"idMal\":62989,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Kakunaru Ue wa\",\"native\":\"\\u63cf\\u304f\\u306a\\u308b\\u3046\\u3048\\u306f\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":null,\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Comedy\",\"Ecchi\",\"Romance\"],\"synonyms\":[\"Now That We Draw\"],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":7372,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"MANGA\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u63cf\\u304f\\u306a\\u308b\\u30a2\\u30cb\\u30e1\",\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/202564\",\"description\":\"Opposites attract in this hysterical rom-com about two high school manga artists who can\\u2019t catch a break!\\n<br><br>\\nDweeby high schooler Uehara Yuuki has created the perfect romantic comedy heroine\\u2014she\\u2019s bashful, airheaded, and completely chaste. When an editor at Uehara\\u2019s dream publisher coldly dismisses his manga story as trite and lacking realism, it sends Uehara into a spiral of despair that pushes him into the path of his bubbly, gorgeous classmate, Miyamoto Niina\\u2014an aspiring manga artist herself! Having gotten similar feedback on her own manga, Miyamoto proposes she and Uehara engage in a fake relationship, since neither of them have any romantic experience. But Miyamoto is far from the perfect heroine Uehara\\u2019s concocted, and he certainly isn\\u2019t the cocky hero from her story either. Can their wacky relationship turn their manga dreams into reality, or will it lead to even more comic disasters?\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: Seven Seas Entertainment)\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx202564-gLnCiyS8vHsB.jpg\",\"color\":\"#5da1e4\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"hfV4hiemNHQ\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/hfV4hiemNHQ\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/219-EwrfceXsqIWg.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/kakunaru_anime\"},{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/kakunaru-anime.com\\/\"}],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":7475,\"name\":\"ROLL2\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/7475\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":161433,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Kakunaru Ue wa\",\"native\":\"\\u63cf\\u304f\\u306a\\u308b\\u3046\\u3048\\u306f\",\"english\":\"Now That We Draw\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/161433\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":209463,\"idMal\":null,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Kanata Kara\",\"native\":\"\\u5f7c\\u65b9\\u304b\\u3089\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2026,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":null,\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Adventure\",\"Fantasy\",\"Romance\"],\"synonyms\":[\"From Far Away\"],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":931,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"MANGA\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u5f7c\\u65b9\\u304b\\u3089\",\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/209463\",\"description\":\"On her way home from school one day, Noriko is unexpectedly plunged into a strange and extraordinary fantasy world. Her troubles compound exponentially when she is rescued and befriended by a handsome young man by the name of Izark. He may be brave and courageous, but inside Izark lurks the darkest evil imaginable. And according to an ancient prophecy, Noriko possesses the power to unleash that evil. Now, inexorably bound together, these two unlikely allies must navigate a world both wondrous and hostile.\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: VIZ Media)\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx209463-7Y5EkvBySyCD.jpg\",\"color\":\"#fe6b28\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"ois8bCu2Ba8\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/ois8bCu2Ba8\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/kanatakara-anime.com\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/219-EwrfceXsqIWg.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/kanatakara_anm\"}],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":30923,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Kanata Kara\",\"native\":\"\\u5f7c\\u65b9\\u304b\\u3089\",\"english\":\"From Far Away\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/30923\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":211877,\"idMal\":64131,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Kanojo no Tomodachi\",\"native\":\"\\u5f7c\\u5973\\u306e\\u53cb\\u9054\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2026,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":null,\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Drama\",\"Ecchi\",\"Romance\"],\"synonyms\":[\"My Girlfriend's Friend\"],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":766,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"MANGA\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u30ab\\u30ce\\u30c8\\u30e2\\u30a2\\u30cb\\u30e1 #\\u5f7c\\u5973\\u306e\\u53cb\\u9054\",\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/211877\",\"description\":\"For the first time in my life, I have a girlfriend. But her friend tempts me with a body that's so seductive... What would you do if your girlfriend's friend came on to you like this? \\n<br><br>\\n(Source: Yanmaga, translated)\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx211877-RKPbAZkcALdE.png\",\"color\":\"#4350f1\"},\"trailer\":null,\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/219-EwrfceXsqIWg.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/kanotomo_anime_\"}],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":133932,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Kanojo no Tomodachi\",\"native\":\"\\u5f7c\\u5973\\u306e\\u53cb\\u9054\",\"english\":null},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/133932\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":202250,\"idMal\":null,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Kashita Maryoku wa [Ribo Harai] de Kyousei Choushuu\",\"native\":\"\\u8cb8\\u3057\\u305f\\u9b54\\u529b\\u306f\\u3010\\u30ea\\u30dc\\u6255\\u3044\\u3011\\u3067\\u5f37\\u5236\\u5fb4\\u53ce\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2026,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":null,\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Adventure\",\"Fantasy\"],\"synonyms\":[\"Magic Repo Man: Dumped by My Party, I'll Cash In With a Cute Support Fairy to Become the Strongest!\",\"\\u8cb8\\u3057\\u305f\\u9b54\\u529b\\u306f\\u3010\\u30ea\\u30dc\\u6255\\u3044\\u3011\\u3067\\u5f37\\u5236\\u5fb4\\u53ce\\uff5e\\u7528\\u6e08\\u307f\\u3068\\u30d1\\u30fc\\u30c6\\u30a3\\u30fc\\u8ffd\\u653e\\u3055\\u308c\\u305f\\u4ffa\\u306f\\u3001\\u53ef\\u611b\\u3044\\u30b5\\u30dd\\u30fc\\u30c8\\u5996\\u7cbe\\u3068\\u4e00\\u7dd2\\u306b\\u53d6\\u308a\\u7acb\\u3066\\u305f\\u9b54\\u529b\\u3092\\u904b\\u7528\\u3057\\u3066\\u6700\\u5f37\\u3092\\u76ee\\u6307\\u3059\\u3002\\uff5e\",\"Kashita Maryoku wa [Ribo Harai] de Kyousei Choushuu ~Youzumi to Party Tsuihou sareta Ore wa, Kawaii Support Yousei to Issho ni Toritateta Maryoku wo Unyou shite Saikyou wo Mezasu.\"],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":689,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"MANGA\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":null,\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/202250\",\"description\":\"If there's one thing you can never have enough of in a world of RPG-style swords and sorcery, it's magic points! Whether you're fueling spells, techniques, or showing off an incredible ability, you've gotta spend those points to do real damage. But what if you run out?\\n<br><br>\\nLent is part of the up-and-coming party known as the \\u201cSkypiercers,\\u201d and thanks to his unique Gift, he can loan massive amounts of magic to others. No MP? No problem with Lent around! Except, now that his companions have become formidable heroes (thanks to his skill), his usefulness is questioned. Kicked out of the group, Lent is furious\\u2026until he discovers a hidden power to his Gift. Now, with his adorably devious fairy partner, he's going to claw back every last scrap of magic from his former party\\u2014with interest!<br><br>\\n(Source: Seven Seas Entertainment)\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx202250-xfuf10GUke6L.jpg\",\"color\":\"#f17843\"},\"trailer\":null,\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/17-R0tMgOvwvhsS.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/twitter.com\\/revo_anime\"}],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":118,\"name\":\"SynergySP\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/118\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":202228,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Kashita Maryoku wa [Ribo Harai] de Kyousei Choushuu ~Youzumi to Party Tsuihou sareta Ore wa, Kawaii Support Yousei to Issho ni Toritateta Maryoku wo Unyou shite Saikyou wo Mezasu.\",\"native\":\"\\u8cb8\\u3057\\u305f\\u9b54\\u529b\\u306f\\u3010\\u30ea\\u30dc\\u6255\\u3044\\u3011\\u3067\\u5f37\\u5236\\u5fb4\\u53ce \\uff5e\\u7528\\u6e08\\u307f\\u3068\\u30d1\\u30fc\\u30c6\\u30a3\\u30fc\\u8ffd\\u653e\\u3055\\u308c\\u305f\\u4ffa\\u306f\\u3001\\u53ef\\u611b\\u3044\\u30b5\\u30dd\\u30fc\\u30c8\\u5996\\u7cbe\\u3068\\u4e00\\u7dd2\\u306b\\u53d6\\u308a\\u7acb\\u3066\\u305f\\u9b54\\u529b\\u3092\\u904b\\u7528\\u3057\\u3066\\u6700\\u5f37\\u3092\\u76ee\\u6307\\u3059\\u3002\\uff5e\",\"english\":\"Magic Repo Man: Dumped by My Party, I'll Cash In With a Cute Support Fairy to Become the Strongest!\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/202228\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":197619,\"idMal\":62311,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Kekkaishi no Ichirinka\",\"native\":\"\\u7d50\\u754c\\u5e2b\\u306e\\u4e00\\u8f2a\\u83ef\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":null,\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Drama\",\"Fantasy\",\"Romance\"],\"synonyms\":[\"Bride of the Barrier Master\"],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":1334,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"NOVEL\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u7d50\\u754c\\u5e2b\\u306e\\u4e00\\u8f2a\\u83ef\",\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/197619\",\"description\":\"Hana Ichise is from a branch family to one of five barrier-weaving magical clans who protect and support Japan. But in the eyes of her mother and father, she\\u2019s an afterthought compared to her talented older twin sister. When Hana\\u2019s true potential awakens at age fifteen, she decides to keep her newfound abilities a secret\\u2014including from her parents\\u2014so she can have a quiet life. But the powerful new head of the elite Ichinomiya clan, Saku Ichinomiya, is looking for a bride\\u2026and he has his eyes on Hana!\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: Yen Press)\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx197619-sFQaF319nGGO.png\",\"color\":\"#506bf1\"},\"trailer\":null,\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/17-R0tMgOvwvhsS.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/ichirinka_anime\"},{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/kekkaishi-ichirinka-anime.com\\/\"}],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":6068,\"name\":\"TROYCA\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/6068\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"ALTERNATIVE\",\"node\":{\"id\":175119,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Kekkaishi no Ichirinka\",\"native\":\"\\u7d50\\u754c\\u5e2b\\u306e\\u4e00\\u8f2a\\u83ef\",\"english\":\"Bride of the Barrier Master\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/175119\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":172192,\"idMal\":57612,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Kikansha no Mahou wa Tokubetsu desu 2nd Season\",\"native\":\"\\u5e30\\u9084\\u8005\\u306e\\u9b54\\u6cd5\\u306f\\u7279\\u5225\\u3067\\u3059 \\u7b2c2\\u671f\",\"english\":\"A Returner's Magic Should be Special Season 2\"},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2026,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"endDa