7\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":208204,\"idMal\":null,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Mahoutsukai Ros\\u00e9 no Sado Life\",\"native\":\"\\u9b54\\u6cd5\\u4f7f\\u3044\\u30ed\\u30bc\\u306e\\u4f50\\u6e21\\u30e9\\u30a4\\u30d5\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":null,\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Fantasy\",\"Slice of Life\"],\"synonyms\":[\"The Sado Life of Ros\\u00e9 the witch\"],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":411,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"MANGA\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u9b54\\u6cd5\\u4f7f\\u3044\\u30ed\\u30bc\\u306e\\u4f50\\u6e21\\u30e9\\u30a4\\u30d5 #\\u4f50\\u6e21\\u30e9\\u30a4\\u30d5\",\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/208204\",\"description\":\"Rose escapes from her own world... and ends up on \\\"Sado Island\\\"? This is the start of a daily-life comedy where she and Sana, a girl who lives on the island, try to make the most of every day!\\n<BR><BR>\\n(Source: Comic Fuz, translated)\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx208204-3cIphMPagoU5.jpg\",\"color\":\"#e4a150\"},\"trailer\":null,\"externalLinks\":[],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":169680,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Mahoutsukai Ros\\u00e9 no Sado Life\",\"native\":\"\\u9b54\\u6cd5\\u4f7f\\u3044\\u30ed\\u30bc\\u306e\\u4f50\\u6e21\\u30e9\\u30a4\\u30d5\",\"english\":null},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/169680\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":210945,\"idMal\":63958,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Majo to Youhei\",\"native\":\"\\u9b54\\u5973\\u3068\\u50ad\\u5175\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2027,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":null,\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Fantasy\"],\"synonyms\":[\"Witch and Mercenary\"],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":1809,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"LIGHT_NOVEL\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u9b54\\u5973\\u3068\\u50ad\\u5175\",\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/210945\",\"description\":\"Nothing in this world is more dangerous than a witch. The epitome of fear and terror, they can summon floods on a whim, conjure balls of fire out of the air, or even destroy entire countries overnight. Incur their wrath, and no one is safe.<br>\\n<br>\\nAt least, that\\u2019s what everyone thinks, and it\\u2019s the very reason they all want Siasha dead. After yet another violent battle for her life, she teams up with Zig, a mercenary, and they depart for unknown lands to find somewhere she can live in peace. But is the pair any match for the lost magic and vicious monstrosities that lie ahead?<br>\\n<br>\\n(Source: Seven Seas Entertainment)\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx210945-uVcWtO8UYiOv.jpg\",\"color\":null},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"Ma6twUC12To\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/Ma6twUC12To\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.anime-witch-mercenary-official.com\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/219-EwrfceXsqIWg.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/anime_majyohei\"}],\"rankings\":[{\"rank\":20,\"type\":\"POPULAR\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":false}],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":4418,\"name\":\"8-bit\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/4418\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"ALTERNATIVE\",\"node\":{\"id\":174233,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Majo to Youhei\",\"native\":\"\\u9b54\\u5973\\u3068\\u50ad\\u5175\",\"english\":\"The Witch and the Mercenary\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/174233\"}},{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":174232,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Majo to Youhei\",\"native\":\"\\u9b54\\u5973\\u3068\\u50ad\\u5175\",\"english\":\"Witch and Mercenary\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/174232\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":202503,\"idMal\":62978,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Majutsu wo Kiwamete Tabi ni Deta Tensei Elf, Moteamashita Jumyou de Ikeru Densetsu to Naru\",\"native\":\"\\u9b54\\u8853\\u3092\\u6975\\u3081\\u3066\\u65c5\\u306b\\u51fa\\u305f\\u8ee2\\u751f\\u30a8\\u30eb\\u30d5\\u3001\\u6301\\u3066\\u4f59\\u3057\\u305f\\u5bff\\u547d\\u3067\\u751f\\u3051\\u308b\\u4f1d\\u8aac\\u3068\\u306a\\u308b\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":null,\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Adventure\",\"Fantasy\"],\"synonyms\":[\"The Reincarnated Elf Left on a Journey to Master His Magic and With His Extra Lifespan Became a Living Legend\",\"Tensei Elf ni Yoru 900-Nen no Yuukku Slow Life\"],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":547,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"OTHER\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":null,\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/202503\",\"description\":\"Minoru Kido, age 30, cause of death: traffic accident. As a Japanese, I died without leaving any evidence of my life. At the time of my death, I was thinking, \\\"Next time, I want to live a long life and leave behind some proof of my life,\\\" when I was reincarnated as an elf with a life span of 1,000 years! That's why I made a vow. I vowed that this time I would spend my whole life living in a way that would leave a mark on my life.<br><br>\\n\\nAt the age of 20, I was able to use all of the healing magic that elves were originally equipped with at will. By the age of 30, I had mastered all attribute magic, and by the age of 100, I had deciphered all the ancient magic formulas. For the remaining 900 years of my life, all I have to do is run out of the Elven forest and become a warrior.<br><br>\\n\\nOne day, I'll be missed by a fledgling adventurer who will eventually be called a hero. Sometimes, a country is founded in my name. Sometimes, I was called the founder of magic and became an object of worship. This is the story of a reincarnated elf who roars his name into history as a living legend.<br><br>\\n\\n(Source: Kakuyomu, translated)\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx202503-nHeL8zPVOzVp.jpg\",\"color\":\"#e47828\"},\"trailer\":null,\"externalLinks\":[],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"ALTERNATIVE\",\"node\":{\"id\":166851,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Majutsu wo Kiwamete Tabi ni Deta Tensei Elf, Moteamashita Jumyou de Ikeru Densetsu to Naru\",\"native\":\"\\u9b54\\u8853\\u3092\\u6975\\u3081\\u3066\\u65c5\\u306b\\u51fa\\u305f\\u8ee2\\u751f\\u30a8\\u30eb\\u30d5\\u3001\\u6301\\u3066\\u4f59\\u3057\\u305f\\u5bff\\u547d\\u3067\\u751f\\u3051\\u308b\\u4f1d\\u8aac\\u3068\\u306a\\u308b\",\"english\":null},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/166851\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":189796,\"idMal\":61398,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Make Heroine ga Oosugiru! 2nd Season\",\"native\":\"\\u8ca0\\u3051\\u30d2\\u30ed\\u30a4\\u30f3\\u304c\\u591a\\u3059\\u304e\\u308b\\uff012\\u671f\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":null,\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Comedy\",\"Romance\"],\"synonyms\":[\"Makeine: Too Many Losing Heroines! Sea