\/anime\\/211304\",\"description\":\"Momose has always longed for a peaceful high school life. She wants nothing to do with hoodlums, delinquents, or troublemakers. When she meets Ichikura, an inconspicuous black-haired boy with glasses, he looks like a normal, nice guy. But it turns out that back in junior high he was a nefarious delinquent! He keeps assuring her that he\\u2019s changed his ways, but he still has a knack for picking fights! Has Ichikura really turned over a new leaf? And will Momose keep the secret about his rowdy past?\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: Seven Seas Entertainment)\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx211304-C8U1mk1I91rp.jpg\",\"color\":\"#f16b28\"},\"trailer\":null,\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/219-EwrfceXsqIWg.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/otasukebu_anime\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/otasukebu.com\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Instagram\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/48-VFlxaXGaNqXk.png\",\"color\":\"#833AB4\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.instagram.com\\/otasukebu\"},{\"site\":\"TikTok\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/196-o2g5cLUG6k5V.png\",\"color\":\"#010101\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.tiktok.com\\/@otasukebu\"}],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":128448,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Megane, Tokidoki, Yankee-kun\",\"native\":\"\\u30e1\\u30ac\\u30cd\\u3001\\u6642\\u3005\\u3001\\u30e4\\u30f3\\u30ad\\u30fc\\u304f\\u3093\",\"english\":\"Glasses With a Chance of Delinquent\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/128448\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":102674,\"idMal\":null,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"M