":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/20221\"}},{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":32629,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Minami-ke\",\"native\":\"\\u307f\\u306a\\u307f\\u3051\",\"english\":null},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/32629\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":108992,\"idMal\":63802,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Mobius Dust\",\"native\":\"\\u30e1\\u30d3\\u30a6\\u30b9\\u30fb\\u30c0\\u30b9\\u30c8\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2026,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":null,\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Supernatural\"],\"synonyms\":[\"Project Anima\",\"Mebius Dust\",\"M\\u00f6bius Dust\"],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":3449,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"NOVEL\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":null,\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/108992\",\"description\":\"On February 29, 2000, a group of M\\u00f6bius meteorites fell down to earth. These meteorites brought new material called M\\u00f6bius Dust, which dissolves in air and can cause miracles. The day the M\\u00f6bius meteorites fell was dubbed 2.29, and the economic disparity in Japan increased dramatically after that day. A group of people fed up with the wealth inequality fought back with acts of terrorism. The police established a special group to fight against the the terrorists and a school to train members for that group.\\n<br><\\/br>\\n(Sources: Comic Natalie, Live Chart)\\n\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx108992-aKpjh4JVayhd.png\",\"color\":\"#ffe4ae\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"486nVRQfVoo\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/486nVRQfVoo\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/mebiusdust.asmik-ace.co.jp\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/17-R0tMgOvwvhsS.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/ANIMA_info\"}],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":95,\"name\":\"Doga Kobo\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/95\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"OTHER\",\"node\":{\"id\":108987,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Sakugan\",\"native\":\"\\u30b5\\u30af\\u30ac\\u30f3\",\"english\":\"SAKUGAN\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/108987\"}},{\"relationType\":\"OTHER\",\"node\":{\"id\":107372,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Mahoutsukai ni Narenakatta Onnanoko no Hanashi.\",\"native\":\"\\u9b54\\u6cd5\\u4f7f\\u3044\\u306b\\u306a\\u308c\\u306a\\u304b\\u3063\\u305f\\u5973\\u306e\\u5b50\\u306e\\u8a71\\u3002\",\"english\":\"The Stories of Girls Who Couldn't Be Magicians\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/107372\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":206774,\"idMal\":63381,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Mouse Cursor de Genjitsu wo Sousa Dekiru You ni Natta node, Onnanoko wo Ippai Click Shimasu\",\"native\":\"\\u30de\\u30a6\\u30b9\\u30ab\\u30fc\\u30bd\\u30eb\\u3067\\u73fe\\u5b9f\\u3092\\u64cd\\u4f5c\\u3067\\u304d\\u308b\\u3088\\u3046\\u306b\\u306a\\u3063\\u305f\\u306e\\u3067\\u3001\\u5973\\u306e\\u5b50\\u3092\\u3044\\u3063\\u3071\\u3044\\u30af\\u30ea\\u30c3\\u30af\\u3057\\u307e\\u30fc\\u3059\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":null,\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Ecchi\",\"Romance\",\"Supernatural\"],\"synonyms\":[\"Click Me All Over\"],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":438,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"MANGA\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":null,\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/206774\",\"description\":\"What if you could actually use a mouse cursor in real life? Takumi, the nerdy outcast, harbors unrequited feelings for his first love, Mone, who treats him with disdain. During computer class, Takumi discovers that his mouse cursor extends beyond the screen and into the physical world...?! With this newfound power visible only to him, Takumi sees an opportunity for mischief. He uses the cursor to get revenge on Mone, clicking on sensitive areas and reveling in her reactions. But when an \\\"Intercourse\\\" button appears unexpectedly, Takumi is thrust into a reality he never imagined possible...\\\"Intercourse\\\"?! Could this really be...?!\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: Coolmic)\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx206774-4VI5N6098HPr.png\",\"color\":\"#d6ae1a\"},\"trailer\":null,\"externalLinks\":[],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":199993,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Mouse Cursor de Genjitsu wo Sousa Dekiru You ni Natta node, Onnanoko wo Ippai Click Shimasu\",\"native\":\"\\u30de\\u30a6\\u30b9\\u30ab\\u30fc\\u30bd\\u30eb\\u3067\\u73fe\\u5b9f\\u3092\\u64cd\\u4f5c\\u3067\\u304d\\u308b\\u3088\\u3046\\u306b\\u306a\\u3063\\u305f\\u306e\\u3067\\u3001\\u5973\\u306e\\u5b50\\u3092\\u3044\\u3063\\u3071\\u3044\\u30af\\u30ea\\u30c3\\u30af\\u3057\\u307e\\u30fc\\u3059\",\"english\":\"Click Me All Over\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/199993\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":170822,\"idMal\":57005,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Mukuwarenakatta Murabito A, Kizoku ni Hirowarete Dekiai sareru Ue ni, Jitsu wa Motteita Densetsu-kyuu no Kami Skill mo Kakusei shita\",\"native\":\"\\u5831\\u308f\\u308c\\u306a\\u304b\\u3063\\u305f\\u6751\\u4ebaA\\u3001\\u8cb4\\u65cf\\u306b\\u62fe\\u308f\\u308c\\u3066\\u6eba\\u611b\\u3055\\u308c\\u308b\\u4e0a\\u306b\\u3001\\u5b9f\\u306f\\u6301\\u3063\\u3066\\u3044\\u305f\\u4f1d\\u8aac\\u7d1a\\u306e\\u795e\\u30b9\\u30ad\\u30eb\\u3082\\u899a\\u9192\\u3057\\u305f\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":null,\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Fantasy\"],\"synonyms\":[\"The Villager Who Was Abandoned, Was Picked Up by an Aristocrat and Awakened a Legendary Divine Skill\"],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":1269,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"OTHER\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":null,\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/170822\",\"description\":\"Matteo, who was supposed to be just a common villager, is reborn as the grandson of an imperial aristocrat, Lawrence. He spends his days being doted on by his powerful grandfather. With his immense magical powers, Matteo rapidly hatches a dragon egg and tames the dragon, naming it Eva. When his magical abilities are measured, it's revealed that he possesses the strongest magic power ever recorded!<br><br>\\n\\nHe quickly learns how to use magic, reviving ancient spells and effortlessly drawing the most powerful sword that absorbs magic, making it the strongest. Matteo is also favored by the emperor he meets, but the emperor holds a secret\\u2014?<br><br>\\n\\nClever, illustrious, strong, as expected! The life of the most beloved noble, where everything is affirmed, boldly begins!<br><br>\\n\\n(Source: MAL News)\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx170822-IHYsSYqMqjZq.png\",\"color\":\"#5dc9e4\"},\"trailer\":null,\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/mura-a.com\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/219-EwrfceXsqIWg.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/muraA_dekiai\"}],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\