iness: Reincarnated Me\",\"When I Reincarnated as a Chubby Villainess, For Some Reason, I'm Being Relentlessly Pursued by the Final Boss Prince!\"],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":1328,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"MANGA\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u304a\\u30c7\\u30d6\\u60aa\\u5973\",\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/207782\",\"description\":\"After dying of illness, she has been reincarnated as Celine, the selfish, fat, villainous duchess, sister of the heroine of a popular novel.\\nIf she stays this way, she will be killed by the hero prince and die a miserable death, just as in the novel. She vows to reform herself with all her might and begins to struggle, but she finds herself caught up in unexpected doting and obsession..!<br>\\nWill Celine be able to find \\\"peaceful happiness\\\"?\\n<br><br>\\nA fantasy love story about a reincarnation in another world where she is loved too much by a Yandere.\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: Pocket Comics)\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx207782-aaog7JqDuddN.jpg\",\"color\":\"#d6a178\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"uzM2Fz4jyow\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/uzM2Fz4jyow\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/odebuakujo-anime.com\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/219-EwrfceXsqIWg.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/odebuakujo_pr\"}],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":7199,\"name\":\"Studio Lings\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/7199\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":186638,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Odebu Akujo ni Tensei Shitara, Naze ka Last Boss Ouji-sama ni Shuuchaku Sareteimasu\",\"native\":\"