ke Amai\",\"native\":\"\\u5869\\u5bfe\\u5fdc\\u306e\\u4f50\\u85e4\\u3055\\u3093\\u304c\\u4ffa\\u306b\\u3060\\u3051\\u7518\\u3044\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2026,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":null,\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Comedy\",\"Romance\"],\"synonyms\":[\"The Cold Sato-san is Only Sweet to Me\"],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":1925,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"LIGHT_NOVEL\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u3057\\u304a\\u3042\\u307e\",\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/209502\",\"description\":\"Sato-san is the unattainable flower of the class. She is always cold and curt with classmates, but only I know she's actually very cute when she smiles, even if she's not much of a photographer.\\n<br><br>\\nOshio-kun is friendly and lively, but only I know he works at his family's cafe after school. He does a great job with the cafe's SNS account, and his mischievous smile makes my heart skip a beat!\\n<br><br>\\nInnocent and sweet, but sometimes frustrating, this is a 120%-pure fluffy story about two people falling in love for the first time.\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx209502-5ZtmfNfDopbK.jpg\",\"color\":\"#e4935d\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"ue63MEfLOx8\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/ue63MEfLOx8\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/17-R0tMgOvwvhsS.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/shioamaofficial\"},{\"site\":\"TikTok\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/196-o2g5cLUG6k5V.png\",\"color\":\"#010101\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.tiktok.com\\/@shioama_official\"},{\"site\":\"Instagram\",\"ico