w it. The year is 1600. Ten years have passed since Oda Nobunaga unified the whole of Japan. When Nobunaga realizes he is nearing the end of his life, he announces that he will hand over the reins of power to whoever brings him the strongest warrior. The generals, whose dreams of conquering the country had been crushed, put up their own strongest warriors and aim to become the king of the country!\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: Kodansha USA)\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx193296-MNiEPtAn7xNi.jpg\",\"color\":\"#f16b43\"},\"trailer\":null,\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/17-R0tMgOvwvhsS.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/tenkaichi_MYM?t=khzWsNr-jXRxsCw0HLAKrw&s=09\"}],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":137158,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Tenkaichi: Nihon Saikyou Bugeisha Ketteisen\",\"native\":\"\\u30c6\\u30f3\\u30ab\\u30a4\\u30c1\\u3000\\u65e5\\u672c\\u6700\\u5f37\\u6b66\\u82b8\\u8005\\u6c7a\\u5b9a\\u6226\",\"english\":\"Tenkaichi: The Greatest Warrior Under the Rising Sun\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/137158\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":204060,\"idMal\":63100,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Tetsunabe no Jan!\",\"native\":\"\\u9244\\u934b\\u306e\\u30b8\\u30e3\\u30f3\\uff01\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2026,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":null,\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Comedy\"],\"synonyms\":[\"Iron Wok Jan!\"],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":736,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"MANGA\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u9244\\u934b\\u306e\\u30b8\\u30e3\\u30f3\",\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/ani