Fantasy\"],\"synonyms\":[\"Jeonjijeok Dokja Sijeom\",\"\\uc804\\uc9c0\\uc801 \\ub3c5\\uc790 \\uc2dc\\uc810\",\"Omniscient Reader's Viewpoint\",\"ORV\"],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":24564,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"OTHER\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":null,\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/179068\",\"description\":\"Dokja was an average office worker whose sole interest was reading his favorite web novel 'Three Ways to Survive the Apocalypse.' But when the novel suddenly becomes reality, he is the only person who knows how the world will end. Armed with this realization, Dokja uses his understanding to change the course of the story, and the world, as he knows it.<br>\\n<br>\\n(Source: Crunchyroll)\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx179068-wlmOf8c4HnXf.jpg\",\"color\":\"#e4865d\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"jzIGTLlqeRE\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/jzIGTLlqeRE\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/zendokushi-anime.com\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Crunchyroll\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/5-AWN2pVlluCOO.png\",\"color\":\"#F88B24\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.crunchyroll.com\\/\"}],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":119257,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Jeonjijeok Dokja Sijeom\",\"native\":\"\\uc804\\uc9c0\\uc801 \\ub3c5\\uc790 \\uc2dc\\uc810\",\"english\":\"Omniscient Reader\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/119257\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":205966,\"idMal\":null,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"ZERO RISE\",\"native\":\"ZERO RISE\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":null,\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Sports\"],\"synonyms\":[\"\\u30bc\\u30ed\\u30e9\\u30a4\\u30ba\"],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":536,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"OTHER\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u30bc\\u30ed\\u30e9\\u30a4\\u30ba\",\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/205966\",\"description\":\"In a hyper-competitive society, where the gap between rich and poor is widening,a flawless existence are demanded, and only the strongest survive.\\nStruggling and writhing amidst it all, can they reclaim what they've lost...?<br><br>\\n\\nThose who possess talent, yet have been pushed aside because of past mistakes or the circumstances they were born into. For them, a new beginning is offered \\u2014 a hidden street basketball league known as <i>ZERO RISE.<\\/i><br><br>\\n\\nOnly those who fight their way to victory can erase their past scars and reclaim the stage. Not only trained basketball players can step into this fight. Risking it all and pushing themselves to the limit, every kind of underdog gathers.<br><br>\\n<b>As they fight to RISE up from ZERO.<\\/b><br><br>\\n(Source: ZERO RISE English site)\\n\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx205966-HnS3vR5yDkSG.jpg\",\"color\":\"#c9e40d\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"CLrvbaFm6_c\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/CLrvbaFm6_c\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/219-EwrfceXsqIWg.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/zerorise_pj\"},{\"site\":\"YouTube\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/13-ZwR1Xwgtyrwa.png\",\"color\":\"#FF0000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/@ZERORISE\"},{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/zerorise-pj.com\\/\"}],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":7701,\"name\":\"NICHICALINE\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/7701\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":174427,\"idMal\":57990,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Zombie no Afureta Sekai de Ore dake ga Osowarenai\",\"native\":\"\\u30be\\u30f3\\u30d3\\u306e\\u3042\\u3075\\u308c\\u305f\\u4e16\\u754c\\u3067\\u4ffa\\u3060\\u3051\\u304c\\u8972\\u308f\\u308c\\u306a\\u3044\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2026,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":null,\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Ecchi\",\"Supernatural\",\"Thriller\"],\"synonyms\":[\"I am the only one who is not attacked in the world filled with zombies.\"],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":1578,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"LIGHT_NOVEL\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":null,\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/174427\",\"description\":\"In an instant, the daily life of Takemura, an office worker who hates people, changed. Before he knew it, he found himself in a world full of zombies. But for some reason, he is the only one who is not attacked by the zombies.\\n<br><br>\\n\\\"Helping people? Why would I do that? I'm going to live in this world as I please.\\\" In a post-apocalyptic world where civilization is on the verge of collapse, Takemura has unexpectedly gained great power. As the only person that the zombies won't touch, will he be a hero, or is he just another......?\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: Frontier Works, translated)\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/medium\\/b174427-VgQyYaE6cASQ.jpg\",\"color\":\"#e45d6b\"},\"trailer\":null,\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co