ons the two friends\\/rivals in romance pose to each other to prove their love for this boy who hardly seems to know they exist. That won\\u2019t stop them from conducting nightly rituals to entice him into their dreams, though, or listing out what exactly they like about him, down to the very last organ. But when push comes to shove, will they choose their hilarious friendship over a shot at love? \\n<br><br>\\n(Source: Kodansha USA)\",\"bannerImage\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/banner\\/181284-BthvQRasKf46.jpg\",\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx181284-JJafhd5gDT53.jpg\",\"color\":\"#5da1e4\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"n3c6bAOhVUg\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/n3c6bAOhVUg\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/kirio-fc.com\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/219-EwrfceXsqIWg.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/kirio_fc\"},{\"site\":\"HIDIVE\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/20-3nWxygrjVM5A.png\",\"color\":\"#03AEEF\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.hidive.com\\/season\\/35227\"},{\"site\":\"YouTube\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/13-ZwR1Xwgtyrwa.png\",\"color\":\"#FF0000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/playlist?list=PLxSscENEp7JgMGXyhUEr1I_5ryXN436vi\"}],\"rankings\":[{\"rank\":88,\"type\":\"RATED\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":false}],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":41,\"name\":\"Satelight\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/41\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":171282,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Kirio Fanclub\",\"native\":\"\\u9727\\u5c3e\\u30d5\\u30a1\\u30f3\\u30af\\u30e9\\u30d6\",\"english\":