019s attention. He\\u2019s convinced she\\u2019s out of his league, but as their unlikely friendship grows, Maki starts to wonder\\u2026could there be more than just friendship between them?<br>\\n<br>\\n(Source: Crunchyroll)\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx169580-nXxpmqu6UVux.jpg\",\"color\":\"#f1bb50\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"3mTUxCIyJhA\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/3mTUxCIyJhA\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/17-R0tMgOvwvhsS.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/twitter.com\\/2ndinclass\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/kuranika.asmik-ace.co.jp\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Crunchyroll\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/5-AWN2pVlluCOO.png\",\"color\":\"#F88B24\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.crunchyroll.com\\/series\\/GT00371673\"}],\"rankings\":[{\"rank\":436,\"type\":\"RATED\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":true},{\"rank\":19,\"type\":\"RATED\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":false},{\"rank\":19,\"type\":\"POPULAR\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":false},{\"rank\":7,\"type\":\"RATED\",\"season\":\"SPRING\",\"allTime\":false},{\"rank\":9,\"type\":\"POPULAR\",\"season\":\"SPRING\",\"allTime\":false}],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":957,\"name\":\"CONNECT\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/957\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"ALTERNATIVE\",\"node\":{\"id\":148082,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Class de 2-banme ni Kawaii Onnanoko to Tomodachi ni Natta\",\"native\":\"\\u30af\\u30e9\\u30b9\\u3067\\uff12\\u756a\\u76ee\\u306b\\u53ef\\u611b\\u3044\\u5973\\u306e\\u5b50\\u3068\\u53cb\\u3060\\u3061\\u306b\\u306a\\u3063\\u305f\",\"english\":\"I Made Friends with the Second Prettiest Girl in My Class\"},\"siteUrl\":