Life\"],\"synonyms\":[\"Win like Xiao He\",\"To Be Winner\"],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":355,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"MANGA\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"CN\",\"hashtag\":null,\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/166444\",\"description\":\"Xiao He, a famous player in an online game, once defeated a female thief in the game. Surprisingly, the female thief is a former top-class e-sports player! What makes her end up like this? The two strangers always come across each other without knowing it. What will happen to them in the digital life?\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: Pocket Comics)\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx166444-kPSbXJ1kVDE8.jpg\",\"color\":\"#3586e4\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"cIIEAVY6U0k\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/cIIEAVY6U0k\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"iQIYI\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/204-VS6anqt2SaIN.png\",\"color\":\"#00CC36\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.iqiyi.com\\/a_1ooa2sp6xmd.html\"}],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":106218,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Cheng Ye Xiao He\",\"native\":\"\\u6210\\u4e5f\\u8427\\u6cb3\",\"english\":\"Win like Xiao He\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/106218\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":129741,\"idMal\":null,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Chenmo Zhi Lan\",\"native\":\"\\u6c89\\u9ed8\\u4e4b\\u84dd\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":null,\"format\":\"ONA\",\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Mystery\",\"Sci-Fi\"],\"synonyms\":[\"Tacit Blue\"],\"duration\":22,\"popularity\":236,\"episodes\":13,\"source\":\"ORIGINAL\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"CN\",\"hashtag\":null,\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/129741\",\"description\":\"The story takes place in the City of Sin in a future galaxy: In order to adapt to the changes brought about by technology, a large number of galactic citizens have undergone a high degree of physical modification. However, a group of \\\"cyborgs\\\" has become weaponized, and a series of riots have occurred, plunging the galaxy into unprecedented turmoil. The culprit behind is a high-tech criminal organization codenamed \\\"Illum\\\".\\n<br><br>\\nIn order to fight this evil force, the \\\"Tacit Blue\\\" investigation team led by Carl was established. They began a life-and-death confrontation with Illum, and discovered the shocking conspiracy behind the cyborg riot... During this time, each member of Tacit Blue had to face their own past and scars, and learn to face and redeem themselves, all while saving the galaxy.\",\"bannerImage\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/banner\\/129741-rWQb2KYOJQfs.jpg\",\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx129741-MCh5XZQkC60Z.png\",\"color\":\"#f19386\"},\"trailer\":null,\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.escapevelocity.cn\\/our-work\\/tacit-blue\"}],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":6732,\"name\":\"Escape Velocity Animation\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/6732\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":210309,\"idMal\":48832,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"CHERRY AND VIRGIN\",\"native\":\"CHERRY AND VIRGIN\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2027,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"endDate\":{\"year\":2027,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":null,\"format\":\"MOVIE\",\"genres\":[\"Comedy\",\"Romance\"],\"synonyms\":[],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":1143,\"episodes\":1,\"source\":\"ORIGINAL\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#CHERRYANDVIRGIN\",\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/210309\",\"description\":\"<i>Cherry and Virgin<\\/i> is a romantic comedy featuring a 32-year-old \\\"eromanga\\\" author Ryou and a 28-year-old \\\"fujoshi'' Ami. Neither character is great at interacting with members of the opposite gender\\u2014Ryou is somewhat of an otaku and defenseless against women, and Ami does not have a good impression of 3D men. After a fateful encounter, the story follows the two as they learn to navigate a sea of interpersonal relationships and come to better understand the bitter and sweet aspects of modern relationships.\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: MAL News)\",\"bannerImage\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/banner\\/210309-dniMopiUzuSM.jpg\",\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/medium\\/b210309-PfeIVnq0Z6Iv.jpg\",\"color\":null},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"OxZt56rZ-Tc\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/OxZt56rZ-Tc\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[],\"rankings\":[{\"rank\":7,\"type\":\"POPULAR\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":false}],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":110206,\"idMal\":null,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Chimera\",\"native\":\"\\u30ad\\u30de\\u30a4\\u30e9\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":null,\"format\":\"MOVIE\",\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Horror\",\"Supernatural\"],\"synonyms\":[],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":1457,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"NOVEL\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":null,\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/110206\",\"description\":\"The series centers on K\\u014d \\u014ctori, a normal high school student who experiences a repeating dream of being eaten by a beast from inside himself. When K\\u014d meets Reiichi Kuki, the elite student who rules his school, the encounter awakens hidden powers inside him.\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx110206-aOzRDXHZimT8.jpg\",\"color\":\"#50a1f1\"},\"trailer\":null,\"externalLinks\":[],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":205374,\"idMal\":62702,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Chu Wu\",\"native\":\"\\u695a\\u4e4c\",\"english\":\"The Crow\"},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2026,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":null,\"format\":\"ONA\",\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Fantasy\"],\"synonyms\":[\"\\u0e04\\u0e33\\u0e2a\\u0e32\\u0e1b\\u0e2d\\u0e35\\u0e01\\u0e32\"],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":166,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"MANGA\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"CN\",\"hashtag\":null,\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/205374\",\"description\":\"The dead transformed into vengeful spirits, crossing through a gate to bring calamity to the human world. The delivery man Zhang Zha accidentally entered a haunted graveyard, unleashing a disaster as spirits crossed into the human world. A cast of extraordinary figures became involved. Amid a series of battles and adventures, Zhang grew stronger and a modern martial world story filled with mystery and excitement unfolded.\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx205374-tRZGd0IjdAys.jpg\",\"color\":\"#00bbff\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"cMJUAPXKb70\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\