            "text": "{\"data\":{\"Page\":{\"pageInfo\":{\"hasNextPage\":true,\"total\":5000},\"media\":[{\"id\":202253,\"idMal\":62931,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"DEATH STRANDING ISOLATIONS (Working Title)\",\"native\":\"DEATH STRANDING ISOLATIONS (Working Title)\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2027,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":null,\"format\":\"ONA\",\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Adventure\",\"Horror\",\"Sci-Fi\",\"Supernatural\"],\"synonyms\":[\"\\u30c7\\u30b9\\u30fb\\u30b9\\u30c8\\u30e9\\u30f3\\u30c7\\u30a3\\u30f3\\u30b0\",\"\\u30c7\\u30b9\\u30b9\\u30c8\"],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":780,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"VIDEO_GAME\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":null,\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/202253\",\"description\":\"An original anime series based on the \\u201cDeath Stranding\\u201d video game. <br><br>\\n\\nOnce, there was an explosion... \\n<br><br>\\nLonesome souls of the dead manifest in the physical world, reaching in search of the living. However, the connection they create triggers a massive explosion that eradicates anything of this world\\u2014a phenomenon referred to as the Death Stranding. These events wipe out nations as well as civilization itself. People who remain are now isolated, withdrawn, and without connections. As humanity stands at the brink a legendary porter set out to transport both cargo and wishes of its senders, reconnecting people in the hope that they might still be saved. \\n<br><br>\\nSomewhere in North America, just as Sam Bridges walks through the continent in order to save America, the someones are also trying to deal with their isolation in their own way. An old man trying to realize salvation through ways outside of the connection advocated by Bridges. A female warrior who tries to kickstart a world of constant fighting. A boy with a grudge against Bridges. A girl who embraces loneliness. <br><br>\\n\\nOn the precipice of the end of humanity and the world, their fates and hopes converge, as another story of Death Stranding begins. \\n<br>\\nAnd now, comes another explosion... <br><br>\\n\\n(Source: KOJIMA PRODUCTIONS, edited)\\n\\n<br><br><i>Note: Title and Relations are provisional and will be updated when more info is announced.<\\/i>\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx202253-yXhyhChbYDBG.jpg\",\"color\":\"#fe6b28\"},\"trailer\":null,\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Disney Plus\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/118-mphNAqNDTvhO.png\",\"color\":\"#21037C\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.disneyplus.com\\/\"}],\"rankings\":[{\"rank\":2,\"type\":\"POPULAR\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":false}],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":7229,\"name\":\"E&H Production\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/7229\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"OTHER\",\"node\":{\"id\":199150,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"DEATH STRANDING MOSQUITO (Working Title)\",\"native\":\"DEATH STRANDING MOSQUITO (Working Title)\",\"english\":null},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/199150\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":199150,\"idMal\":62549,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"DEATH STRANDING MOSQUITO (Working Title)\",\"native\":\"DEATH STRANDING MOSQUITO (Working Title)\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":null,\"format\":\"MOVIE\",\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Horror\",\"Sci-Fi\",\"Supernatural\"],\"synonyms\":[\"\\u30c7\\u30b9\\u30b9\\u30c8\",\"\\u30c7\\u30b9\\u30fb\\u30b9\\u30c8\\u30e9\\u30f3\\u30c7\\u30a3\\u30f3\\u30b0\"],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":1232,\"episodes\":1,\"source\":\"VIDEO_GAME\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":null,\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/199150\",\"description\":\"Announced at the Kojima Productions 10th anniversary event: an anime film set in the \\u201cDeath Stranding\\u201d video game series.\\n\\n<br><br><i>Note: Title and Relations are provisional and will be updated when more info is announced.<\\/i>\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx199150-neXyswwJIlnN.jpg\",\"color\":\"#6b281a\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"GFLoRTwPtic\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/GFLoRTwPtic\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":7540,\"name\":\"ABC Animation Studio\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/7540\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"OTHER\",\"node\":{\"id\":202253,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"DEATH STRANDING ISOLATIONS (Working Title)\",\"native\":\"DEATH STRANDING ISOLATIONS (Working Title)\",\"english\":null},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/202253\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":153474,\"idMal\":null,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Di Ba\",\"native\":\"\\u5e1d\\u9738\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":null,\"format\":\"ONA\",\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Drama\",\"Fantasy\"],\"synonyms\":[\"Emperor's Domination\"],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":144,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"OTHER\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"CN\",\"hashtag\":null,\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/153474\",\"description\":\"Over the years, countless powerful cultivators have come and gone. \\nBut the world never realized that behind every powerful cultivator, there seemed to be a mysterious... Dark Crow. After the Dark Crow guided a legion of young cultivators to the peak of cultivation and established their own sects, he chose to leave the world behind.\\n<br><br>\\nThousands of years have passed since his departure, and the once mighty sects have become weak and in danger of failing. Finally the Dark Crow returned in the form of a young man, here to fulfill his promise to defend the sects.\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: Tencent, translated)\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx153474-YYNK0CjTI7RG.png\",\"color\":null},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"xR-Uq-9EGO8\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/xR-Uq-9EGO8\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Tencent Video\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/121-BQIBl0q1Eh9w.png\",\"color\":\"#2FA3F9\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/v.qq.com\\/detail\\/t\\/mzc00200hbpl39z.html\"}],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":6475,\"name\":\"Ruo Hong Culture\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/6475\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"ALTERNATIVE\",\"node\":{\"id\":147491,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Di Ba\",\"native\":\"\\u5e1d\\u9738\",\"english\":\"Emperor Is Back\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/147491\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":122529,\"idMal\":null,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Dian Dao\",\"native\":\"\\u70b9\\u9053\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":null,\"format\":\"ONA\",\"genres\":[],\"synonyms\":[],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":74,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"ORIGINAL\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"CN\",\"hashtag\":null,\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/122529\",\"description\":null,\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.ani