null,\"source\":\"OTHER\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"CN\",\"hashtag\":null,\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/137687\",\"description\":\"The beautiful young girl awakened the ancient sword, and became its slave? She was just trying to cultivate her swordsmanship, but instead she was forcefully transformed and imbued with its techniques. There's actually such a perverted practice?\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: Tencent, translated)\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx137687-D2M56ilscXik.png\",\"color\":\"#43e450\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"kN9H1ZYFN0w\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/kN9H1ZYFN0w\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Tencent Video\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/121-BQIBl0q1Eh9w.png\",\"color\":\"#2FA3F9\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/v.qq.com\\/detail\\/t\\/mzc00200ililxr0.html\"},{\"site\":\"Weibo\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/120-Q60x0hPKE19B.png\",\"color\":\"#E6162D\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/weibo.com\\/u\\/7658748054\"}],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":6162,\"name\":\"Foch\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/6162\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"ALTERNATIVE\",\"node\":{\"id\":144511,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Jian Ling Tongju Riji\",\"native\":\"\\u5251\\u7075\\u540c\\u5c45\\u65e5\\u8bb0\",\"english\":null},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/144511\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":153462,\"idMal\":null,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Jianzhi Shenxian\",\"native\":\"\\u517c\\u804c\\u795e\\u4ed9\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":null,\"format\":\"ONA\",\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Comedy\",\"Fantasy\"],\"synonyms\":[\"Pluralistic Immortal\"],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":97,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"MANGA\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"CN\",\"hashtag\":null,\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/153462\",\"description\":\"Ye Yangtian was born into a wealthy family, but he lived a frivolous life. However, although he is a playboy, his heart is full of pure feelings. When prosperity is exhausted, there is only one fool in love left in the world. Unexpectedly, Ye Yang meets the immortal on the way to heaven! All of a sudden, the world is in chaos! L\\u00fc Dongbin became a strong reserve of the chairman. Heaven has an extra immortal, but the mortal world is unfolding.\\n\\n\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx153462-AzBMA7OuG6je.png\",\"color\":\"#e46b1a\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"UTqbUSgB0fE\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/UTqbUSgB0fE\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Tencent Video\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/121-BQIBl0q1Eh9w.png\",\"color\":\"#2FA3F9\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/v.qq.com\\/detail\\/t\\/mzc0020042oqcme.html\"}],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"ADAPTATION\",\"node\":{\"id\":115247,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Jianzhi Shenxian\",\"native\":\"\\u517c\\u804c\\u795e\\u4ed9\",\"english\":null},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/115247\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":155329,\"idMal\":null,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Jidao Long Shen 2\",\"native\":\"\\u6781\\u9053\\u9f99\\u795e \\u7b2c\\u4e8c\\u5b63\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":null,\"format\":\"ONA\",\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Fanta