ce: iQIYI, translated)\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx211220-V4JuyjRR4auR.png\",\"color\":\"#780d0d\"},\"trailer\":null,\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"iQIYI\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/204-VS6anqt2SaIN.png\",\"color\":\"#00CC36\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.iqiyi.com\\/v_o7rmp790lk.html?vid=092fe1c03df5be829680876835270aa7&fid=4198235234784001&ps4=0&ischarge=false&ps3=pca_115_fansou_card&lt=3&ht=0&e2=92d1a4e49b4e7f7c8e3fd7b2123d3c0e&ps2=3\"}],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":6546,\"name\":\"GARDEN\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/6546\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":137700,\"idMal\":null,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Liaotian Qun De Richang Shenghuo\",\"native\":\"\\u804a\\u5929\\u7fa4\\u7684\\u65e5\\u5e38\\u751f\\u6d3b\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":null,\"format\":\"ONA\",\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Adventure\",\"Comedy\",\"Fantasy\",\"Slice of Life\"],\"synonyms\":[],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":258,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"OTHER\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"CN\",\"hashtag\":null,\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/137700\",\"description\":\"On a certain day, Song Shuhang accidentally joined a deeply afflicted Xianxia chuunibyou(Year 2 middle school disease) chat group, the group members inside all address each other as \\u2018fellow daoist\\u2019. Their contact cards are all either Sect Master, Cave Master, Spiritual Master or Heavenly Expert. Even the group master\\u2019s missing pet dog named Great Devil Dog abandoned his home. They chat all day about things like concocting pills, intruding mysterious territories, martial arts experiences and more.\\n<br><br>\\nOne day, he abruptly realizes after lurking for a long time that\\u2026\\u2026 In this group, every single group member is actually a real cultivator, with the ability to move mountains and drain seas, the kind that can live for thousands of years!\\n<br><br>\\nAh ah ah ah, his worldview has utterly collapsed in a single night!\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx137700-x4DGFWsbutvj.png\",\"color\":\"#d6bb1a\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"LX8i3EEqXuI\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/LX8i3EEqXuI\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Weibo\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/120-Q60x0hPKE19B.png\",\"color\":\"#E6162D\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/weibo.com\\/u\\/2270328724\"},{\"site\":\"Tencent Video\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/121-BQIBl0q1Eh9w.png\",\"color\":\"#2FA3F9\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/v.qq.com\\/detail\\/t\\/mzc00200rrl3c3u.html\"}],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":6931,\"name\":\"Max-World\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/6931\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"ALTERNATIVE\",\"node\":{\"id\":102799,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Xiu Zhen Liao Tian Qun\",\"native\":\"\\u4fee\\u771f\\u804a\\u5929\\u7fa4\",\"english\":\"Cultivation Chat Group\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/102799\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":156094,\"idMal\":null,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Lin Yuan Xing\",\"native\":\"\\u4e34\\u6e0a\\u884c\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":null,\"format\":\"ONA\",\"genres\":[\"Fantasy\"],\"synonyms\":[\"Trip to the Abyss\"],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":84,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":nu