ko's only source of solitude, her apartment, has been turned upside down. Now, every day is full of heart-pounding surprises! \\n<br><br>\\n(Source: Manga Plaza)\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx202985-lyp5TYpTnqSg.jpg\",\"color\":\"#e4935d\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"UE1NvURy0-E\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/UE1NvURy0-E\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Official Site\",\"icon\":null,\"color\":null,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.tadaoja-anime.com\\/\"},{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/17-R0tMgOvwvhsS.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/tadaoja_anime\"},{\"site\":\"Crunchyroll\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/5-AWN2pVlluCOO.png\",\"color\":\"#F88B24\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.crunchyroll.com\\/series\\/GT00371775\\/pardon-the-intrusion-im-home\"}],\"rankings\":[{\"rank\":80,\"type\":\"RATED\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":false}],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":103,\"name\":\"Tatsunoko Production\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/103\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":201573,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Tadaima, Ojamasaremasu!\",\"native\":\"\\u305f\\u3060\\u3044\\u307e\\u3001\\u304a\\u3058\\u3083\\u307e\\u3055\\u308c\\u307e\\u3059\\uff01\",\"english\":\"Pardon the Intrusion, I'm Home!\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/201573\"}}]}}},{\"id\":410978,\"episode\":7,\"airingAt\":1778945400,\"media\":{\"id\":202102,\"idMal\":62913,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"NEEDY GIRL OVERDOSE\",\"native\":\"NEEDY GIRL OVERDOSE\",\"english\":\"NEEDY GIRL OVERDOSE\"},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2026,\"month\":4,\"day\":5},\"endDate\":{\"year\":2026,\"month\":6,\"day\":28},\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"season\":\"SPRING\",\"format\":\"TV\",\"genres\":[\"Adventure\",\"Drama\",\"Psychological\",\"Slice of Life\"],\"synonyms\":[\"\\u30cb\\u30fc\\u30c7\\u30a3\\u30ac\\u30fc\\u30eb \\u30aa\\u30fc\\u30d0\\u30fc\\u30c9\\u30fc\\u30ba\",\"NEEDY STREAMER OVERLOAD\",\"NEEDY GIRL OVERDOSE -OVERTURE-\"],\"duration\":25,\"popularity\":29705,\"episodes\":13,\"source\":\"VIDEO_GAME\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u30cb\\u30c7\\u30a3\\u30ac\",\"averageScore\":68,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/202102\",\"description\":\"OMGkawaiiAngel, affectionately known as \\\"KAngel\\\", is the top streamer girl with 10 million subscribers, and not a day goes by without seeing her in action. Whether online, on TV, or at a live show, she is always surrounded by her cheering fans.\\n<br><br>\\nStriving to catch up with KAngel's popularity is a three-girl streaming unit called Karamazov.\\n<br><br>\\nAnd far removed from the world of these streamers is Kache, a girl who lives with her freeloader boyfriend while working at a theme cafe.\\n<br><br>\\nThe story of the \\\"Internet Angel\\\" who captivated the world, woven by a girl who shines like a star and girls who reach for that brilliance, and the story of \\\"you\\\" on the other side of the screen, begins here.\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: Official Site)\\n<br><br>\\n<i>Note: Prior to broadcasting, \\\"NEEDY GIRL OVERDOSE -OVERTURE-\\\" \\u2014 a theatrical pre-screening of the first 3 episodes rearranged and edited together\\u2014 debuted in Japan on March 6, 2026.<\\/i>\",\"bannerImage\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/banner\\/202102-RBgWbaATyuDt.jpg\",\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx202102-7qDmTI7eT5xF.png\",\"color\":\"#c950f1\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"dxiVApAjPDg\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/dxiVApAjPDg\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\