 these mysterious events. Each story is independent but features recurring characters you'll come to know and appreciate as they, each in their own way, try to deal with things 'not of this world'.\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: MU)\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx207675-h3TZK82jG5aD.png\",\"color\":\"#e4a15d\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"gUKK4uohtgE\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/gUKK4uohtgE\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"YouTube\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/13-ZwR1Xwgtyrwa.png\",\"color\":\"#FF0000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/playlist?list=PLxSscENEp7JgbFVxH93w5flYikcz7V3YM\"},{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/219-EwrfceXsqIWg.png\",\"color\":\"#000000\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/x.com\\/animehyakki_PR\"},{\"site\":\"Prime Video\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/261-I11R5ZZpcwgD.png\",\"color\":\"#1A98FF\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.primevideo.com\\/detail\\/0M5TD1X03KDPFOAB178702QXF4\"}],\"rankings\":[{\"rank\":8,\"type\":\"RATED\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":false},{\"rank\":9,\"type\":\"POPULAR\",\"season\":null,\"allTime\":false},{\"rank\":5,\"type\":\"RATED\",\"season\":\"SPRING\",\"allTime\":false},{\"rank\":7,\"type\":\"POPULAR\",\"season\":\"SPRING\",\"allTime\":false}],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":7472,\"name\":\"Imagica Infos\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/7472\"},{\"id\":7531,\"name\":\"Imageworks Studio\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/7531\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":34623,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Hyakki Yakou Shou\",\"native\":\"\\u767e\\u9b3c\\u591c\\u884c\\u6284\",\"english\":null},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/34623\"}}]}}},{\