:[\"Comedy\",\"Fantasy\",\"Romance\",\"Slice of Life\"],\"synonyms\":[\"Observation Records of My Fianc\\u00e9e: The Misadventures of a Self-Proclaimed Villainess\",\"\\u0e1a\\u0e31\\u0e19\\u0e17\\u0e36\\u0e01\\u0e2a\\u0e31\\u0e07\\u0e40\\u0e01\\u0e15\\u0e01\\u0e32\\u0e23\\u0e13\\u0e4c\\u0e04\\u0e39\\u0e48\\u0e2b\\u0e21\\u0e31\\u0e49\\u0e19\\u0e1c\\u0e39\\u0e49\\u0e1b\\u0e23\\u0e30\\u0e01\\u0e32\\u0e28\\u0e15\\u0e31\\u0e27\\u0e40\\u0e1b\\u0e47\\u0e19\\u0e19\\u0e32\\u0e07\\u0e23\\u0e49\\u0e32\\u0e22\"],\"duration\":24,\"popularity\":18038,\"episodes\":12,\"source\":\"LIGHT_NOVEL\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"JP\",\"hashtag\":\"#\\u81ea\\u79f0\\u60aa\\u5f79\\u4ee4\\u5b22\",\"averageScore\":71,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/192808\",\"description\":\"Bertia is reincarnated into her favorite otome game\\u2014not as the heroine, but as the villainess engaged to the perfect Crown Prince Cecil! Fully aware that her role is to sabotage his future romance, she\\u2019s determined to bloom as a wicked flower and wither away according to the story. But no matter how hard she tries to scheme, her \\u201cevil\\u201d plans only make her more endearing!<br>\\n<br>\\n(Source: Crunchyroll)\\n<br><br>\\n<i>Note: Jishou Akuyaku Reijou na Konyakusha no Kansatsu Kiroku. was streamed 3 days in advance of the TV broadcast on Prime Video, and Crunchyroll beginning April 3, 2026. Regular broadcasting began on April 6, 2026.<\\/i>\",\"bannerImage\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/banner\\/192808-iaS1GnOo5l3G.jpg\",\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx192808-tfrX4Gn2Y1Ye.jpg\",\"color\":\"#5da1e4\"},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"r6RkeRy4B4c\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/r6RkeRy4B4c\\/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Twitter\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/219-EwrfceXs