cape death and became a dragon tamer, looking to start a new legendary journey.\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: Tencent, translated)\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx153465-R9kh0vZhFZQF.png\",\"color\":\"#e4a150\"},\"trailer\":null,\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Tencent Video\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/121-BQIBl0q1Eh9w.png\",\"color\":\"#2FA3F9\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/v.qq.com\\/detail\\/t\\/mzc00200tzdxr9b.html\"}],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":6344,\"name\":\"Mili Pictures\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/6344\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"ALTERNATIVE\",\"node\":{\"id\":141171,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Mu Long Shi\",\"native\":\"\\u7267\\u9f99\\u5e08\",\"english\":\"Dragon Tamer\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/141171\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":199449,\"idMal\":60566,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Nan Hong\",\"native\":\"\\u96be\\u54c4\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":null,\"format\":\"ONA\",\"genres\":[\"Romance\",\"Slice of Life\"],\"synonyms\":[\"Eternal Love\",\"Endless Devotion\",\"First Frost\"],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":456,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"NOVEL\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"CN\",\"hashtag\":null,\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/199449\",\"description\":\"When Wen Yifan returned to her hometown for work, she unexpectedly ran into the rumored \\\"First-Class Handsome Guy\\\" at a bar. However, she soon discovered that he was Sang Yan, someone she had hurt and rejected in high school. In a twist of fate, these two individuals who could never get along found themselves constantly crossing paths. They even ended up renting the same unit by chance and becoming housemates. With unspoken feelings buried deep within, strong emotions begin to stir...<br><br>\\n\\nLet's see how Sang Yan, the \\\"Peak Ideal Boyfriend,\\\" interprets and expresses his profound affection and sweet love!<br><br>\\n\\n(Source: INKR)\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/medium\\/b199449-0AXlHs4CZFDc.jpg\",\"color\":\"#f16b43\"},\"trailer\":null,\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Bilibili\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/45-6JAD1SYYCHI2.png\",\"color\":\"#00A1D6\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.bilibili.com\\/bangumi\\/media\\/md23774654\"}],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"SOURCE\",\"node\":{\"id\":147198,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Nan Hong\",\"native\":\"\\u96be\\u54c4\",\"english\":\"Eternal Love\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/147198\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":121301,\"idMal\":null,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Nezha Chuanqi - Long Yu Dixiatie\",\"native\":\"\\u54ea\\u5412\\u4f20\\u5947\\u00b7\\u9f99\\u4e0e\\u5730\\u4e0b\\u94c1\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":null,\"format\":\"MOVIE\",\"genres\":[],\"synonyms\":[],\"duration\":110,\"popularity\":147,\"episodes\":1,\"source\":\"NOVEL\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"CN\",\"hashtag\":null,\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/121301\",\"description\":\"The films tell the story about how the dragon tribe decided to take revenge on mankind in order to free themselves of their shackles.\",\"bannerImage\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/banner\\/121301-Ah6HSwh28PyP.jpg\",\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx121301-SqAMki99SxTh.jpg\",\"color\":\"#f1e4c9\"},\"trailer\":null,\"externalLinks\":[],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":168245,\"idMal\":62751,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Nian Fanchen\",\"native\":\"\\u5ff5\\u51e1\\u5c18\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":2026,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":null,\"format\":\"ONA\",\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Adventure\",\"Fantasy\"],\"synonyms\":[\"I'm Actually a Cultivation Bigshot\",\"Yuanlai Wo Shi Xiuxian Dalao\",\"\\u539f\\u6765\\u6211\\u662f\\u4fee\\u4ed9\\u5927\\u4f6c\"],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":222,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"OTHER\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"CN\",\"hashtag\":null,\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/168245\",\"description\":\"Li Nianfan transmigrated into the world of immortal cultivation with a mortal body. After learning that he had no talent for cultivation, he settled down to live an ordinary life. But only to find...\\n<br><br>\\nThe dog he adopted watched his writing and painting, and became the demon lord that ruled half the world. The tree he planted in the backyard listened to him play and sing, and grew into the world tree that held up the bridge between heaven and earth. A casual conversation enlightened a passing traveler to become the immortal sage that defined the era...\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: Tencent, translated)\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/large\\/bx168245-aWbAktBRYTf6.jpg\",\"color\":\"#e4ae5d\"},\"trailer\":null,\"externalLinks\":[{\"site\":\"Tencent Video\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/link\\/icon\\/121-BQIBl0q1Eh9w.png\",\"color\":\"#2FA3F9\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/v.qq.com\\/x\\/cover\\/mzc00200fhers3y.html\"}],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":6320,\"name\":\"Chongzhuo Animation\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/6320\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[{\"relationType\":\"ALTERNATIVE\",\"node\":{\"id\":145269,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Yuanlai Wo Shi Xiuxian Dalao\",\"native\":\"\\u539f\\u6765\\u6211\\u662f\\u4fee\\u4ed9\\u5927\\u4f6c\",\"english\":\"A Big Shot Actually\"},\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/manga\\/145269\"}}]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":155324,\"idMal\":null,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Nitian Zhan Shen\",\"native\":\"\\u9006\\u5929\\u6218\\u795e\",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":null,\"format\":\"ONA\",\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Adventure\",\"Fantasy\"],\"synonyms\":[\"God of War Against the Sky\",\"Heaven Defying God of War\"],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":86,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"OTHER\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"CN\",\"hashtag\":null,\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/155324\",\"description\":\"Hundred years ago, a generation of God of War Ye Qingyun was born, crushing the sons of various great figures, making the enemy frightened by the wind, but unexpectedly betrayed by his lover Luo Ling, brother wolf thirteen, and falling into the Devil Abyss! A hundred years later, all walks of life entered the golden age, and wicked characters emerged wildly! Ye Qingyun was reborn as a waste disciple of the Ye Family, a small family in the Eight Desolate Continent! Fate is reversed and fate is changed! In this life, I will not only crush the genius, but also kill all those who bear me! A ruthless sword, a dragon slaying knife, kill everything, unify the gods, dominate all things!\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\