"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/8144\",\"description\":\"The story centers on a princess who wishes to reach the Moon. Her journey and resulting disappearance raise clamor and chaos throughout the royal palace and among the creatures of the kingdom.\",\"bannerImage\":null,\"isAdult\":false,\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https:\\/\\/s4.anilist.co\\/file\\/anilistcdn\\/media\\/anime\\/cover\\/medium\\/8144.jpg\",\"color\":null},\"trailer\":null,\"externalLinks\":[],\"rankings\":[],\"studios\":{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":371,\"name\":\"Union Cho\",\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/studio\\/371\"}]},\"relations\":{\"edges\":[]},\"airingSchedule\":{\"nodes\":[]}},{\"id\":206274,\"idMal\":62794,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Tian Guan Xue Yuan\",\"native\":\"\\u5929\\u5b98\\u5b66\\u9662 \",\"english\":null},\"startDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"endDate\":{\"year\":null,\"month\":null,\"day\":null},\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"season\":null,\"format\":\"ONA\",\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Fantasy\"],\"synonyms\":[\"Tian Guan\"],\"duration\":null,\"popularity\":47,\"episodes\":null,\"source\":\"ORIGINAL\",\"countryOfOrigin\":\"CN\",\"hashtag\":null,\"averageScore\":null,\"siteUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/anilist.co\\/anime\\/206274\",\"description\":\"To resist invasions from other worlds, the Heavenly Great Sage founded Tianguan Academy. Every year, the Academy would recruit new students\\u2014but in the end, only nine could become the official Heavenly Officers. Gu Tian, a young soccer player, accidentally awakened his hidden power while saving someone on the field. Invited by his senior Xia Zhi, he boarded Subway Line 36 to Tianguan Academy. With the world's finest teachers, strict assessments, and a brutal elimination system, the Academy pushes its students to the limit. By a stroke of fortune, Gu Tian became the 81st student to pass the entrance trial. Under the guidance of celestial masters, he studied spells and divine decrees, honed his combat skills against 